# game/act2.rpy:6
translate schinese act2_1e8374e7:

    # "I slowly drift off deep into my own mind where all I see is endless darkness. Normally, whenever I have moments like these, I’m rendered completely helpless while a horrid nightmare creeps in."
    "我的意识渐渐飘向了无边无际的黑暗深处，每当可怕的噩梦就这样毫无征兆地出现时，我都会感到深深的无助。"

# game/act2.rpy:7
translate schinese act2_b620bc53:

    # "I can’t even form any cognitive thought during those times as I seem to simply exist as a witness to the conjured images being laid out before me."
    "在噩梦悄然来袭时，我甚至无法形成任何完整的自我认知，只能作为一位观测者，目睹发生在我面前的一切。"

# game/act2.rpy:8
translate schinese act2_0737afe8:

    # "This time, however, I manage to think and contemplate coherently despite being fully aware that I’m still sound asleep… Nothing morbid comes to even reveal itself from this void, too."
    "然而这一次，尽管我清楚地意识到自己此刻还在沉睡，我还是尽可能地去主导自己的意识...可是在这片虚空中，并没有任何东西在我的视野中显现。"

# game/act2.rpy:9
translate schinese act2_f9b0a081:

    # "It’s... oddly tranquil... Yet there’s still this unsettling feeling that never seems to leave my abstract being."
    "...周围出奇地平静...不知为何，这让我愈发地感到不安，似乎我将永远被困在这片无意识的空间里。"

# game/act2.rpy:10
translate schinese act2_604996f4:

    # "Is… is this a moment for me to think to myself? I suppose I really haven’t had the time to sit down and think about everything that’s happened..."
    "也许...我应该在这个时候多去思考有关自己的事？毕竟，到目前为止，我一直都没有什么时间可以坐下来好好思考发生在自己身边的一切..."

# game/act2.rpy:11
translate schinese act2_c590dbc4:

    # main "Alright then… let’s do this."
    main "好吧...就这么办。"

# game/act2.rpy:12
translate schinese act2_7538a140:

    # "After I tell myself those words, the void melts and readjusts itself into the image of the Midnight Sun base’s main hall. It’s quite fuzzy and muddled, especially in the edges of my ‘vision’, though."
    "在我自言自语之后，虚空便开始瓦解，我的四周变换为‘午夜炙阳’基地的场景。然而，画面却异常的混乱和模糊，所谓的‘视野’的边缘也尤为昏暗。"

# game/act2.rpy:13
translate schinese act2_39ce0ff1:

    # "Huh… it seems like whatever I think of comes to life here. Is this what lucid dreaming is like?"
    "嗯...如果这也算是梦境的话，那我现在一定是在做清醒梦？"

# game/act2.rpy:14
translate schinese act2_9cfba59b:

    # "I remember Dylan telling me a lot about it and how fun and exhilarating these experiences can be… Since I’m here anyway, I suppose I’ll go ahead and indulge myself."
    "我记得Dylan曾经告诉过我，他所经历的梦境往往都是多么有趣、多么令人振奋...既然现在我已经意识到自己陷入梦里了，那么我理应能够自由行动才对。"

# game/act2.rpy:15
translate schinese act2_3a3c48ee:

    # "This is certainly a lot less detailed than the real thing, but I can clearly tell that over there is Alice’s usual work station with all the panels floating around."
    "基地大厅控制室里的物品明显比平常少的多。但是Alice常用的工作台、以及四周漂浮着的面板，依然是清晰可见。"

# game/act2.rpy:16
translate schinese act2_4ecbbbba:

    # "It’s all jumbled up, though, with some screens overlapping and her main panel being in a chaotic arrangement of different shortcuts and folders."
    "然而，周围的一切都是无序的。一些面板交叠在一起，屏幕上混乱地排列着不同的文件夹和快捷方式。"

# game/act2.rpy:17
translate schinese act2_4d193549:

    # "By the sofa set on the other end of the room, there’s a coffee table filled with… candy wrappers? No, they’re too big to be just wrappers…"
    "在房间另一端的沙发旁，有一张咖啡桌，上面摆满了...糖果的包装纸？不，如果是包装纸的话也未免太大了..."

# game/act2.rpy:18
translate schinese act2_abd38dd4:

    # main "If only I could go get a closer look…"
    main "要是我能离近点看看就好了..."

# game/act2.rpy:19
translate schinese act2_684e4b70:

    # "And just like that, the scenery zooms in onto the coffee table. I’m then able to take a closer look at the wrappers. These are… milk chocolate cubes? From a famous manufacturer, too…"
    "在我刚有这样的念头之后，我的视野就放大到了咖啡桌上。现在我能够仔细看清这些包装纸了...牛奶巧克力？还是来自一家著名的制造商..."

# game/act2.rpy:20
translate schinese act2_f46180f1:

    # "It’s a shame I can’t eat them for being a canine."
    "很可惜，作为犬科动物，这种食物我无福消受。"

# game/act2.rpy:21
translate schinese act2_5cebc452:

    # "I wonder who eats this many chocolates anyway? Can’t be Max… could it? Hmph, I’d rather a meteor shower will hit Bayline City right now than believe that."
    "我有些纳闷到底是谁吃了这么多的牛奶巧克力？是Max吗？估计不是。呵...我宁可相信Bayline城现在下起了流星雨，也不相信Max会一个人吃这么多甜食。"

# game/act2.rpy:22
translate schinese act2_78125645:

    # "Maybe Oswald? But he’s a canine, too… Hmmm..."
    "也许是Oswald？但...呃...他也是犬科..."

# game/act2.rpy:23
translate schinese act2_c9ca8121:

    # main "...Oswald"
    main "...Oswald。"

# game/act2.rpy:24
translate schinese act2_8e5424ca:

    # "His likeness appears before me simply standing there with that signature smile of his. His gentle gaze meets mine, never breaking eye contact as his face flushes red… How odd..."
    "狼的面容浮现在我眼前，他依然带着自己标志性的微笑站在那里。当我与他的目光相遇、并交汇在一起时，我发现他的脸染上了一层红晕...好奇怪..."

# game/act2.rpy:25
translate schinese act2_fe676eb7:

    # "Everyone else seems to be wary, even hostile towards me... except you."
    "其他人似乎都对我怀有警惕，甚至带有敌意...除了你。"

# game/act2.rpy:26
translate schinese act2_7737736f:

    # "Why are you so different? Your kindness and concern… Where does it come from? Out of everyone I’ve encountered in this waking nightmare, you just seem to be..."
    "为什么你会如此与众不同？你的善意和关心...到底又是从何而来？在我清醒的噩梦里遇到的每个人中，你似乎是..."

# game/act2.rpy:27
translate schinese act2_6dddb99e:

    # main "... the greatest mystery of them all."
    main "...最大的谜团。"

# game/act2.rpy:28
translate schinese act2_fcc77959:

    # "I stir slowly from my deep sleep feeling neither light nor heavy. It’s as if my whole body’s gone numb and confused not knowing what it should feel."
    "我从沉睡中缓缓清醒过来，甚至分不清现在到底是在梦境还是现实。似乎仍处于麻木状态的身体，让我无法准确描述自己的真实感受。"

# game/act2.rpy:29
translate schinese act2_56284eb2:

    # "What a surreal experience… I can still see the faint silhouette of the hunky wolf in my vision, but it quickly disappears as soon as I take notice."
    "这真是一场超脱现实的体验...甚至那只壮狼的微弱身影仍然在我的视线中，稍纵即逝。"

# game/act2.rpy:32
translate schinese act2_49cebee5:

    # "I try to take my surroundings in slowly once more... Still the same, slightly dusty and mostly empty room."
    "我试着再一次慢慢感受周围的环境...还是那个略有灰尘、而且几乎空空荡荡的房间。"

# game/act2.rpy:33
translate schinese act2_76707d99:

    # "I then decide to check the time on my phone once blood starts properly recirculating though my entire body again. It’s… way later into the afternoon! Wouldn’t someone have woken me up by now??"
    "然后，当我回过神来，查看手机上的时间时，这才意识到现在已经...到下午了！这么晚了都没有人叫醒我吗？？"

# game/act2.rpy:34
translate schinese act2_1815e11c:

    # "I worriedly jump out of bed and rush towards the hallway, my heart steadily sinking, feeling as if I’ve done something wrong again."
    "我担心地从床上一跃而起，连忙朝走廊冲去，同时心怀愧疚，感觉自己又一次做错了什么。"

# game/act2.rpy:38
translate schinese act2_c292b622:

    # "The door slides open and I run through at full speed, not even being aware of my surroundings."
    "门刚滑开我就一个箭步冲了出去，甚至完全没有注意周围的环境。"

# game/act2.rpy:39
translate schinese act2_143590dc:

    # "What meets me on the other side is a tall figure that I bump into, knocking me off balance before I fall flat on my face."
    "于是我一头撞在了另一侧的一个高大身影上，紧接着脸朝下摔倒在地板上。"

# game/act2.rpy:42
translate schinese act2_ca3f0848:

    # main "GAH!"
    main "啊！"

# game/act2.rpy:43
translate schinese act2_69e6d277:

    # ben "What in the--?!"
    ben "搞什么鬼——？！"

# game/act2.rpy:44
translate schinese act2_6a1d6ef5:

    # "I quickly pick myself back up and look hurriedly at what just I bumped into."
    "我连忙回过神，望向我急匆匆撞到的人。"

# game/act2.rpy:45
translate schinese act2_77b8a086:

    # "Much to my surprise, it was Benjie, who’s holding rolls of some kind of material, some of which are currently on the floor."
    "我这才惊讶地发现面前的人是Benjie。他手中拿着成卷的某种材质的布料，其中一些还被我撞掉在地板上。"

# game/act2.rpy:46
translate schinese act2_3937427f:

    # "Ugh… I do {i}not{/i} want to have another altercation with him. The last thing I need is for both my ears to be bandaged."
    "啊...千万{i}不要{/i}再次和他发生争执了，我可不想两只耳朵都被包扎起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:48
translate schinese act2_db414ee0:

    # ben "You should really watch where you’re going, you know."
    ben "嘿，走路一定要看路。"

# game/act2.rpy:49
translate schinese act2_794533db:

    # "He gives me a mischievous smirk while he keeps his eyes on me. I sigh as I stand up."
    "在他盯着我看的时候，朝我露出了不太友善的假笑。我一边叹气，一边站起身。"

# game/act2.rpy:50
translate schinese act2_57559fbc:

    # main "Yep. I’m aware."
    main "好，我会注意的。"

# game/act2.rpy:52
translate schinese act2_15a8576d:

    # ben "If strangers were to see you like that, they’d think you were a lunatic."
    ben "如果有陌生人看到你这样，他们会认为你是个疯子。"

# game/act2.rpy:53
translate schinese act2_0b5f4bf3:

    # "Benjie moves toward my other side, giggling like an asshole."
    "Benjie走到我的身侧，像个混蛋一样傻笑着。"

# game/act2.rpy:54
translate schinese act2_aa87cf49:

    # main "So… you think I’m a lunatic?"
    main "所以...你觉得我是疯子吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:56
translate schinese act2_18574deb:

    # ben "Oh, please. You make it sound like we’re complete strangers."
    ben "噢，得了吧。你说得好像我们完全是陌生人一样。"

# game/act2.rpy:57
translate schinese act2_bacd231e:

    # main "But we are, though."
    main "但是，我们确实是..."

# game/act2.rpy:58
translate schinese act2_24410db3:

    # "Benjie chuckles to himself."
    "Benjie突然轻声笑了。"

# game/act2.rpy:60
translate schinese act2_797c215b:

    # ben "My, my. So cold and hostile. Where even is that coming from?"
    ben "我的，我的问题。之前确实对你太冷漠了，甚至还有些敌视你。"

# game/act2.rpy:61
translate schinese act2_2aff07e3:

    # "Ugh, tell that to the bandaged ear! I swear, what is with this guy…?"
    "呃...我向我包扎着的耳朵发誓！这家伙绝对是哪里出问题了...？"

# game/act2.rpy:62
translate schinese act2_63df6f82:

    # main "- Gah, I don’t have time for this. I’m late."
    main "——啊，我没时间跟你寒暄了，我已经迟到了。"

# game/act2.rpy:64
translate schinese act2_1365226b:

    # ben "Late? For what, exactly?"
    ben "迟到？你要去干什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:65
translate schinese act2_90ca97e3:

    # main "Training, or something. I dunno, just leave me alone!"
    main "训练什么的...我也不知道，总之我得先过去！"

# game/act2.rpy:66
translate schinese act2_68c905e0:

    # "I start walking away when Benjie suddenly stops me in my tracks."
    "在我正要离开时，Benjie突然拦住了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:68
translate schinese act2_b1601eca:

    # ben "Training? From who, Oswald?"
    ben "训练？谁指导你？是Oswald吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:69
translate schinese act2_61a8de6a:

    # main "Who else?"
    main "除了他还有谁？"

# game/act2.rpy:70
translate schinese act2_44bb48c9:

    # "Benjie doesn’t bother to stifle his chuckle anymore. He instead grasps my shoulder, causing my entire being to flinch."
    "Benjie终于还是没忍住，放声大笑了出来。他抓住了我的肩膀，让我整个心都突然咯噔了一下。"

# game/act2.rpy:72
translate schinese act2_1dbab85e:

    # ben "Well, before you go and make a fool of yourself, I have to mention that Oswald isn’t going to be here for the majority of the day. He has work today."
    ben "好吧，在你闹出笑话之前，我得提醒你一下，Oswald今天大部分时间都不会在这里。他还有其他工作要做。"

# game/act2.rpy:73
translate schinese act2_cff6c462:

    # main "W-What? What work?"
    main "什——什么？那是什么工作？"

# game/act2.rpy:75
translate schinese act2_dbdd5702:

    # ben "Oh, I dunno. The bar? They have alternating work days."
    ben "噢，我不知道。也许是酒吧？他们的工作是轮班制的。"

# game/act2.rpy:76
translate schinese act2_c66c8897:

    # main "Hmph. I don’t like what that insinuates."
    main "唔...我并不这么认为。"

# game/act2.rpy:78
translate schinese act2_e308c23b:

    # ben "Well, if you don’t believe me. You can ask him on the way. Oh and..."
    ben "好吧，如果你不信我，尽管问他便是了。噢，另外..."

# game/act2.rpy:83
translate schinese act2_9a6d3eb2:

    # "Benjie makes audible sniffing noises before continuing."
    "我还没有意识到发生什么，只听到了Benjie嗅探的声音。"

# game/act2.rpy:84
translate schinese act2_8e320f65:

    # "Wait…"
    "等等..."

# game/act2.rpy:85
translate schinese act2_c787e919:

    # "Did he just sniff me?!"
    "他刚才是在闻我身上的味道吗？！"

# game/act2.rpy:87
translate schinese act2_62661739:

    # ben "You need a shower. When was the last time you cleaned yourself?"
    ben "你需要洗个澡。话说你上次洗澡是在什么时候？"

# game/act2.rpy:88
translate schinese act2_1c460268:

    # main "I- well… 2 days ago?"
    main "我——呃...两天前？"

# game/act2.rpy:91
translate schinese act2_0c5b04d4:

    # ben "Unacceptable. Come with me, the showers are this way."
    ben "难以置信。跟我来，我告诉你浴室在哪里。"

# game/act2.rpy:93
translate schinese act2_acdae26a:

    # "Benjie begins to pace away from me. I take a moment to sniff myself and…"
    "在Benjie朝着浴室行走的途中，我快速地闻了闻自己身上的气味，然后..."

# game/act2.rpy:94
translate schinese act2_7c81ff30:

    # "Oh jeez, I really do need a bath. I hesitantly follow the raccoon, covering any of my… {i}stinky{/i} parts on the way there."
    "噢，草，我得赶紧洗个澡。我跟在浣熊身后，用上衣紧裹着自己...{i}发臭的{/i}身体，并与他保持着一定距离。"

# game/act2.rpy:99
translate schinese act2_238e31b1:

    # "We reach the entrance to the showers shortly, the faint trickling of pouring water echoes across the walls. Seems like some people are already in…"
    "我们很快就到达了浴室的入口，里面水流溅落的回声在墙壁四周回荡着，听起来好像已经有人在里面了..."

# game/act2.rpy:100
translate schinese act2_f278ad3c:

    # "Best be quick about the rinse, then. I don’t want to encounter anyone in their birthday suit, after all..."
    "我最好尽快把自己冲洗干净，毕竟我可不想撞见任何一个一丝不挂的人..."

# game/act2.rpy:102
translate schinese act2_2113858f:

    # ben "You can throw your clothes in the hamper over there. Towels are over there, and anything you might need for the shower should be inside the stall."
    ben "你可以把衣服扔到那边的篮子里，毛巾在这边，每个隔间里都放着你可能会用到的沐浴用品。"

# game/act2.rpy:103
translate schinese act2_7d41e814:

    # main "Thanks..."
    main "谢谢..."

# game/act2.rpy:106
translate schinese act2_9159df36:

    # "He immediately leaves me to do my dirty work, literally… and I intend to be quick about it."
    "他在说完以后立刻离开了浴室...我得尽快把我自己发臭的身体清洗干净才行。"

# game/act2.rpy:107
translate schinese act2_ea9f8276:

    # "I hastily disrobe and take a towel to cover my unmentionables, quickly pacing through each stall, looking for an empty one."
    "我快速地脱下了衣服，用毛巾遮住了我的那个地方，并在众多隔间中寻找一个空余的。"

# game/act2.rpy:108
translate schinese act2_d6acaf4e:

    # "Two of the stalls at the front seem to be occupied already, so I decide to just take the one next to it. As I get ready to go in, though, someone exits the stall directly next to me."
    "最前面的两个隔间好像已经有人了，所以我决定去旁边的那个。正当我准备走进的时候，有人正好从我一旁的隔间里走了出来。"

# game/act2.rpy:109
translate schinese act2_b57d1ac9:

    # main "W-Wait…"
    main "等——等一下..."

# game/act2.rpy:110
translate schinese act2_66d736b5:

    # "A wet, dripping, and bulky wolf emerges from the shower’s mist without a towel to cover his… whatsits."
    "一只浑身湿漉漉、毛发还在滴水的高大红狼从隔间的雾气中冒了出来，甚至没有用毛巾遮住他的...那个部位。"

# game/act2.rpy:112
translate schinese act2_7e04b2d7:

    # osw "Ahhh… that felt nice… now where’s that towe-"
    osw "啊...爽啊...毛巾...我刚才放到哪——"

# game/act2.rpy:114
translate schinese act2_2bcee43b:

    # "Oswald and I lock gazes, both of us pausing to process what it is that we’re currently witnessing. When it finally sinks in, our faces immediately turn red."
    "Oswald和我同时愣在了原地，盯着对方看了好一会儿，突然意识到两人早已满脸通红。"

# game/act2.rpy:117
translate schinese act2_9e099e32:

    # osw "G-Gah! D-D-Don’t look!"
    osw "呃-啊——！别——别看过来！"

# game/act2.rpy:118
translate schinese act2_35fd9ad5:

    # "The wolf stammers as he hastily covers up his nether regions and his arm. My legs suddenly feel like jelly and I’m unable to move anywhere, let alone shimmy towards the stalls."
    "狼结结巴巴地向后退去，急忙用手臂遮住自己的下体。但我的腿突然软的像果冻一样，哪儿也去不了，更不用说朝着隔间里移动了。"

# game/act2.rpy:119
translate schinese act2_1f7f838a:

    # "That raccoon… He must’ve known this would happen… ugh, fuck me… wait..."
    "那只浣熊...他一定是算计好了会发生这种事...呃-淦...等等..."

# game/act2.rpy:120
translate schinese act2_48bf95b7:

    # osw "W-What are you standing there for?! Get in!"
    osw "你-那你站在那里干什么？！快进去啊！"

# game/act2.rpy:121
translate schinese act2_18b8090e:

    # main "I-I-I… I c-can’t…"
    main "我—我—我—我办不到..."

# game/act2.rpy:125
translate schinese act2_7e8ac5b7:

    # "Then, just as I’m thinking that things couldn’t get any worse, another pair of wet footsteps walk out of the other occupied stall."
    "就在这时，又有另一个声音从第一个隔间里走了出来，没有什么比现在更糟了。"

# game/act2.rpy:127
translate schinese act2_b8cc5693:

    # mx "Yo, Oz, you said you needed-"
    mx "喂，Oz，你说过你需要先找——"

# game/act2.rpy:129
translate schinese act2_5d0f4bae:

    # "Oh, just kill me already…!"
    "算了，赶快杀了我吧...！"

# game/act2.rpy:131
translate schinese act2_5d7cdfc9:

    # mx "{i}Get. In. The. Stall.{/i}"
    mx "{i}立 刻 滚 到 里 面 去。{/i}"

# game/act2.rpy:133
translate schinese act2_a7728785:

    # main "Y-Yes Sir!"
    main "遵-遵命！"

# game/act2.rpy:135
translate schinese act2_3d2e5761:

    # "My body immediately reacts and I quickly place myself inside the stall, finally feeling like I was starting to calm down."
    "我的身体立刻回应起来，连忙把自己关进了隔间里，终于可以冷静下来了。"

# game/act2.rpy:136
translate schinese act2_06ec8828:

    # "Man what an absolute disaster… as if I didn’t need to make things any more awkward between me and that hot-headed tiger!"
    "我的天，这真是一场灾难级别的相遇...这估计是我和那只脾气暴躁的老虎之间发生的最为尴尬的一件事了！"

# game/act2.rpy:137
translate schinese act2_602e9575:

    # "Not to mention any more hostile… I can still hear them talking outside, it’s muffled though."
    "更不用说之后他对我的敌视会有多么强烈...虽然声音很小，但我仍然能听到他们在外面说话的声音。"

# game/act2.rpy:138
translate schinese act2_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "..."

# game/act2.rpy:139
translate schinese act2_161cba7a:

    # "Alright, I think I’ve calmed down enough. Time to do the one thing I came here for…"
    "好吧，我想我已经足够冷静了。是时候实现我来这里的真正目的了..."

# game/act2.rpy:141
translate schinese act2_e2011e25:

    # "I place my towel on the metal rack then turn the center knob slowly. The shower begins flowing with a soft trickle of water."
    "我将毛巾放在金属架上，然后慢慢转动中心旋钮。淋浴开始伴随着柔和水声浸湿我的毛发。"

# game/act2.rpy:142
translate schinese act2_114196b8:

    # main "Hmm… this way?"
    main "嗯...这边是？"

# game/act2.rpy:143
translate schinese act2_daa8fa59:

    # "I turn the right knob more, the water then becomes hotter and falls harder, with steam beginning to form."
    "我把旋钮朝着右边转动，水温开始变得更热，更加用力地冲刷着我，蒸汽也开始缓缓弥漫起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:144
translate schinese act2_375f4a56:

    # main "Nope! Too hot, too hot!"
    main "噢！不行！太热了，太热了！"

# game/act2.rpy:145
translate schinese act2_da49aef8:

    # "I hurriedly turn the right knob back, then begin turning the left knob, the heat then suddenly turns into a chilling flow."
    "我赶紧把旋钮朝反方向转动，热气瞬间化为一股寒流。"

# game/act2.rpy:146
translate schinese act2_4110e333:

    # main "G-Gah! Cold shock…"
    main "呜-呃啊！好冷..."

# game/act2.rpy:147
translate schinese act2_893d83d4:

    # "I continue to experiment with the water temperature, wanting to get it just right."
    "我继续调试水温，想让它恰到好处。"

# game/act2.rpy:148
translate schinese act2_625967e8:

    # "After finding the perfect temperature, I proceed to rinse the rest of my body while letting my eyes wander to see where the shampoo is."
    "在找到了合适的温度之后，我接着冲洗身体的其他部分，同时环视四周寻找着洗发水的位置。"

# game/act2.rpy:149
translate schinese act2_29c0f4fd:

    # "After finally finding the rather small-sized bottle on a metal rack, I pick it up and check how much of its contents is left. It’s already half-empty."
    "终于，我在金属架上找到了一个相当小的瓶子。当我拿起它的时候，发现里面已经是半空的了。"

# game/act2.rpy:150
translate schinese act2_d95643b5:

    # "I guess someone else would tell me that it’s also half-full, but then again, it’s not gonna get me any more shampoo."
    "我想别人会跟我说，这是半满而非半空，注重拥有的而不是哀叹只剩下这些。但是话又说回来了，这样除了改变自己的心态也不能让洗发液多起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:151
translate schinese act2_84dcf213:

    # "I squeeze the bluish-white liquid as hard as I can, squirting it onto my palm in a satisfying swirl."
    "我用力的从小瓶中挤出洗发液，将其涂抹在掌心，拉出一个令人愉悦的泡沫旋。"

# game/act2.rpy:154
translate schinese act2_a98161dd:

    # "After pouring out enough for my whole body, I put the bottle back down, turn the water off, then proceed to lather myself."
    "待得我全往身上倒上足够多的洗发液后，我将瓶子放回原处，关掉水，将洗发液搓出泡沫。"

# game/act2.rpy:155
translate schinese act2_ac2c9e09:

    # "I try to work my way around the bandaged ear when I get there."
    "在这一过程中我尽可能地避开自己缠绕着绷带的耳朵。"

# game/act2.rpy:158
translate schinese act2_cda64557:

    # "After everything seems covered, I turn the water back on and rinse myself thoroughly from the tip of my ears to the tip of my toes."
    "在全身都被泡沫覆盖之后，我重新打开淋浴，从耳朵到脚趾把自己彻底冲洗了个干净。"

# game/act2.rpy:159
translate schinese act2_89b02e1b:

    # "Good thing the bandage is hydrophobic, otherwise that would have posed some problems."
    "还好绷带的材质是疏水的，否则很有可能会造成感染。"

# game/act2.rpy:160
translate schinese act2_5b24d89c:

    # main "There we go..."
    main "终于洗好了..."

# game/act2.rpy:162
translate schinese act2_dfa3996b:

    # "After closing the shower, I look for the air dryer button out of instinct. My old apartment had it, and it was always a big help in drying off my fur instead of with just a towel afterward."
    "关闭淋浴后，我本能地四处寻找空气干燥器的按钮。我的旧公寓里安装着这个东西，它可以替代毛巾擦拭，方便用来烘干自己的身体。"

# game/act2.rpy:164
translate schinese act2_819407bc:

    # "To my disappointment, this stall didn’t have any. I sigh in resignation. I miss my old apartment already…"
    "令人失望的是，这个隔间内并没有安装类似的东西。我无奈地叹了口气，开始想念起自己的旧公寓了..."

# game/act2.rpy:165
translate schinese act2_e77b482c:

    # main "Why did this even have to happen…?"
    main "到底是为什么会发生这样的事..."

# game/act2.rpy:167
translate schinese act2_307e6484:

    # "I wrap the towel around my waist, expecting my clothes to be where I left them. Instead, they’re nowhere to be seen."
    "在我把毛巾裹在腰上，去找我扔在篮子里的衣服时，却发现那里空空如也。"

# game/act2.rpy:168
translate schinese act2_8843b601:

    # main "W-Where are my…?"
    main "我的衣服跑哪去——？"

# game/act2.rpy:169
translate schinese act2_361f84c7:

    # osw "Psst."
    osw "嘿。"

# game/act2.rpy:170
translate schinese act2_e8a911de:

    # main "H-Huh?"
    main "嗯？"

# game/act2.rpy:172
translate schinese act2_ef2e551a:

    # "To my surprise, Oswald is still here with a towel now wrapped around his waist hiding all of his… manly glory."
    "我惊讶地发现Oswald居然还留在浴室里，只不过此时，他的腰上缠着一个毛巾...盖住了他的..."

# game/act2.rpy:173
translate schinese act2_a0d60226:

    # "There seems to be some sort of… holo-tattoo on his left arm? I’m surprised he has one… and so big, too."
    "他的左臂上似乎有着某种...全息文身？而且看起来面积非常大。"

# game/act2.rpy:174
translate schinese act2_d6ba63c5:

    # "I was fully expecting him to be long gone at this point. He doesn’t seem to be embarrassed anymore. Instead, he’s sporting his usual demeanor."
    "我本以为他早就离开浴室了。不过，现在的他看起来已经没有那么尴尬了，反而表现出自己平时一贯的举止。"

# game/act2.rpy:176
translate schinese act2_d65271f2:

    # osw "Are you ok? I hope what you… saw, didn’t…"
    osw "你还好吗？我希望你没有...看到些..."

# game/act2.rpy:177
translate schinese act2_f7e82c35:

    # main "It’s fine, Oswald. Let’s just… forget it ever happened, ok?"
    main "没事的，Oswald。让我们把刚才发生的事忘了，好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:178
translate schinese act2_77636a65:

    # osw "[mc]..."
    osw "[mc]..."

# game/act2.rpy:179
translate schinese act2_969f414b:

    # "Oswald trails off a bit, but quickly recomposes himself."
    "Oswald的声音有点小，但很快就恢复了平时的音量。"

# game/act2.rpy:181
translate schinese act2_6b33c613:

    # osw "O-ok. Maybe that’s for the best…"
    osw "好——好吧，也许这样最好..."

# game/act2.rpy:183
translate schinese act2_2aaeeb72:

    # "Oswald sighs before moving towards the exit."
    "Oswald在走出大门前叹了口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:185
translate schinese act2_d76ffd0c:

    # osw "Your clothes are over there. I’ll see you later, [mc]."
    osw "你的衣服放在那边。[mc]，我们待会儿见。"

# game/act2.rpy:186
translate schinese act2_37a6e902:

    # main "W-Wait!"
    main "等等！"

# game/act2.rpy:187
translate schinese act2_7e36dd76:

    # "Oswald looks at me expectantly, pulling his puppy eyes on me."
    "Oswald用他那像是狗勾般的眼神期待地看着我。"

# game/act2.rpy:188
translate schinese act2_9da93a82:

    # main "Oswald… I just wanted to ask…"
    main "Oswald...我只是想问..."

# game/act2.rpy:190
translate schinese act2_7dcd2c80:

    # osw "Yeah?"
    osw "诶？"

# game/act2.rpy:191
translate schinese act2_4ceea966:

    # main "When… are you gonna be training me?"
    main "你什么时候...开始训练我？"

# game/act2.rpy:192
translate schinese act2_b782bbbc:

    # "I ask, wanting to confirm what Benjie said earlier."
    "我想确认之前Benjie所说的话。"

# game/act2.rpy:194
translate schinese act2_107a1e55:

    # osw "O-Oh. I’m actually not the one doing that today."
    osw "噢——噢，实际上，今天要训练你的人不是我。"

# game/act2.rpy:195
translate schinese act2_67ad4841:

    # main "W-Wait… then who’s gonna do it?"
    main "等等...那是由谁来做这种事？"

# game/act2.rpy:197
translate schinese act2_439b9ff0:

    # osw "Benjie will. I have to work at the bar today, so just… try to have more patience with him, ok? Trust me, it’ll be worth it."
    osw "Benjie会的。我今天必须要在酒吧里工作，所以...试着对他多一点耐心，好吗？相信我，这绝对是值得的。"

# game/act2.rpy:199
translate schinese act2_0e66861b:

    # "A pit in my stomach forms just thinking about spending more time with Benjie, but I guess I really have no say in it."
    "听到我马上要去和Benjie两人单独相处很长一段时间，我的心里就感觉到一阵酸楚，但这真的不是我能决定的。"

# game/act2.rpy:200
translate schinese act2_f514fae2:

    # main "Alright… I-If you say so…"
    main "好吧...如果连你都这么说的话..."

# game/act2.rpy:204
translate schinese act2_7be48a12:

    # "Oswald nods to me before leaving towards the hallway. I simply sigh as I check the clothes that Oswald left for me."
    "Oswald向我点了点头，然后走向了走廊。我叹了口气，检查Oswald指给我的衣服。"

# game/act2.rpy:205
translate schinese act2_4f49ca2b:

    # main "Hmm… let’s see here…"
    main "嗯...随机应变吧..."

# game/act2.rpy:206
translate schinese act2_915202b9:

    # "The clothes are neatly folded with a note on top of it."
    "衣服叠得整整齐齐，只不过上面放着一张纸条。"

# game/act2.rpy:207
translate schinese act2_2694f6f5:

    # main "What’s this… ‘Meet me in the training room. -B’."
    main "这是什么...‘我在训练室等你。——B’。"

# game/act2.rpy:208
translate schinese act2_96f0c07d:

    # main "Oh great."
    main "哦，好吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:209
translate schinese act2_03ec4cf6:

    # "I dry myself off with a towel, just enough to wear the clothes without getting them damp. I put on said clothes begrudgingly, knowing these came from Benjie."
    "我用毛巾尽可能擦干自己的身体，确保穿上衣服以后不会让它们受潮。不过我还是有些不情愿地穿上了衣服，因为我知道这些衣服实际上是Benjie留给我的。"

# game/act2.rpy:210
translate schinese act2_57fdc4f7:

    # "To my surprise, they’re actually a perfect fit. I wonder how the raccoon pulled that off…?"
    "但令人惊讶的是，它们穿起来真的非常合身。我不清楚那只浣熊是如何做到的...？"

# game/act2.rpy:211
translate schinese act2_246e5d25:

    # main "Welp. Time to get this over with…"
    main "不管怎样，该去训练室了...."

# game/act2.rpy:216
translate schinese act2_dca73225:

    # "After finishing {i}that{/i} whole fiasco, I try to recompose myself before showing my face to Benjie. I bet he planned for me to see their... {i}manly parts…{/i}"
    "在经历了几次和Benjie{i}那样{/i}的尴尬场面之后，我需要在面对他之前，先调整好自己的状态。至少我敢打赌，刚才看到Oswald和Max{i}雄气满满{/i}的场面，绝对是他精心计划好的。"

# game/act2.rpy:217
translate schinese act2_437c2ef4:

    # "At this point, I don’t even know how he wants to end me. I’m debating which one’s better, though: the bullet, or by my own heat?"
    "此时，我甚至考虑不出他还能有什么方法可以让我难堪。我也开始怀疑，到底是子弹擦伤耳朵这件事更好，还是看到Oswald的裸体害羞到满脸通红更好。"

# game/act2.rpy:218
translate schinese act2_bb402ae7:

    # "Alright, calm down [mc]. I’m supposed to look {i}decent{/i}, not at all flustered. That’ll probably just give him the satisfaction he wants."
    "好吧，[mc]，先让自己冷静下来。我应该尽可能让自己看起来{i}体面{/i}一些，只有表现得处事不惊，才不会任由他摆布。"

# game/act2.rpy:222
translate schinese act2_c7741baa:

    # "I take one deep breath before turning towards the training room where I see the raccoon standing at the shooting range. He isn’t stationary on one of the rows, however."
    "我深吸了一口气，走进了训练室，看到Benjie此时正举着枪站在射击场上，不过他面前的靶子并不是静止不动的。"

# game/act2.rpy:223
translate schinese act2_a870b545:

    # "He’s strafing from left to right, shooting vigorously at each target. It’s quite impressive, even more impressive than how accurate Oswald was yesterday."
    "浣熊从左到右进行扫射，精准地命中每一个目标。这甚至比昨天Oswald射击的场面还要让人印象深刻。"

# game/act2.rpy:224
translate schinese act2_5ece4298:

    # main "Hey, Benjie..."
    main "嗨，Benjie..."

# game/act2.rpy:226
translate schinese act2_cee9cbbf:

    # "No answer. He just gives a glance my way before shooting one more round through the rows. I sit down on one of the benches and proceed to just observe him silently."
    "他没有回答，只是瞥了我一眼，然后进行又一轮的射击。我在其中一张长椅上坐下，静静地注视着他。"

# game/act2.rpy:227
translate schinese act2_c95e2548:

    # "To my surprise, even with how fast and loose he’s being, all of the rows are pinging bullseye!"
    "他的动作是那么迅速、神态也似乎漫不经心。但令人惊讶的是，每一发子弹都精准地命中了移动目标的靶心。"

# game/act2.rpy:228
translate schinese act2_a540c707:

    # "I’m left dumbfounded at how much skill that has to take, let alone how much brain power that has to consume."
    "我对他卓越的技能感到目瞪口呆，更不用说想达到这样的精准度，要花费多么大的功夫。"

# game/act2.rpy:229
translate schinese act2_74acb22a:

    # "It’s starting to make {i}my{/i} head hurt, but I quickly snap back to reality when Benjie looks my way."
    "这让{i}我{/i}的脑袋开始疼起来了，但是当Benjie转身看向我时，我很快就回到了现实。"

# game/act2.rpy:231
translate schinese act2_88019136:

    # ben "Your turn."
    ben "轮到你了。"

# game/act2.rpy:232
translate schinese act2_84abc78e:

    # main "W-What?"
    main "什-什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:234
translate schinese act2_ea004566:

    # ben "I’m not going to have to drag you all the way here, am I?"
    ben "你来这儿可不是为了看我表演，不是吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:235
translate schinese act2_edb0e6cb:

    # main "...Oh! R-Right, sorry."
    main "...噢！好-好的，对不起。"

# game/act2.rpy:236
translate schinese act2_fa0fe3fb:

    # "I stand up and quickly position myself as Benjie grabs a pistol from the row in front of me. He hands it to me after I’ve properly positioned myself."
    "我起身站到正确的位置上，Benjie从我面前的那排手枪中抓起一把，然后把它交给了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:237
translate schinese act2_9ed71259:

    # "I look at it rather hesitantly; I never thought I’d ever have the need to handle firearms in my entire life. I look to Benjie, who’s giving me a rather judgmental look."
    "我犹豫地看着手中的这把枪，在此之前，我从没想过这辈子会用到这种东西。我看着Benjie，他正在用一种相当挑剔的眼神看着我。"

# game/act2.rpy:239
translate schinese act2_da7bdc17:

    # ben "[mc]..."
    ben "[mc]..."

# game/act2.rpy:240
translate schinese act2_f82e0873:

    # main "Yes?"
    main "怎么了？"

# game/act2.rpy:241
translate schinese act2_80574604:

    # ben "Have you ever handled a gun before?"
    ben "你以前接触过枪吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:242
translate schinese act2_14dd72d8:

    # main "N-No..."
    main "没-没有..."

# game/act2.rpy:243
translate schinese act2_fd9aa36d:

    # "Benjie strokes his chin, thinking of something."
    "Benjie摸了摸下巴，似乎在思考着什么。"

# game/act2.rpy:245
translate schinese act2_d6c3e371:

    # ben "Hmmm… alright."
    ben "嗯...好吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:246
translate schinese act2_ac249c03:

    # "Benjie looks at me intently, removing his hand from his jacket’s pockets. He sluggishly points towards the gun, creating a circling motion afterwards."
    "Benjie专注地看向我，把手从外套的口袋里抽了出来，不紧不慢地指了指枪，然后用手指转了转圈。"

# game/act2.rpy:248
translate schinese act2_1481a7a5:

    # ben "First of all, get your finger off the trigger. You might accidentally pop someone’s eye out."
    ben "首先，把你的手指从扳机上拿开。你可能会不小心把别人的眼睛弄瞎。"

# game/act2.rpy:249
translate schinese act2_08cfe9e0:

    # "I look at my hand and quickly fumble to place my index finger somewhere else, almost dropping the gun in the process."
    "我看着自己的手，迅速意识到食指放置的位置，在这个过程中差一点把枪丢在了地上。"

# game/act2.rpy:251
translate schinese act2_1f05b7a9:

    # ben "W-Wha--?! Just, plant it on the barrel!"
    ben "你-你在干什么——？！先用另一只手支撑在一侧的枪管上！"

# game/act2.rpy:252
translate schinese act2_23d31693:

    # main "The… barrel?"
    main "哪个...桶？\n{i}{size=-10}*译注：barrel既有‘枪管’的意思，也有‘桶’的意思{/size}{/i}"

# game/act2.rpy:253
translate schinese act2_9d750119:

    # ben "That long thing where the bullets get shot out of."
    ben "我说的是用来射出子弹的那个长管子。"

# game/act2.rpy:255
translate schinese act2_d113719e:

    # "I do as I’m told, placing my finger on the ‘barrel’. Huh, so that’s what it’s called... I could hear Benjie sigh under his breath."
    "我按照他所说的去做，把手指扶在“桶”上。咦，原来枪管是这个单词吗... 一旁的Benjie开始默默地叹气。"

# game/act2.rpy:257
translate schinese act2_878bc4e9:

    # ben "Right... Next thing."
    ben "好了...接下来。"

# game/act2.rpy:260
translate schinese act2_78ae517f:

    # "I continue to observe the gun when I hear a muffled ‘thump’ onto one of the benches."
    "在我继续观察手上的枪支时，听到有什么东西落在长椅上的声音。"

# game/act2.rpy:262
translate schinese act2_7af02dc3:

    # "I glance in the direction of the sound, only to see Benjie standing there without his jacket on."
    "我顺着声音的方向望了一眼，看到Benjie将他的外套脱在了椅子上。"

# game/act2.rpy:263
translate schinese act2_7b5fc68a:

    # "Underneath is… a tank top? Ok... He looks… a lot leaner without it."
    "下面穿着的是...背心？好吧，看起来...他在脱掉了外套后显得更加高瘦了。"

# game/act2.rpy:264
translate schinese act2_66a059fc:

    # "Eh, I suppose that comes with being a thief. But still, he’s quite well-built; I can see some semblance of muscle on his arms."
    "呃，我想这也许和他曾经身为小偷有关。不过，仔细观察后发现，他的身体还是相当健壮的，手臂上依然有着很明显的肌肉线条。"

# game/act2.rpy:267
translate schinese act2_9bc5a927:

    # ben "Uh… [mc]? You’re um… drooling…"
    ben "呃...[mc]？你这是在...流口水吗...？"

# game/act2.rpy:268
translate schinese act2_d7fc2ba6:

    # main "H-Huh?!"
    main "诶？！"

# game/act2.rpy:269
translate schinese act2_859cc7bd:

    # "I wipe my muzzle off quickly to see if I am indeed slobbering. God, I thought I already grew past my dog slobber phase in high school…!"
    "我赶紧擦了擦自己的嘴角，看看自己是不是真的在流口水。我的天，我以为自己早就过了青春期会流口水的阶段了...！"

# game/act2.rpy:270
translate schinese act2_fa4318cd:

    # ben "Ooook… You’re quite weird, [mc]."
    ben "好——吧...[mc]，你真是个怪人。"

# game/act2.rpy:271
translate schinese act2_c13d0f9e:

    # main "O-Oh… I am?"
    main "啊-哦...我是这样的吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:273
translate schinese act2_3dc54993:

    # ben "Yes. But in a good way, of course. Shelve those puppy eyes for now, it’s the lifeblood of this group, after all."
    ben "是的，但这也并不是什么坏事。总之，先收起你卖萌的眼神，毕竟我们现在的训练可是和这个组织的命脉挂钩的。"

# game/act2.rpy:275
translate schinese act2_f1fefe1d:

    # "Benjie then moves closer and positions himself behind me, seeming like he’s observing every possible angle of my entire being."
    "Benjie向我身边凑近，站在我身后观察着我的每一个角度。"

# game/act2.rpy:276
translate schinese act2_9eb36d6d:

    # "It was a little off-putting like I’m being inspected for doing something wrong."
    "这种感觉令人有些反感，就像是我做错了什么事而接受检查一样。"

# game/act2.rpy:277
translate schinese act2_593f2835:

    # ben "Alright… Now for your shooting form."
    ben "好...接下来是你的射击姿势。"

# game/act2.rpy:278
translate schinese act2_64df4de5:

    # main "G-Got it… how do I do that."
    main "好-好的...我该怎么做。"

# game/act2.rpy:279
translate schinese act2_2a915019:

    # ben "Before that..."
    ben "在那之前..."

# game/act2.rpy:280
translate schinese act2_2eca7503:

    # "Benjie clears his throat."
    "Benjie清了清嗓子。"

# game/act2.rpy:282
translate schinese act2_4377052d:

    # ben "...How was the shower?"
    ben "...你觉得刚才的淋浴怎么样？"

# game/act2.rpy:283
translate schinese act2_ce8a2798:

    # "I almost immediately choke on my own saliva and tense up. I start feeling flushed as blood rushes up to my head, making me sweat profusely."
    "我立刻被自己的口水呛到，血液快速地涌上了面颊，紧张地脸红了起来，甚至连汗水都止不住地渗了出来。"

# game/act2.rpy:284
translate schinese act2_ce3a87b6:

    # "Oh geez, I bet I’m tomato-red under all my fur right now. I then begin to feel my entire being shriveling up from embarrassment."
    "噢，我的天，我现在整张脸一定红的像番茄一样，并且因为极度地尴尬，身体也开始渐渐缩成了一团。"

# game/act2.rpy:285
translate schinese act2_432a90fb:

    # "Suddenly, a pair of hands firmly grasp my hips, holding me still."
    "突然，一双手紧紧地抓住了我的髋部，将我固定在原地。"

# game/act2.rpy:286
translate schinese act2_c1df83b9:

    # ben "This stiff and tense feeling. Don’t forget it when you get ready to shoot."
    ben "记住现在这种紧张和僵硬的感觉，在你准备射击时要好好保持住这种状态。"

# game/act2.rpy:287
translate schinese act2_0c45f312:

    # "Benjie lets go of my hips after a few moments, then begins trailing his hands onto my shoulders."
    "片刻之后，Benjie松开了我的髋部，然后把手搭在了我的肩膀上。"

# game/act2.rpy:289
translate schinese act2_b37e04f6:

    # ben "Keep these as relaxed as you can, though. Now, raise the gun and aim at the target."
    ben "另外尽管身体要保持紧张，但是在此前提下也要学着尽可能地放松。现在，把枪举起来瞄准目标。"

# game/act2.rpy:290
translate schinese act2_fa21913c:

    # "I expect Benjie to let go of my shoulders as I raise the gun, but he doesn’t; quite the opposite, actually."
    "我希望Benjie可以在我举枪的时候松开我的肩膀，但他并没有，反倒与我想的正好相反。"

# game/act2.rpy:291
translate schinese act2_b55bfb57:

    # "The more I raise my arms, the more he presses down on my shoulders, making my entire arm feel weird and weak."
    "我越是举起手臂，他就越是用力压在我的肩膀上，这让我的整条手臂都感觉到奇怪和无力。"

# game/act2.rpy:292
translate schinese act2_4cfd99a2:

    # main "...L-Like this?"
    main "...要像...现在这样吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:293
translate schinese act2_bb8190a9:

    # ben "You’re naturally tensing up. Of course, it’s to be expected, but…"
    ben "你总是会自然而然地紧张起来。当然，这在意料之中，但是..."

# game/act2.rpy:294
translate schinese act2_6d20cce5:

    # "He quickly moves to my side before lightly smacking my back."
    "他迅速走到我身边，然后轻轻拍打着我的背。"

# game/act2.rpy:295
translate schinese act2_258daebd:

    # ben "Proper posture. You aren’t a hunchback, so you have no excuse pressuring your diaphragm."
    ben "姿势还是不对。你不是驼背，所以没有必要刻意去压迫你的隔膜肌。"

# game/act2.rpy:297
translate schinese act2_d450b76e:

    # "Benjie then moves in front of me, avoiding the path of the gunshot. He adjusts my arms further then places a hand on my chest."
    "Benjie避开枪口的路径，移动到我的面前。他进一步调整我手臂的位置，然后将一只手抵在我的胸前。"

# game/act2.rpy:298
translate schinese act2_251c305b:

    # ben "It’s a lot easier to shoot when you’re breathing steady. Try it."
    ben "当你呼吸平稳的时候，射击会变得容易很多。试试看吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:299
translate schinese act2_d802667d:

    # "I do as he says, breathing in and out slowly. It becomes a lot more smooth the more I do it and it feels rather relieving, making the remaining tension from my shoulders abate a bit."
    "我照着他说的去做，试着慢慢调整呼吸。渐渐地，我感觉自己变得越来越放松，肩膀上的紧绷感也减弱了很多。"

# game/act2.rpy:300
translate schinese act2_c669699f:

    # ben "See? You get it."
    ben "看到了吗？你还是能够理解的。"

# game/act2.rpy:301
translate schinese act2_473f76e9:

    # main "Y-yeah, sort of."
    main "算是...有点吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:302
translate schinese act2_02cc11d4:

    # ben "Good, next."
    ben "好，那接下来。"

# game/act2.rpy:303
translate schinese act2_1cebcfd9:

    # "Benjie moves behind me again."
    "Benjie又回到了我的身后。"

# game/act2.rpy:306
translate schinese act2_d6a3aa90:

    # "Then, out of nowhere, he smacks my butt."
    "突然，他举起手打在了我的屁股上。"

# game/act2.rpy:307
translate schinese act2_22b2f760:

    # main "W-What the hell?!"
    main "你——你在干什么？！"

# game/act2.rpy:308
translate schinese act2_d77878de:

    # ben "Spread the legs a bit more. Keep ‘em balanced, else you’ll topple over with bigger guns."
    ben "把腿稍微张开点，然后保持好平衡，不然你会被枪的后坐力推翻的。"

# game/act2.rpy:309
translate schinese act2_31a0976f:

    # main "O-Oh! {i}You um... didn’t really have to smack my ass though…{/i}"
    main "嗷——好啊！{i}但是...你真的没必要打我的屁股...{/i}"

# game/act2.rpy:310
translate schinese act2_6233c3d3:

    # "I trail off while looking directly at Benjie’s straight, emotionless face. He doesn’t seem to be kidding around with that."
    "我直视着Benjie，他带着毫无表情的脸走到了一旁，看上去似乎并不是在开玩笑。"

# game/act2.rpy:312
translate schinese act2_d7b1acfb:

    # ben "Now, this isn’t going to make your aim better, but it’s going to put as many odds into letting you line up your shots easier."
    ben "好了，在你做好这一切准备之后，虽然你要打的靶子并没有什么变化，但这会使你更容易去观察并稳定地瞄准靶心。"

# game/act2.rpy:313
translate schinese act2_f8aa542c:

    # ben "Shooting with accuracy is a skill that takes time, like all things, but utilizing these principles can weigh the gunfight more in your favor. Got it?"
    ben "就向你学习其他东西一样，精准射击也是一项需要时间去练习的技能。但是首先你必须要先掌握这些持枪和瞄准的基本原则，这样才会让你在枪战中处于有利位置。明白了吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:314
translate schinese act2_eaf8c386:

    # "I just nod as I gulp down from nervousness. I feel like I’m about to puke with how weird this pose feels."
    "我点点头，又因为紧张感而咽了咽口水。我觉得我快要吐了，现在的姿势要多难受有多难受。"

# game/act2.rpy:315
translate schinese act2_755323d8:

    # ben "Alright. Now, place your finger on the trigger, and try to control the upward force from the recoil."
    ben "好的。现在，把手指放在扳机上，并尝试身体适当前倾以减弱后坐力。"

# game/act2.rpy:316
translate schinese act2_24d40d5a:

    # "I half-heartedly do so, hesitating to pull the trigger. I can’t dawdle for long, though, especially with Benjie watching me so intently."
    "我心不在焉地按照他所说的去做，始终犹豫着要不要开枪。不过我知道自己不能磨蹭太久，因为Benjie一直在后面盯着我看。"

# game/act2.rpy:318
translate schinese act2_743d7151:

    # "I pull the trigger, and I hear a muffled shot escaping the barrel and a bit of recoil surging through my body."
    "我扣动扳机，伴随着枪管中的一声闷响，一阵明显的后坐力朝我的上肢袭来。"

# game/act2.rpy:319
translate schinese act2_49d11eff:

    # ben "Huh. Second base. Not bad for a first shot."
    ben "嗯，9环，作为初学者来说还不错。"

# game/act2.rpy:320
translate schinese act2_e0ab4576:

    # main "You… You can tell?"
    main "你...你能看得到吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:321
translate schinese act2_861c2ddd:

    # ben "Yep. Says right here."
    ben "当然，这里有显示。"

# game/act2.rpy:322
translate schinese act2_bd866658:

    # "He points towards the panel next to the row, displaying a hole on the circle, in between the smallest and second smallest circle."
    "他指向我所在这一行的一块显示面板，画面上清楚地显示出，在最小的圆和第二小的圆之间存在着一个小洞。"

# game/act2.rpy:323
translate schinese act2_ea89826f:

    # main "O-Oh… that’s where my shot went?"
    main "噢——这就是我射中的地方？"

# game/act2.rpy:324
translate schinese act2_79a19c59:

    # ben "Essentially."
    ben "可以这么说。"

# game/act2.rpy:325
translate schinese act2_c8e700ad:

    # "I immediately try to loosen up when Benjie grunts at me."
    "正当我准备放松的时候，Benjie突然提高了嗓门。"

# game/act2.rpy:328
translate schinese act2_d7f306f1:

    # ben "Hey! Who said you can relax?"
    ben "喂！谁说你现在就可以放松了？"

# game/act2.rpy:329
translate schinese act2_ad15e0df:

    # main "G-Gah! I thought we were done!"
    main "啊——呃！我以为已经结束了！"

# game/act2.rpy:330
translate schinese act2_c60130fc:

    # ben "Not until you empty that whole magazine, you aren’t! Now, get as close to the center as possible!"
    ben "除非你打光整盒子弹，不然不许休息！现在，尽可能击中靶心！"

# game/act2.rpy:331
translate schinese act2_fb771c38:

    # main "Y-Yes, Sir!"
    main "是-是的，遵命！"

# game/act2.rpy:332
translate schinese act2_8b21b6d5:

    # "Fuck, I said that out of instinct. I never knew Benjie could be this authoritarian… He never exuded that aura at all, as far as I’ve seen."
    "草，我出于本能说出了这种士兵般的回应。但我真的没有想到Benjie居然会像军官一样专制...根据我之前对他的了解，根本就想不出他居然能散发这样的气场。"

# game/act2.rpy:334
translate schinese act2_b2ef683f:

    # "I try to replicate the form Benjie taught me."
    "好吧，试着去重复一遍Benjie教给我的技巧。"

# game/act2.rpy:335
translate schinese act2_8e604d18:

    # "Legs spread: ok…"
    "双腿张开：好的..."

# game/act2.rpy:336
translate schinese act2_995817ae:

    # "Breathing: clear."
    "呼吸：调整完毕。"

# game/act2.rpy:337
translate schinese act2_9db32b2c:

    # "Shoulders: relaxed…"
    "肩膀：保持放松..."

# game/act2.rpy:338
translate schinese act2_5e5bc10e:

    # "Ok, now calm down…"
    "好，然后让自己冷静下来..."

# game/act2.rpy:340
translate schinese act2_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "..."

# game/act2.rpy:344
translate schinese act2_886e8d31:

    # "I manage to eventually empty the whole magazine, each shot taking me a few minutes to prepare before pulling the trigger, though."
    "虽然每次射击时我都需要先调整几分钟时间才能够扣动扳机，不过，最终我还是打完了一整盒的子弹。"

# game/act2.rpy:345
translate schinese act2_4953dbf9:

    # "I could see in my peripherals that Benjie was stifling a chuckle or two as he watched me, covering it up under his hand."
    "我在周围的设备中看到了Benjie正一边看着我，一边捂着嘴偷笑的表情。"

# game/act2.rpy:347
translate schinese act2_d0dc0a55:

    # ben "Alright… that’s enough, [mc]."
    ben "好了...[mc]，已经可以了。"

# game/act2.rpy:348
translate schinese act2_d8a906be:

    # main "T-Thank God..."
    main "谢天谢地..."

# game/act2.rpy:349
translate schinese act2_4afd74f0:

    # "I almost absentmindedly fling the gun back onto its previous position on the table, not even noticing how sweaty I’ve gotten. So much for that shower half an hour ago…"
    "我神志恍惚地把枪丢回到原来的位置，这才注意到我的身体已经被汗水浸透了。和我半小时前淋浴完以后有过之而无不及。"

# game/act2.rpy:351
translate schinese act2_f3217989:

    # ben "We’ll take a break for the rest of the day. We still have a week to go though, so we’ll have the opportunity to work on it some more."
    ben "今天剩下的时间可以先休息一下。距离我们任务开始还有一周的时间，所以明天你还会被安排其他的训练工作。"

# game/act2.rpy:352
translate schinese act2_324cc373:

    # main "Ehhhh…! Do we still have to do this tomorrow?!"
    main "\呃...！明天还要继续吗？！"

# game/act2.rpy:354
translate schinese act2_a318673b:

    # ben "Not like you have any other plans at the moment, no?"
    ben "除此之外，你难道还有别的安排吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:355
translate schinese act2_a9e1b6d1:

    # "I groan a bit more while sitting down almost feeling like I might melt onto the bench when I hear footsteps from the entrance."
    "我呻吟着瘫坐在椅子上，感觉到自己快要融化了。就在这时，门口传来了脚步声。"

# game/act2.rpy:357
translate schinese act2_9666a3ec:

    # osw "Uh… knock knock, am I interrupting anything?"
    osw "...嘿，我没有打扰到你们吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:359
translate schinese act2_e06049c3:

    # ben "Oh, Oswald. You gonna open up shop now?"
    ben "噢，Oswald。你是打算现在去店里吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:360
translate schinese act2_c5fc23e0:

    # "I immediately stand to greet Oswald. Finally, he’s not in his birthday suit... Instead, he’s wearing the same kind of suit he wore in the bar. He must be done getting ready for work…"
    "我立刻站起身迎接Oswald，发现他此时并不是一丝不挂，而是已经穿上了和之前酒吧里一模一样的礼服。看起来他已经准备好要去酒吧工作了..."

# game/act2.rpy:363
translate schinese act2_103a1997:

    # osw "Not yet, Benjie. I think I forgot my deodorant and perfume somewhere… They aren’t in my room."
    osw "还有些时间。对了，Benjie，你知道我的除臭剂和香水放在什么地方了吗...我在房间里找了一圈都没找到。"

# game/act2.rpy:365
translate schinese act2_145bc410:

    # ben "Oh dear, what a tragedy. I don’t suppose you think that… {i}*gasp*{/i} someone stole it?!"
    ben "噢，天哪，这真是场悲剧。你该不会觉得...{i}*咳咳*{/i}，是有人把他们偷走了吧？！ "

# game/act2.rpy:366
translate schinese act2_058317e9:

    # "Oh geez, the raccoon’s got thief jokes."
    "呃，好冷，前小偷竟然开了一个有关小偷的玩笑。"

# game/act2.rpy:368
translate schinese act2_c9c1566a:

    # osw "Not funny, Benjie. I know you wouldn’t steal my crap even if your life depended on it."
    osw "Benjie，这一点也不好笑。我知道就算你把命赌上，也不会偷我的那些东西。"

# game/act2.rpy:370
translate schinese act2_630eadf9:

    # ben "I am a supporter of natural scents, yes. Why would I want what people manufacture?"
    ben "没错，我可是自然体味的支持者。那我为什么非要去拿别人的人造品呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:372
translate schinese act2_7b3d9fca:

    # "Oswald gives the raccoon a rather disgusted look. I think he got the same idea that I did when Benjie said that."
    "Oswald厌恶地瞪了浣熊一眼。我想他现在的想法和我自己在与Benjie对话时是一样的。"

# game/act2.rpy:374
translate schinese act2_cacc6197:

    # ben "...Didn’t land, huh? Ugh… it’s right next to the boxing ring."
    ben "...看来你还是没get到点？啊，好吧，呃...我刚在在拳击台的旁边看到了。"

# game/act2.rpy:377
translate schinese act2_4fafe1a7:

    # "Benjie looks at Oswald, then at me rather flippantly."
    "Benjie看了Oswald一眼，然后无奈地看着我。"

# game/act2.rpy:378
translate schinese act2_27a7e24d:

    # osw "I use vanilla extract, thank you very much."
    osw "不 客 气，我用的可是香草精粹。"

# game/act2.rpy:380
translate schinese act2_9582fb91:

    # "Oswald comes back, two spray cans in hand. He seems to have already sprayed them on the way here; he has a distinct, rather strong smell of men’s deodorant."
    "Oswald拿着两个喷雾罐回到了我们面前。他似乎已经在来这里的路上已经喷过了；闻起来带有一股明显的、相当强烈的男士除臭剂的味道。"

# game/act2.rpy:382
translate schinese act2_2486c98d:

    # ben "You’re no fun, Oz."
    ben "Oz，你真的很无趣。"

# game/act2.rpy:384
translate schinese act2_f559ec04:

    # "Oswald nods with a smile, but his expression changes when he looks my way."
    "Oswald笑了笑作为回应，但当他看向我时，表情却发生了一些变化。"

# game/act2.rpy:386
translate schinese act2_396580fd:

    # "He’s wearing a rather guilty expression, then his face contorts to annoyance when he looks back at Benjie once more."
    "他看上去像是很愧疚的样子，在他回头去看Benjie的时候，似乎还有些恼怒。"

# game/act2.rpy:388
translate schinese act2_85248a4c:

    # osw "I hope you’re not overworking him... for your {i}own{/i} sake."
    osw "我希望你不要为了{i}你自己{/i}的利益...而让他过度工作..."

# game/act2.rpy:390
translate schinese act2_de36095b:

    # ben "Kinda hard not to, especially with only a week’s deadline to make him ready for the mission."
    ben "我很难不这样做，尤其是现在只剩一周的最后期限来让他为任务做好充足准备。"

# game/act2.rpy:392
translate schinese act2_f95fc405:

    # "Oswald briefly bares his teeth, making violent gestures in Benjie’s way. I’m taken aback at how… protective Oswald is of me. I intervene for Benjie’s sake."
    "Oswald短暂地露出了獠牙，向Benjie做出一个粗暴的手势。他对我的保护让我感到有些惊讶，于是我连忙介入到了他们两人的谈话中。"

# game/act2.rpy:395
translate schinese act2_dee54608:

    # main "It’s okay, Oswald! I’ll be fine. Besides, I kinda do need to keep up with you guys if I don’t want to… you know…"
    main "放心，Oswald，我会没事的！而且我真的很想能跟上你们的脚步，还有...我也不希望你...呃...你明白的..."

# game/act2.rpy:396
translate schinese act2_e1c9f22c:

    # "Oswald’s clearly surprised, looking a little embarrassed as he slowly backs away."
    "Oswald显然很惊讶，他的神色有些尴尬，慢慢地往后退了一小步。"

# game/act2.rpy:398
translate schinese act2_06714991:

    # osw "O-Oh… Don’t worry, [mc]. I’ll make sure nothing happens to you. Don’t worry, yeah?"
    osw "哦-哦...[mc]，我会保证一切都没事的，所以请你别担心，好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:399
translate schinese act2_3710f83b:

    # "I happily nod at him, both of us blushing before Oswald excuses himself."
    "我高兴地朝他点点头，在Oswald离开之前，我们俩人都脸红了。"

# game/act2.rpy:401
translate schinese act2_e5ad49b6:

    # osw "Well… I-I have to open the bar now. Take care of him, Benjie!"
    osw "啊...我——我现在要去酒吧了。Benjie，替我照顾好他！"

# game/act2.rpy:404
translate schinese act2_2bc963f4:

    # ben "I’m not his babysit- oh, why do I even bother…"
    ben "我又不是他的保姆——唉，我为什么要为这种事费心..."

# game/act2.rpy:407
translate schinese act2_84070cea:

    # "Oswald rushes back towards the entrance, leaving Benjie and me alone."
    "Oswald头也不回地冲向基地的入口，训练室里现在只剩下我和Benjie。"

# game/act2.rpy:409
translate schinese act2_a0e5b658:

    # ben "There he goes again…"
    ben "他终于走了..."

# game/act2.rpy:410
translate schinese act2_5c354759:

    # "Benjie seems rather exhausted after that interaction, much more than when he was training me."
    "在突发的小互动之后，Benjie似乎已经筋疲力尽了，这比他刚才训练我的时候还要累得多。"

# game/act2.rpy:411
translate schinese act2_f181f824:

    # ben "I swear, that wolf can be a handful, especially because of…"
    ben "我发誓，那只狼最近都很难对付，尤其是..."

# game/act2.rpy:412
translate schinese act2_b73d52f1:

    # "Benjie eyes me from head to toe. I awkwardly try to cover myself up, with his gaze just being so judging, it’s nuts. He might as well be a squirrel instead."
    "Benjie从头到脚打量着我，我被他盯得有些难受，下意识地遮掩自己。"

# game/act2.rpy:415
translate schinese act2_da7bdc17_1:

    # ben "[mc]..."
    ben "还有你，[mc]..."

# game/act2.rpy:416
translate schinese act2_95c3db50:

    # main "Yeah...?"
    main "怎么了...？"

# game/act2.rpy:418
translate schinese act2_36bbcba1:

    # ben "If we’re gonna spend so much time together, I should definitely learn more about you."
    ben "如果我们今后必定会花很多时间相处的话，我想我应该多去了解你才对。"

# game/act2.rpy:419
translate schinese act2_cf8f5fcb:

    # main "M-Me? What’s so special about me?"
    main "我...？我有什么特别之处吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:421
translate schinese act2_967db899:

    # ben "Hmmm… Maybe about why you wanted to be a DJ?"
    ben "嗯...也许你可以跟我讲讲，你为什么想成为一名DJ？"

# game/act2.rpy:422
translate schinese act2_782c0766:

    # main "Oh… that? It’s just a really cheesy story…"
    main "哦...你是说这个？不过这本身是个挺无聊的故事..."

# game/act2.rpy:423
translate schinese act2_f85bf826:

    # "Benjie changes position, signaling how intently he’s listening. I clear my throat as I slightly reposition myself as well, ready to tell this story."
    "Benjie改变了坐姿，表现出他对这个问题的专注。我清了清嗓子，同时也调整了一下自己坐在椅子上的方向，准备向他讲述这个故事。"

# game/act2.rpy:424
translate schinese act2_b382ae33:

    # main "Well… I didn’t really grow up in… a normal family."
    main "好吧...我并不是在一个...很正常的家庭中长大的。"

# game/act2.rpy:426
translate schinese act2_8b35c784:

    # ben "How… so?"
    ben "嗯...这是怎么一回事呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:427
translate schinese act2_0649f1e9:

    # main "If I had to describe it it would be, I guess… abusive? I don’t really know, it wasn’t like I was hit or anything."
    main "如果非要描述的话，我想大概是...我的记忆中充满了他们永无止境的辱骂？我真的不知道，这并不是说我被他们殴打或是诸如此类的事。只是...无尽的冷暴力。"

# game/act2.rpy:429
translate schinese act2_6227ab63:

    # ben "Oh..."
    ben "哦..."

# game/act2.rpy:430
translate schinese act2_2945fd6a:

    # main "My parents… well, we lived in the countryside. Simple life, ya know?"
    main "我的家人...嗯，我们一起居住在乡下，过着相当简单的生活。"

# game/act2.rpy:431
translate schinese act2_a61734f7:

    # main "You were only supposed to dream as big as the town you were raised in, and, well… that was about as far as I could get with my parents."
    main "他们一直对我施加这样的思想，告诉我‘你的梦想最多只能和你出生的这个小镇一样大’。"

# game/act2.rpy:432
translate schinese act2_0117aa5e:

    # "I immediately start to feel like tearing up. In an instant, I feel a gentle touch on my back."
    "我不知道该如何组织语言，每当我想到过去的事时，都会禁不住想要流泪。就在这时，我的背后传来了轻柔的触摸。"

# game/act2.rpy:434
translate schinese act2_cb5b92ff:

    # "I look to Benjie, who was giving me an uncharacteristically concerned look."
    "我看向Benjie，他正一反常态地用关切的目光看着我。"

# game/act2.rpy:435
translate schinese act2_55768358:

    # main "... I was a big fan of music. Whenever I told my parents anything besides what they wanted for me, I kinda just… ran for it."
    main "...在我还小的时候，我就意识到自己对音乐有多么的痴迷。然而就算我有多么喜爱音乐，父母只让我做他们想让我做的事，所以我只能强迫自己在他们面前表现得不那么喜欢。"

# game/act2.rpy:436
translate schinese act2_69fc4a3f:

    # main "Soon, high school came around. Pretty gloomy, so I started sharing my playlists. People liked it, so I thought ‘Hey, why don’t I make my own music?’"
    main "很快，我上了高中。那时的自己一直在被忧郁所笼罩，于是我开始在网络上分享我的播放列表。并惊讶地发现有很多人喜欢它，所以当时我就在想——‘为什么我不试着制作自己的音乐呢？’"

# game/act2.rpy:438
translate schinese act2_a7a9b944:

    # "Benjie gives me an approving look before I continue with my story."
    "在我继续讲述我的故事之前，Benjie给了我一个赞许的眼神。"

# game/act2.rpy:439
translate schinese act2_78f9b3b9:

    # main "I went to college with a friend. Name’s Dylan, he was and still is my biggest fan, if you could call him that."
    main "我和我的一位名叫Dylan的朋友一起上了同一所大学，他曾经是、现在也依旧是我的头号粉丝。"

# game/act2.rpy:440
translate schinese act2_a744b0d9:

    # main "He was the last nail in the coffin for me to really strive for DJ-ing. Really connect with people, bring ‘em together."
    main "他使我可以不顾周围人的评判，一心一意为自己向往的DJ事业而奋斗。我也通过自己的音乐真正地将大家建立起了联系，并让他们为共同的爱好聚集在了一起。"

# game/act2.rpy:442
translate schinese act2_eb0f2728:

    # ben "...Huh. Knew I spotted a pacifist."
    ben "...嗯，我看出你是位和平主义者了。"

# game/act2.rpy:443
translate schinese act2_84abc78e_1:

    # main "W-What?"
    main "什-什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:444
translate schinese act2_3d124595:

    # "Benjie refuses to continue, however. He instead eyes my bandaged ear."
    "Benjie似乎在示意我可以先暂停一下。而他此时的目光紧紧地注视在我绑着绷带的耳朵上。 "

# game/act2.rpy:446
translate schinese act2_bdf3087b:

    # ben "... I’m sorry for grazing that."
    ben "...我很抱歉之前擦伤了你的耳朵。"

# game/act2.rpy:447
translate schinese act2_055879cf:

    # main "O-Oh, this? It’s not a big deal… Oswald says it should’ve healed by now, but…"
    main "噢——你说这个？这没什么大不了的...Oswald告诉我，理论上讲，伤口现在应该已经好了才对，但是..."

# game/act2.rpy:449
translate schinese act2_f526cd79:

    # ben "That’s… strange. I hate to say this, but… Let the cat check it out. She’ll hear you from the infirmary."
    ben "确实很奇怪。虽然我不想这么说，但...你应该让那只猫再好好看看。她会在医务室为你做检查的。"

# game/act2.rpy:450
translate schinese act2_4685baaf:

    # main "O-Oh… you sure?"
    main "噢噢...你确定还要特地检查一下吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:453
translate schinese act2_70d92cf0:

    # "Benjie nods, helping me stand. He takes back his jacket and wears it once more, placing his hands back into the pockets."
    "Benjie点了点头，扶我站了起来。他拿起一旁的夹克重新穿在身上，把双手插回到了口袋里。"

# game/act2.rpy:454
translate schinese act2_d2ff4807:

    # "I make my way to the infirmary, but Benjie stops me midway."
    "在我正要前往医务室时，Benjie突然拦住了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:456
translate schinese act2_5343a08f:

    # ben "[mc], wait."
    ben "[mc]，等一下。"

# game/act2.rpy:457
translate schinese act2_7af04855:

    # main "Y-Yeah? What is it?"
    main "啊？怎么了？"

# game/act2.rpy:459
translate schinese act2_eda17f6a:

    # ben "Tomorrow, when we train… I’ll be less strict."
    ben "下次我们再训练的时候...我会尽可能不像今天这么严格。"

# game/act2.rpy:460
translate schinese act2_29c9921d:

    # main "Really? Why the change?"
    main "诶？为什么突然要改变这个？"

# game/act2.rpy:461
translate schinese act2_5e295992:

    # ben "You seem to respond better to that approach. Besides… I did say I wanted to get a closer look at you… and now I have."
    ben "你似乎对非强制的方式能表现出更好的反应。另外...我之前说过 ，我确实很想更多地了解你...而现在，我对你的了解更加丰富了。"

# game/act2.rpy:462
translate schinese act2_84cba391:

    # main "Oh… uh, ok. I’ll see you later, then, Benjie!"
    main "哦...呃，好的。那Benjie，我们待会儿再见吧！"

# game/act2.rpy:465
translate schinese act2_1e38fdd2:

    # "I leave towards the infirmary, hoping to see Ellie soon. Maybe Oswald wrapped my bandage wrong, so it hasn’t healed yet? I guess I’ll find out soon…"
    "我朝医务室走去，希望能尽快见到Ellie。也许...Oswald把我的绷带包错了，所以伤口现在还没痊愈？或许等下我就知道是什么原因了..."

# game/act2.rpy:468
translate schinese act2_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/act2.rpy:469
translate schinese act2_ce58264e:

    # "{i}Meanwhile...{/i}"
    "{i}与此同时...{/i}"

# game/act2.rpy:472
translate schinese act2_2088f25a:

    # ben "...[mc]… You’re an only child. Yet you remind me of {i}him{/i} so much… How can someone who grew up in the dark have such an empathetic heart?"
    ben "...[mc]...虽然你是独生子，但你...和{i}他{/i}实在太像了... 一个在黑暗中长大的人究竟是怎样一直保持着这样一颗同理心呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:473
translate schinese act2_a20cefa7_1:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/act2.rpy:476
translate schinese act2_f22b9bae:

    # "I turn at the bend, the light of the infirmary illuminating the dim hallway. I survey the surroundings... no sign of life can be found."
    "我在拐角处转身，看到医务室的灯光点亮了门外昏暗的走廊。当我环顾四周时，却发现周围并没有任何人在。"

# game/act2.rpy:478
translate schinese act2_bc580a9a:

    # "I sheepishly look around the nooks and crannies for Ellie, hoping that she has those cat-like invisibility powers all felines I’ve met seem to have."
    "我又朝着房间的角落和缝隙中寻找Ellie的踪迹，毕竟...作为猫科兽人，我总觉得她自带一种能够“隐藏身形”的能力。"

# game/act2.rpy:479
translate schinese act2_a29c6e4f:

    # "After a few minutes of searching, however, I still came up empty-handed. I do {i}not{/i} need another workout today; this life will certainly need some getting used to."
    "然而，经过几分钟的搜寻，仍然没有看到任何人的踪影。今天的训练已经让我筋疲力尽，我真的不想再找下去了。"

# game/act2.rpy:480
translate schinese act2_8453e6e1:

    # "I resign myself to sitting on one of the examination tables, just catching my breath."
    "我坐在其中的一张检查台上，想先休息一下，顺便喘口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:482
translate schinese act2_b9f9fbf9:

    # "As I do so, the door opposite of me whirs before quietly opening up, with Ellie appearing from the room on the other side with a tray of beakers and flasks."
    "而我刚刚坐下，Ellie便从房间另一侧的门里走了出来，她的手中还拿着一个托盘，上边摆满了各种烧杯和烧瓶。"

# game/act2.rpy:484
translate schinese act2_6d5d51c5:

    # el "Alright… that should all be this week’s extracts… Now for the reagent inventory check…"
    el "好的...这应该就是本周所提炼出的物质了...现在要进行的是试剂库存检查..."

# game/act2.rpy:486
translate schinese act2_311663b1:

    # "She places the tray under the shelves, without even taking notice of me. She seems to be deep in thought, so I try to gently catch her attention."
    "她把托盘放在架子底下，陷入了沉思，甚至完全没有注意到我的存在。"

# game/act2.rpy:487
translate schinese act2_8b8f8f7b:

    # main "E...Ellie…?"
    main "E...Ellie...?"

# game/act2.rpy:488
translate schinese act2_8690127b:

    # el "...And then, we could change the potassium chlorate for white phosphorus for the projectile grenades…"
    el "...然后，我们可以把氯酸盐替换成白磷...用于抛射用的手榴弹..."

# game/act2.rpy:489
translate schinese act2_e2bcaf4a:

    # "Oh jeez. Looks like being gentle isn’t really going to nab her attention..."
    "我的天，看来我需要稍微提高点声音才能引起她的注意了..."

# game/act2.rpy:490
translate schinese act2_eda6adf0:

    # main "Ellie...!"
    main "Ellie...!"

# game/act2.rpy:491
translate schinese act2_5576d4fa:

    # el "But for the smoke trailers, we could stick with the chlorate…"
    el "但是对于烟雾追踪器，我们仍然可以坚持使用氯酸盐..."

# game/act2.rpy:492
translate schinese act2_a3601f66:

    # main "ELLIE!"
    main "ELLIE！"

# game/act2.rpy:495
translate schinese act2_5bfd3d49:

    # el "Sweet light of Eden!"
    el "啊！！"

# game/act2.rpy:496
translate schinese act2_21862dd2:

    # "She jolts upwards, her fur all bristled. Guess I went too far…"
    "她突然猛地跳了起来，甚至都炸毛了。也许我的声音大的有些过头了..."

# game/act2.rpy:497
translate schinese act2_0c2ab135:

    # main "Uh… H-hi there..."
    main "呃...嗨，你好..."

# game/act2.rpy:499
translate schinese act2_4a224c32:

    # el "O-Oh. It’s just you. I-is there something you need?"
    el "噢——哦，原来是你啊。你——有什么事吗？ "

# game/act2.rpy:500
translate schinese act2_bab1c925:

    # "I notice that she’s still shivering from the shock, so I try to talk a bit more slowly than usual."
    "她仍因刚才的震惊还未缓过来，所以我试着进一步放缓自己的语速。"

# game/act2.rpy:501
translate schinese act2_9c069022:

    # main "Uhm… It’s about this bandage…"
    main "嗯...是关于这个绷带的事..."

# game/act2.rpy:503
translate schinese act2_9679ad19:

    # el "...The one on your ear? But that shouldn’t be on for more than a few minutes… Did Oswald forget to trigger it?"
    el "...你耳朵上的那个吗？但是一般情况下这个绷带只要使用几分钟就会看到效果了...难道是Oswald忘记将它激活了吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:504
translate schinese act2_53b309d2:

    # main "T-Trigger it…?"
    main "激活...？"

# game/act2.rpy:506
translate schinese act2_5ff46c95:

    # el "O-Oh! Well… Edenite medical equipment works quite differently. Let me see here…"
    el "哦哦——！嗯...这里的医疗设备工作原理和普通医疗完全不同。让我来看看..."

# game/act2.rpy:508
translate schinese act2_ada6c4fd:

    # "She inches closer towards me and reaches out for the bandage then begins to tickle it."
    "她朝我这边靠近，然后伸手去触碰绷带，并用爪子在上面挠来挠去。"

# game/act2.rpy:509
translate schinese act2_58b8c6bc:

    # "Though the ear is covered, I can still feel her paw trailing across the surface. It starts making my ear twitch."
    "虽然耳朵被一层绷带所覆盖，但她爪子在绷带表面上的力度，仍然让我的耳朵有些抽搐。"

# game/act2.rpy:510
translate schinese act2_5ab4cb8c:

    # main "W-What are you doing?!"
    main "你...在做什么？！"

# game/act2.rpy:512
translate schinese act2_3646aaa4:

    # el "Agitating the bandage. It’s made of a polymer that releases spores which then accelerate the healing process. Now, please try to stay still."
    el "搅动绷带。它由一种能释放孢子的聚合物制成，经过激活后可以加速伤口愈合过程。现在，请尽量不要乱动。"

# game/act2.rpy:514
translate schinese act2_aeb68365:

    # "She continues to trace her finger across the bandage, then I start feeling a lot chillier. At first, it was as if a breeze started blowing at me, then I felt my legs going numb."
    "她继续用手指在绷带上揉来揉去，然后我感觉到了身体突然开始变得寒冷。起初，像是一阵微风朝我吹来，随后我的双腿开始变得麻木。"

# game/act2.rpy:515
translate schinese act2_933f90ca:

    # "My hands then began tingling. My vision started to blur a bit too, with my head aching in tandem with it."
    "紧接着，连我的手掌也开始变得刺痛了。甚至到最后，伴随着头部的疼痛，我的视线也变得有些模糊。"

# game/act2.rpy:516
translate schinese act2_441b7b11:

    # main "Nnnghh…!"
    main "唔呃...！"

# game/act2.rpy:518
translate schinese act2_a5c75432:

    # el "Hm? O-Oh, right. The blood flow will start coagulating in the area, so you might feel some imbalances… it should go away after a little bit."
    el "嗯？哦，对了。这会使你的血液加速流动到这个部位，然后在该区域快速凝结，所以一开始你可能会感觉到有些...不平衡...不过这种症状很快就会消失的。"

# game/act2.rpy:520
translate schinese act2_49b184c6:

    # "Her trailing stops, and the bandage begins to fall on its own. Its thread falls onto my muzzle, which Ellie quickly takes and crumples before promptly disposing."
    "在她停止手上的动作后，绷带也开始自然脱落，并掉落在我的吻部。Ellie立刻把它拿起来揉成了一团，然后迅速进行了处理。"

# game/act2.rpy:521
translate schinese act2_c1799228:

    # "She pulls herself closer to the wound and examines it thoroughly."
    "她贴近我的伤口并认真地进行检查。"

# game/act2.rpy:522
translate schinese act2_9a2485cb:

    # main "Uhm… is it alright…?"
    main "嗯...已经好了吗...？"

# game/act2.rpy:524
translate schinese act2_578d74b5:

    # el "Huh… It’s healed, but…"
    el "呃...已经痊愈了，不过..."

# game/act2.rpy:525
translate schinese act2_eef542a5:

    # main "But what?"
    main "不过什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:527
translate schinese act2_ea1233b1:

    # el "Hmmm… I guess you just have to see for yourself…"
    el "唔...我想你应该需要自己看看..."

# game/act2.rpy:528
translate schinese act2_8465451d:

    # "I blow out air in anxiety. I take out my phone and turn on its front camera to look. It seems fine, except… a part’s chipped off?! It’s just-- just gone!"
    "我突然因她的态度而感到焦虑，然后拿出手机打开了前置摄像头。看起来...伤口愈合的很不错，除了...耳朵上的一小部分缺损？！我的耳朵，它——它现在有了一个缺痕！"

# game/act2.rpy:529
translate schinese act2_adbab3f1:

    # main "What the hell? Why’s it still chipped off?!"
    main "这到底是什么鬼？为什么它还是没有长好？！"

# game/act2.rpy:531
translate schinese act2_06c575b7:

    # el "O-Oh… The bandage just accelerates the healing process but…"
    el "噢——呃...绷带只是加速了愈合过程，但是..."

# game/act2.rpy:533
translate schinese act2_a5b63945:

    # el "It doesn’t magically regenerate the body part itself…"
    el "它并不会神奇地让身体部位本身再生..."

# game/act2.rpy:534
translate schinese act2_762a997a:

    # main "Oh, fuck… everyone’s gonna think I’m some sort of troublemaker if I keep getting shit like these…"
    main "噢，草...以后所有人都会知道我曾经因为某种事故导致耳朵受伤了..."

# game/act2.rpy:536
translate schinese act2_2c4122ff:

    # el "W-Well, [mc], it is a bit… unavoidable in this line of work…"
    el "好吧...[mc]，我只能说...这种伤在此类工作中往往是...不可避免的..."

# game/act2.rpy:537
translate schinese act2_f76d6529:

    # "I grimace at the thought of more scars like these. I mean, Oswald gets shit like this and he comes out of it a sexy beast! But as for me… well… I sigh before facing Ellie once more."
    "一想到可能还会有更多这样的伤痕，我的脸就变得有些扭曲。我想说，Oswald也有类似的伤痕，但是这些痕迹在他身上反而令他看起来更加性感！但是对于我来说...唉...我只能在Ellie面前叹了口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:538
translate schinese act2_dcbf8fbc:

    # main "...I guess it can’t really be helped. Thanks, Ellie."
    main "...我想可能真的没有办法了。不过还是非常谢谢你，Ellie。"

# game/act2.rpy:540
translate schinese act2_b34a781d:

    # el "O-Oh! N-No problem, [mc]…!"
    el "喔-哦...！[mc]，没...没事的！"

# game/act2.rpy:541
translate schinese act2_b2fe72a7:

    # "She surprisingly becomes quite flustered at my gratitude. I guess she really is just easily flushed."
    "出乎意料的是，她对我的谢意表现得相当慌张。我猜她确实是一个很容易害羞的人。"

# game/act2.rpy:542
translate schinese act2_2b174063:

    # "I thought she was like that only towards Benjie, but now it doesn’t seem it’s a specific thing."
    "我之前还以为她只有在Benjie面前才会这样，不过现在看起来，她只是性格如此。"

# game/act2.rpy:543
translate schinese act2_803e4ddf:

    # "Then again, Benjie constantly patronizing her on top of the constant antagonizing probably isn’t helping, either."
    "另外...或许现在看来，Benjie对她的苛刻态度可能也有些过度的样子？"

# game/act2.rpy:545
translate schinese act2_4d298d51:

    # main "...Anyways, I’m just…"
    main "...那么，我现在..."

# game/act2.rpy:546
translate schinese act2_9139cdd0:

    # "I stand from the examination table and start walking towards the exit."
    "我从检查台上站起来，打算离开医务室。"

# game/act2.rpy:547
translate schinese act2_17ff86a1:

    # main "...going to go and see if I can-"
    main "...应该去看看还有没有其他事..."

# game/act2.rpy:549
translate schinese act2_e8f97eab:

    # el "W-Wait!"
    el "等-请等一下！"

# game/act2.rpy:550
translate schinese act2_d192dd09:

    # "Ellie sheepishly stops me."
    "Ellie不好意思地拦住了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:552
translate schinese act2_9ed94518:

    # el "[mc]… I require something that needs…"
    el "[mc]...我需要一些...东西..."

# game/act2.rpy:553
translate schinese act2_0e76a445:

    # "Ellie trails off at the last few words into a mumble."
    "Ellie在说到最后几个字的时候，几乎是在自言自语了。"

# game/act2.rpy:554
translate schinese act2_dabe97c4:

    # main "Needs? Needs what?"
    main "东西？需要什么东西？"

# game/act2.rpy:556
translate schinese act2_35126176:

    # el "Y...Yo... -easu--…"
    el "你...你的...数——"

# game/act2.rpy:557
translate schinese act2_b76fd856:

    # "She continues to mumble to herself, and I just stand there in confusion."
    "她继续在自言自语，只留我一人困惑地愣在原地。"

# game/act2.rpy:558
translate schinese act2_5b072bf7:

    # el "..Y-Your… m-measurements…"
    el "...你——你的...测量数据..."

# game/act2.rpy:559
translate schinese act2_b059f104:

    # main "...My what?"
    main "...我的什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:561
translate schinese act2_86894ec2:

    # el "I… well… Just come with me, please?"
    el "我...呃...请跟我过来，好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:562
translate schinese act2_5961110d:

    # "I hesitate to go with her, skeptical about the direction she’s headed."
    "我满脑子的疑惑，犹豫着要不要跟她走。"

# game/act2.rpy:563
translate schinese act2_3c299677:

    # "She seems to be inching towards the lab, and a part of me just feels squeamish to go in there especially because of the impression I got from Alice’s warnings."
    "她似乎正慢慢地朝着实验室的方向走去，而我则是对即将进入那个地方感到有些不适。尤其在我的印象中，Alice曾经还对我发出了警告。"

# game/act2.rpy:564
translate schinese act2_a39b0132:

    # main "C-Can’t you just get them here…?"
    main "就...就在这里不行吗...？"

# game/act2.rpy:566
translate schinese act2_db79d2e3:

    # el "Uhm… well, my scanning equipment is in there, so…"
    el "嗯...嗯，我的扫描设备在实验室里，所以..."

# game/act2.rpy:567
translate schinese act2_350140a5:

    # "An awkward silence follows."
    "紧接着是一阵尴尬的沉默。"

# game/act2.rpy:568
translate schinese act2_55fc0817:

    # "I suppose I shouldn’t be giving Ellie a hard time. Something tells me it’ll be a lot more trouble than it’s worth to upset Ellie…"
    "我想我不应该让Ellie感到难堪。有人提醒过我，要是让Ellie心烦意乱，造成的麻烦可比麻烦本身还要多得多..."

# game/act2.rpy:569
translate schinese act2_ebadce6d:

    # "I sigh in resignation."
    "我无奈地叹了口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:570
translate schinese act2_adf7a3ae:

    # main "Fine… fine, let’s go into your lab then."
    main "好吧...好吧，那我就跟你去实验室里吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:571
translate schinese act2_e5bb305e:

    # "Ellie’s face relaxes with relief."
    "Ellie的表情如释重负般地放松了。"

# game/act2.rpy:573
translate schinese act2_31ea013e:

    # el "A-Alright… this way, please."
    el "好——好的...请到这边来。"

# game/act2.rpy:575
translate schinese act2_4acf0ed3:

    # "Ellie meekly points towards the door she came from, which makes my uneasiness resurface."
    "Ellie腼腆地指了指她来的那扇门，我突然又觉得不安了。"

# game/act2.rpy:576
translate schinese act2_50355c78:

    # "I try my best to stifle it as I follow her, constantly telling myself that this isn’t going to be as bad as its starting to look."
    "当我跟随她走进实验室时，我一遍又一遍地告诉自己事情不会变得更糟。"

# game/act2.rpy:577
translate schinese act2_fc8d479d:

    # "I wrap my arms gently around myself as the cat opens the doors and ushers me in. After the doors open, though, a surprising scent of fragrant flowers and other greenery overwhelms my nose."
    "当实验室的门打开时，一股令人惊讶的花香和其他植物的香味立即充斥着我的鼻子。"

# game/act2.rpy:578
translate schinese act2_84f6ac5b:

    # main "Nngh…!"
    main "唔...！"

# game/act2.rpy:580
translate schinese act2_cabe1f35:

    # el "O-Oh…! I forgot that canines like you have a more acute sense of smell compared to others."
    el "噢噢...！我忘了犬科的嗅觉要比其他物种更敏锐。"

# game/act2.rpy:582
translate schinese act2_5e30e5c3:

    # el "Well… please allow yourself to acclimate to it. It is not the least bit harmful, I assure you."
    el "嗯...请试着适应一下吧。我向你保证，这没有一点害处。"

# game/act2.rpy:583
translate schinese act2_e8118721:

    # "I just nod while rubbing my nose a bit. It feels like it’s pollen season all over again…"
    "我只能一边揉着鼻子一边点头，这种感觉像是又一次到了花粉季一样..."

# game/act2.rpy:585
translate schinese act2_b41dbb9c:

    # "As soon as I enter, I immediately understand why so many varied scents are in the air. This entire place is filled to the brim with different kinds of plants in all shapes and sizes!"
    "一进门，我便立刻意识到为什么这里会有如此浓烈的气味了。整个房间里摆满了各种形状花样繁杂的植物！"

# game/act2.rpy:586
translate schinese act2_f808062a:

    # "Ellie trails some of the leaves that she passes by as she heads into the direction of a smaller room, examining a few of the flasks and other containers."
    "Ellie穿过几片植物的叶子，走向了其中一个较小的房间里，检查着一些烧瓶、以及其他的容器。"

# game/act2.rpy:587
translate schinese act2_d45a3cca:

    # "I stand there, extremely dumbfounded, and just stare blankly at all the plants."
    "我站在她身边，目瞪口呆地望着所有的植物。"

# game/act2.rpy:588
translate schinese act2_51dc06cc:

    # main "So… uh, Ellie…"
    main "所以...呃，Ellie..."

# game/act2.rpy:590
translate schinese act2_1229722b:

    # el "W-Wait a moment… still calibrating the systems…"
    el "等一下...我还在校准系统..."

# game/act2.rpy:591
translate schinese act2_9d6f388a:

    # "More silence only broken by the rustling of leaves, the continuous whirring of the machines, and the occasional clinking of glass."
    "周围一片寂静，只有树叶的沙沙声、以及机器运转的嗡嗡声，偶尔还有玻璃被树叶轻触的叮当声。"

# game/act2.rpy:592
translate schinese act2_db8eee25:

    # "Ellie passes by in quick bursts, taking a piece from a nearby leaf, then going some under the counters, then stores a beaker or two into a sealed container."
    "Ellie从我身边快速经过，从附近的某个植物上取下了一小片叶子，然后又从柜台下面拿出了一些什么东西，并从中取出一两个烧杯，把这些东西混合进容器里。"

# game/act2.rpy:593
translate schinese act2_96edc41a:

    # "It’s quite a mesmerizing sight, kind of like watching Dylan mixing drinks. I do wonder… How is he holding up?"
    "我的目光被她的动作吸引，这让我又想起Dylan当时调酒的样子。我真的很想知道...Dylan现在究竟怎么样了？"

# game/act2.rpy:594
translate schinese act2_8d4d4e58:

    # "I’m gonna have to tell him that, for the most part, I’m doing alright. I’m just not sure if he knows all of these going on in his place of work..."
    "我想告诉他，我现在大体上过得很好。只是我到目前还不确定{i}(也不能去问){/i}他是否知道在他兼职的地方还隐藏着这样的事..."

# game/act2.rpy:596
translate schinese act2_0e827d25:

    # el "[mc]… It’s time for me to… ummm…"
    el "[mc]...是时候让我...嗯..."

# game/act2.rpy:597
translate schinese act2_12c707ed:

    # main "My… measurements?"
    main "你是想说你需要我的...测量数据吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:599
translate schinese act2_2135b6a8:

    # el "Y-Yes… and for that, y-you may have t-to…"
    el "是——是的...为此，你...你可能需要..."

# game/act2.rpy:600
translate schinese act2_6381e796:

    # "She stutters more, her face becoming more and more flushed. I raise an eyebrow at her, confused about what she wants me to do."
    "她越来越结结巴巴，脸也开始泛红。我对她挑起眉毛，不知道她到底想要我做什么。"

# game/act2.rpy:601
translate schinese act2_567a9102:

    # main "...Uh-huh?"
    main "...嗯？"

# game/act2.rpy:603
translate schinese act2_e8999a9c:

    # el "S...S-Strip…"
    el "把...把...衣服脱光..."

# game/act2.rpy:604
translate schinese act2_c004c2dd:

    # "Oh. Fucking Hell. No way…!"
    "噢，该死，{b}绝对{/b}不行...！"

# game/act2.rpy:605
translate schinese act2_cdae1c51:

    # main "...S-Strip…?!"
    main "...脱——脱光？！"

# game/act2.rpy:607
translate schinese act2_224ccee7:

    # el "Eeeep...!"
    el "没-没错...！"

# game/act2.rpy:608
translate schinese act2_1b78f1aa:

    # main "W-W-Why do I have to be--?!"
    main "为...为什么我非要...？！"

# game/act2.rpy:610
translate schinese act2_b7c44f7e:

    # el "I-I’m sorry!"
    el "对...对不起！"

# game/act2.rpy:612
translate schinese act2_d077e7fb:

    # el "It’s just that I-I just need to… examine you i-in full…!"
    el "我只是...只是需要对你进行...彻底的检查！"

# game/act2.rpy:613
translate schinese act2_0ff81730:

    # "I try to hide my embarrassment, tugging at my clothes tightly as if that’ll prevent me from ever stripping in front of her."
    "我努力掩饰自己的尴尬，紧紧地拽着自己的衣服，好像这样就可以守住我的衣服一样。"

# game/act2.rpy:614
translate schinese act2_eacfe49c:

    # "Ellie also seems to be shriveling up like me. She’s definitely not comfortable with this either."
    "Ellie有些畏缩。看上去，她似乎也对此有些不适。"

# game/act2.rpy:615
translate schinese act2_03646759:

    # "I sigh once more, immediately understanding one thing. If we both want to get this over with, I just have to… comply..."
    "我再次叹了口气，意识到如果我想尽快结束掉这里的问题，那我只需要...照做就好了..."

# game/act2.rpy:616
translate schinese act2_05e9ded6:

    # main "A-Alright…"
    main "好吧..."

# game/act2.rpy:618
translate schinese act2_0d4a105a:

    # el "Really…?"
    el "真的吗...？"

# game/act2.rpy:621
translate schinese act2_8a91478a:

    # "I begin to take off my shirt and pants. I try my best to expel every single embarrassing feeling off of my body as I slowly strip down to my underwear."
    "我开始脱掉短袖和裤子。而当我慢慢地脱下内衣时，我尽全力让自己表现的不要那么尴尬...这只是身体检查而已..."

# game/act2.rpy:622
translate schinese act2_120f4a02:

    # "To my surprise, Ellie seems unfazed by it, remaining as timid as she normally seems to be around everyone."
    "令我惊讶的是，Ellie的情绪似乎并没有什么波动，仍然保持着她平时在其它人面前略显胆怯的举止。"

# game/act2.rpy:623
translate schinese act2_59df4857:

    # "She continues to wait expectantly to get onto my birthday suit, and I just have no choice on the matter whatsoever."
    "她继续满怀期待地等待着从我身上得到她需要的数据，而既然我已经答应了她，我在这件事上也就别无选择了。"

# game/act2.rpy:624
translate schinese act2_2a23b4a0:

    # "Taking a deep breath, I take off my underwear in one swift motion, my sheath in full view."
    "深吸一口气，我迅速脱下内裤，把身体暴露在空气中。"

# game/act2.rpy:626
translate schinese act2_84af0345:

    # main "Ugh…"
    main "呃..."

# game/act2.rpy:628
translate schinese act2_99901c74:

    # el "Alright. T-This way, please."
    el "好的，请...站到这个位置。"

# game/act2.rpy:630
translate schinese act2_7fa2d090:

    # "She ushers me onto a lit platform. I try to shimmy my way through the tight space that is her lab."
    "我努力穿过她实验室的狭小空间，然后被带到了一个被灯光照耀着的平台上。"

# game/act2.rpy:631
translate schinese act2_179df05c:

    # "I’ve been covering my unmentionables with my paws, waves of embarrassment never ceasing to wash over me."
    "我始终用双手捂住自己的胯下，一阵阵的尴尬像海浪一样不停地拍打着我的脸颊。"

# game/act2.rpy:632
translate schinese act2_c3f1035e:

    # "Well, at least I don’t stink, or else that’s another thing I’d have to be embarrassed about..."
    "好吧，还好我刚才洗过了澡，要是有臭味的话就更尴尬了..."

# game/act2.rpy:634
translate schinese act2_27a46e65:

    # el "Alright, [mc]. Stand straight and keep all of your extremities within the square. The scan will begin soon."
    el "好。[mc]，现在请立正站好，让你的四肢都进到平台的范围内，扫描很快就会开始了。"

# game/act2.rpy:635
translate schinese act2_3d821b2a:

    # main "O-Ok…"
    main "好...好的..."

# game/act2.rpy:637
translate schinese act2_11451c60:

    # "Ellie moves to the computer, typing in things I can barely see as she prepares the device."
    "Ellie走到了电脑前开始输入些什么东西，不过从我这个角度什么也看不到就是了。"

# game/act2.rpy:639
translate schinese act2_a058e343:

    # "When she presses enter, the device lights up with multiple light sensors that pass over my body in quick succession, both in top-to-bottom and left-to-right motions."
    "当她按下回车时，设备上突然亮起了许多光学传感器，自上而下、从左到右快速并连续地扫描着我的身体。"

# game/act2.rpy:640
translate schinese act2_73213a8e:

    # "I try my best to stay as stiff and straight as possible, keeping my crotch out of her view and before I even know it, the scan has finished."
    "我尽可能保持身体笔直地站着，同时尽最大努力遮住我的胯下。扫描很快就结束了。"

# game/act2.rpy:641
translate schinese act2_99dd29c3:

    # el "A-Alright… quite average numbers."
    el "好-好吧...相当平均的数字。"

# game/act2.rpy:643
translate schinese act2_68a034c0:

    # "A-Average? Is she calling me average? Well, that just hurts my feelings indirectly…"
    "平...平均？他是在说我很普通吗？好吧，这有点间接性伤害了我的感情..."

# game/act2.rpy:644
translate schinese act2_8cfee910:

    # main "O-Oh… does that mean I can g-go now?"
    main "哦...那我现在可以走了吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:645
translate schinese act2_f385e654:

    # el "Not yet. I still have to do my… personal examination."
    el "还不行。我还想完成一下...我的个人检查。"

# game/act2.rpy:647
translate schinese act2_f504ea90:

    # main "YOUR WHAT?!"
    main "{b}你说什么？！{/b} "

# game/act2.rpy:648
translate schinese act2_a12fef66:

    # el "P-Please, calm down! It’s only a physical exam. You d-don’t have to worry."
    el "请...请你先冷静一下！只是普通的体检而已，别...别担心。"

# game/act2.rpy:650
translate schinese act2_db902789:

    # "I falter a bit while Ellie takes out her stethoscope. She places the two earpieces in and begins pressing the diaphragm onto my chest."
    "我还在犹豫，但Ellie此时已经从一旁拿起听诊器，把听诊头按压在我的胸前。"

# game/act2.rpy:651
translate schinese act2_92acc805:

    # el "Hmm… normal heart rate. Good, good."
    el "嗯...心率正常。好，很好。"

# game/act2.rpy:652
translate schinese act2_90ad4cc7:

    # main "T-That’s weird…"
    main "这...这也太奇怪了..."

# game/act2.rpy:653
translate schinese act2_c7069692:

    # "Ellie only gives me a passing glance before continuing to push onto my chest."
    "Ellie只是看了我一眼，然后推了推我的胸口。"

# game/act2.rpy:654
translate schinese act2_7124b036:

    # el "Alright, please turn around."
    el "好了，现在请转过身。"

# game/act2.rpy:655
translate schinese act2_99a7d5dc:

    # main "I-I’m not sure if I want to…"
    main "我——我不确定我是不是还想再继续体检..."

# game/act2.rpy:657
translate schinese act2_5d10b40f:

    # "Ellie doesn’t hesitate, instead I hear her pressing a button and that spins the platform, revealing to her my backside."
    "Ellie没有丝毫犹豫，与之相反，我只听到她按下了一个按钮，我脚下的平台便自动旋转了起来。现在，我的后背完完全全展现在她的面前。"

# game/act2.rpy:658
translate schinese act2_b94567e5:

    # main "A-Ah!"
    main "啊——！"

# game/act2.rpy:659
translate schinese act2_f236ee65:

    # "She presses down with the diaphragm again, but in a different location on my back this time."
    "他再次把听诊头贴在我的身上，只不过这次是在我背上的其他位置。"

# game/act2.rpy:660
translate schinese act2_0cdf4de2:

    # el "Now, take a deep breath for me."
    el "现在，请你深呼吸。"

# game/act2.rpy:661
translate schinese act2_1aba431d:

    # "I hesitantly do so..."
    "我犹豫了一下，但还是照做了..."

# game/act2.rpy:662
translate schinese act2_db8d704b:

    # "She’s quick to take the stethoscope off after she’s done."
    "Ellie采集数据完毕，快速地把听诊器从我身上拿走。"

# game/act2.rpy:663
translate schinese act2_7141fb63:

    # "I turn my head to face her, feeling completely violated."
    "我转头面对她，感觉自己像是被侵犯了一样。"

# game/act2.rpy:665
translate schinese act2_85621d08:

    # main "Is it finally over…?"
    main "终于可以结束了吗...？"

# game/act2.rpy:666
translate schinese act2_f420a4a6:

    # el "One more thing. C-can you p-please, take your hands off your sheath…"
    el "还有最后一件事，你可以...把手先拿开一下吗..."

# game/act2.rpy:667
translate schinese act2_47a27368:

    # "I gasp loudly."
    "我猛吸一口凉气。"

# game/act2.rpy:669
translate schinese act2_f3cf0234:

    # main "NO WAY!"
    main "{b}想都别想！{/b}"

# game/act2.rpy:670
translate schinese act2_78f0f1df:

    # "I immediately curl up in an attempt to cover what’s left of my dignity, to which she reacts by just staring at me, wide-eyed."
    "我立刻缩起身子，试图掩盖住我最后的隐私，但是Ellie依然睁大了眼睛继续盯着我看。"

# game/act2.rpy:671
translate schinese act2_f5ed65d7:

    # el "[mc]… P-Please just let me take a quick look. I just need a second or two, it’ll be quick… I-I promise!"
    el "[mc]...拜托了，只要一两秒钟就好，很快的...我向你保证！"

# game/act2.rpy:672
translate schinese act2_b8cc6f2c:

    # main "I… I can’t…"
    main "我...还是不行..."

# game/act2.rpy:673
translate schinese act2_e373848f:

    # "Ellie sighs to herself."
    "Ellie自顾自地叹了口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:674
translate schinese act2_aa80d0e3:

    # el "Just a glance... Please?"
    el "就一眼...求你了？"

# game/act2.rpy:675
translate schinese act2_00aab8ee:

    # "She looks at me with pleading eyes, and I do have to admit...they’re quite effective. I start actually feeling bad."
    "她用恳求的眼神看着我，我不得不承认...这对我来说真的相当奏效。我的防线开始有些崩溃了。"

# game/act2.rpy:676
translate schinese act2_dd0e35b1:

    # "I may be giving her too much of a hard time; she doesn’t seem to be deriving any sort of pleasure or joy out of this entire experience any more than I am."
    "这只是个体检，我一直这样扭扭捏捏可能也耽误了她相当多的时间；而且她似乎也只是在完成自己工作数据的收集，丝毫没有其它别的意思。"

# game/act2.rpy:677
translate schinese act2_7d80a055:

    # "Am I being too selfish?"
    "会不会是我有点太自私了呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:678
translate schinese act2_1279ae42:

    # main "U-um…?"
    main "呃...唔..."

# game/act2.rpy:680
translate schinese act2_811e30e1:

    # "I begrudgingly do as she says, slowly revealing my sheath to her. Just like she says, it took only a few seconds of glancing at it before signalling me to cover it up again."
    "我不情愿地把双手从那里拿开，照着她所说的去做了。就像Ellie所说的一样，她确实只看了短短的几秒钟，就示意我可以把它遮住了。"

# game/act2.rpy:681
translate schinese act2_b6c5604e:

    # el "S-See? Just a quick glance, that's all."
    el "对吧？只是短短的几秒钟时间就足够了。"

# game/act2.rpy:683
translate schinese act2_4ad3b7f5:

    # main "How many times do I have to do this…?"
    main "我今后还要做多少次这种身体检查...？"

# game/act2.rpy:684
translate schinese act2_103ae77d:

    # "Ellie moves her bangs as she studies the results on her tablet. After which she looks back at me."
    "Ellie一边在平板电脑上观察数据结果，一边拨弄着她的斜刘海。在被问到这个问题之后，她抬起头看向了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:687
translate schinese act2_3be6383b:

    # el "A-Ah. It was merely to check if you’re in good health, and for the new gear I’m tasked with preparing for you."
    el "啊——这次检测和数据收集一方面是为了检查你是否健康，另一方面是为了我们日后可以为你准备合适的新装备。"

# game/act2.rpy:689
translate schinese act2_84c76b27:

    # "She takes out some rolls of cloth, and immediately something becomes familiar about them."
    "她拿出了几卷布料，我立刻对这些布料卷产生了熟悉的感觉。"

# game/act2.rpy:690
translate schinese act2_38a2af36:

    # "Though I didn’t take a hard look before, I’m pretty sure those are the same rolls that Benjie had with him when I bumped into him."
    "虽然之前并没有仔细去看，但我很确定这和我一开始撞到Benjie身上、他掉在走廊地板上的是同一种东西。"

# game/act2.rpy:691
translate schinese act2_0046bbf8:

    # "But aren’t they on bad terms…? Why would Benjie do something that remotely involves Ellie?"
    "但Benjie和Ellie的关系不是很糟糕吗...？为什么Benjie会负责帮Ellie准备这些东西？"

# game/act2.rpy:692
translate schinese act2_c389c68e:

    # "So many questions, yet so little time for answers… it seems to be the modus operandi around here, and it’s starting to get annoying."
    "我的疑问太多了，然而答案却很少...似乎这里的工作就是这样，但我却因为得不到解答而感到烦躁。"

# game/act2.rpy:693
translate schinese act2_9da3c37d:

    # main "I-Is that so?"
    main "诶？原来是这么一回事吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:695
translate schinese act2_ed39ada7:

    # el "Yes. It’s to make sure you’re as comfortable as possible. I-I’m aware that you’re quite uneasy in our base as is, so I simply…"
    el "是的，为了尽可能做出适合你身体的装备。我...我知道你可能会对我们的基地感到很不安，所以我只是..."

# game/act2.rpy:697
translate schinese act2_203bb47e:

    # "She trails off again. Seems like she doubts herself whether she's doing a good thing or not."
    "她似乎不小心把话题跑偏了，看上去像是在怀疑自己是不是在做一件好事..."

# game/act2.rpy:698
translate schinese act2_8cde604a:

    # "She certainly reminds me of someone… a guy that Dylan would often scold back in college."
    "她让我突然想到了某个人...那个在大学里一直在被Dylan骂来骂去的家伙。"

# game/act2.rpy:699
translate schinese act2_bbef3cd8:

    # "Heh, why am I beating around the bush about it, I know he was only setting me straight… I feel like I’d be more comfortable with him here. He knows me best, after all..."
    "嘿，我为什么要拐弯抹角呢，那个人就是我自己罢了。我知道Dylan只是在很多方面想要纠正我的错误观点，目的是让我变得更好...而且在和他相处的时间里，我总会觉得很舒服。毕竟他是最了解我的那个人..."

# game/act2.rpy:700
translate schinese act2_667f4d7d:

    # main "...Uneasy, huh? I guess... you can say that…"
    main "...不安吗？嗯，我想...也可以这么说吧..."

# game/act2.rpy:702
translate schinese act2_426857cc:

    # "Ellie notices that I’m deep in thought, so she clears her throat."
    "Ellie注意到我在沉思，于是她清了清嗓子。"

# game/act2.rpy:704
translate schinese act2_18af0ab6:

    # el "...Sorry. Did I remind you of something?"
    el "...对不起，我是不是让你想到什么事情了？"

# game/act2.rpy:705
translate schinese act2_fd57dc05:

    # "I stammer at her spot on assessment."
    "我回过神来，结结巴巴地回应道。"

# game/act2.rpy:707
translate schinese act2_d4f19f74:

    # main "...Y-you’re quite observant."
    main "...你...你还真是细心啊。"

# game/act2.rpy:708
translate schinese act2_bc8c518e:

    # "She places the rolls of cloth onto her desk then takes a towel under it before handing it to me."
    "她把布卷放在桌子上，然后从桌子下面拿出了一条毛巾递给了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:710
translate schinese act2_796af8e8:

    # el "Here you go. I’ll let you change and cool down… you can leave afterwards."
    el "数据收集已经结束了，现在可以不用那么紧张了...先换好衣服，休息一下...然后就可以先离开了。"

# game/act2.rpy:711
translate schinese act2_d1e2e178:

    # main "T-Thanks, Ellie."
    main "谢谢你，Ellie。"

# game/act2.rpy:715
translate schinese act2_ec2aa503:

    # "I wrap the towel around my waist and grab my clothes. There’s a room next to Ellie’s lab where I can change."
    "我把毛巾缠在腰上，然后抓起自己的衣服。Ellie实验室旁边有一个小房间，我可以在那里换衣服。"

# game/act2.rpy:716
translate schinese act2_d6e8abf4:

    # "It’s a lot smaller, so small that I think only Ellie and I can fit in here. I quickly put my clothes back on and leave the towel in the room."
    "这个房间看起来非常小，小到似乎只有我和Ellie这种体型的人才适合这里。我连忙穿上衣服，把毛巾留在了房间里。"

# game/act2.rpy:717
translate schinese act2_f0720134:

    # "I leave the small room, but as I make my way towards the exit I take a glance back in Ellie’s direction."
    "当我离开了小房间，走向实验室的出口时，我朝着Ellie的方向望了一眼。"

# game/act2.rpy:718
translate schinese act2_49bca632:

    # "A part of me doesn’t {i}just{/i} want to leave. I’m not gonna let myself just go with their MO."
    "也许，现在的我可能并不是{i}很{/i}想离开这里。"

# game/act2.rpy:719
translate schinese act2_d62487e7:

    # "I take a deep breath and approach Ellie."
    "于是我深吸一口气，朝着Ellie的位置走了过去。"

# game/act2.rpy:722
translate schinese act2_8e4ee2b0:

    # el "...[mc]?"
    el "嗯...[mc]？?"

# game/act2.rpy:723
translate schinese act2_dd6f65d3:

    # main "H-Hey..."
    main "呃-嘿..."

# game/act2.rpy:725
translate schinese act2_7e3da66b:

    # el "I said you were free to leave. S-So why aren’t you?"
    el "你现在可以离开了，怎么还在这里呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:726
translate schinese act2_aefe9361:

    # "Her tone has a more curious tone than that of anger. She turns from her seat to fully face me as I take a seat next to hers."
    "他的语气里并没有生气的情绪，只是完完全全地感到了好奇。当我坐在她旁边的座位上时，她也从自己的座位上转过身面对着我。"

# game/act2.rpy:727
translate schinese act2_ee064f8d:

    # main "I… just wanted to talk, you know? It’s not like I have anything better to do…"
    main "我只是...想和你聊一聊，而且就算我现在离开这里，我也没有其他要做的事..."

# game/act2.rpy:728
translate schinese act2_f6b70019:

    # "Ellie raises an eyebrow at me."
    "Ellie向我挑了挑眉毛。"

# game/act2.rpy:730
translate schinese act2_ab4105f6:

    # el "Didn’t you have some training to do with Benjie, though…?"
    el "不过，你不是还要和Benjie进行训练吗...？"

# game/act2.rpy:731
translate schinese act2_4e1d1653:

    # main "We already had, actually. He sent me here after to have my ear fixed up…"
    main "实际上，今天的训练已经完成了。我来这里也是他建议的..."

# game/act2.rpy:732
translate schinese act2_08350af5:

    # "Ellie clicks her teeth, her hackles raising in suspicion."
    "Ellie咬紧牙关，眉头紧皱。"

# game/act2.rpy:734
translate schinese act2_1b4b55b9:

    # el "That… doesn’t seem to sound like him."
    el "听起来...根本不像是他会做的事。"

# game/act2.rpy:735
translate schinese act2_7e34f2b4:

    # main "W-What do you mean?"
    main "你这是什么意思？"

# game/act2.rpy:737
translate schinese act2_048fb4cb:

    # el "He… did cause the injury in the first place, no…?"
    el "一开始对你耳朵造成伤害的人...不就是他么...？"

# game/act2.rpy:738
translate schinese act2_78272260:

    # "I’m taken aback at Ellie’s frankness."
    "Ellie的直言不讳让我有些惊讶。"

# game/act2.rpy:739
translate schinese act2_b777085e:

    # main "I… well, yes…"
    main "我...好吧，确实是这样..."

# game/act2.rpy:741
translate schinese act2_d0b9a5c4:

    # "An awkward silence fills the room. I’m unsure what to say, and I don’t feel like beating around the bush will progress this conversation anywhere."
    "沉默充满了整个房间。我不知道该说些什么，而且我觉得即使改变话题也无法消除现在的尴尬。"

# game/act2.rpy:742
translate schinese act2_2cc8a24b:

    # main "Those rolls… they came from Benjie, right?"
    main "那些布料卷...是Benjie带给你的，对吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:743
translate schinese act2_3e1e59e1:

    # "Ellie looks at them and starts getting flushed."
    "Ellie看着那些布料卷，脸唰的一下红了。"

# game/act2.rpy:745
translate schinese act2_f2f527e4:

    # el "Y-Yes… what about it?"
    el "对，没错...那又怎么了？"

# game/act2.rpy:746
translate schinese act2_2bc3e0d1:

    # main "I dunno… it kind of feels weird that he does that, yet he says that he doesn’t want to associate himself with you, at all."
    main "我不知道...他的做法确实有点奇怪，但他说他根本不想和你处好关系。"

# game/act2.rpy:748
translate schinese act2_8091e710:

    # "Ellie’s posture deflates, a deep sigh escaping her breath. I guess I was too direct."
    "Ellie抱起双臂，深深地叹了一口气。我想我可能说的太直接了。 "

# game/act2.rpy:749
translate schinese act2_6f5c9740:

    # main "I-I’m sorry!"
    main "对...对不起！"

# game/act2.rpy:751
translate schinese act2_e9ef5c53:

    # el "No. You’re right. He doesn’t want anything to do with me."
    el "没事，你说得对，他不想和我有任何关系。"

# game/act2.rpy:752
translate schinese act2_8dfec933:

    # "She clenches her fists on her lab coat."
    "她抓着白大褂的手紧紧地握成了拳头。"

# game/act2.rpy:753
translate schinese act2_48ed955c:

    # main "You’re bothered by it… aren’t you?"
    main "这让你感到很困扰吗...？"

# game/act2.rpy:756
translate schinese act2_5c31bd8a:

    # "She nods at me meekly before turning to her desk. I roll my chair next to hers and make eye contact."
    "她温顺地向我点了点头，然后转过了身。我把椅子推到她的旁边坐下，并关切地看着她。"

# game/act2.rpy:759
translate schinese act2_7eae2227:

    # el "It’s not the hate and disdain I’m bothered by. It’s… the reasons why."
    el "我并没有因为被仇恨或是被蔑视而困扰，我只是...很想知道他这么做的原因。"

# game/act2.rpy:760
translate schinese act2_c3732d9f:

    # "She glances at me, and quickly recomposes herself."
    "她看了我一眼，很快恢复了冷静。"

# game/act2.rpy:762
translate schinese act2_a8318f03:

    # el "N-Not that you have a-anything to worry about, of course! This is just the way… it’s always been."
    el "不过，你并不需要为我担心什么！因为一直以来都是这样..."

# game/act2.rpy:763
translate schinese act2_e79a42eb:

    # "I click my teeth and raise my brow at her."
    "我向他挑起眉毛。"

# game/act2.rpy:764
translate schinese act2_f943538f:

    # main "Do you know why?"
    main "那你有什么头绪吗，关于他这么对待你？"

# game/act2.rpy:765
translate schinese act2_78842846:

    # "She shakes her head. I gently touch her shoulder, our eyes meeting for a bit."
    "她摇了摇头。我盯着Ellie的眼睛，轻轻地拍了拍她的肩膀。"

# game/act2.rpy:767
translate schinese act2_5832869d:

    # el "It’s a mystery to me. All I know is that he only scowls at me and treats me like I’m a huge bother to him. Sometimes, even simply breathing seems to offend him."
    el "这对我来说就是个谜。我只知道他总是对我一个人皱眉，把我当作他的大麻烦看待。有时，甚至只是呼吸都会冒犯他。"

# game/act2.rpy:768
translate schinese act2_49c3225d:

    # main "Have you... tried asking him about it?"
    main "你有没有...试着问过他这件事呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:770
translate schinese act2_b98a85b7:

    # el "H-Huh?"
    el "啊？"

# game/act2.rpy:771
translate schinese act2_c09ae34f:

    # main "Well, the only way to find the answer to this mystery is to ask him yourself."
    main "好吧，要找到这个谜团的答案，唯一的办法就是你亲自去问他。"

# game/act2.rpy:772
translate schinese act2_264212d7:

    # main "If he can’t give an answer, then he’s hating on you without any logical reason and he’ll have to be confronted with that fact."
    main "如果他不能给出答案，那么他就是毫无理由地讨厌你。这是他本人的问题。"

# game/act2.rpy:773
translate schinese act2_982a2b3a:

    # main "If he does, then you’ll know what’s wrong and you can at least see if the problems are with you or with him."
    main "如果他能给出原因，那你也可以知道到底是哪里出了问题，或者说至少可以看看问题是出在你身上还是他身上。"

# game/act2.rpy:775
translate schinese act2_3015a232:

    # "Ellie stares wide-eyed at me. Has she... never really considered actually confronting Benjie?"
    "Ellie睁大眼睛盯着我看。难道她...真的没有想过要和Benjie对峙吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:776
translate schinese act2_13aa3355:

    # "I guess that makes sense… she doesn’t seem to want to be in anyone’s way. Right now, though, that’s her biggest enemy."
    "也许这也是说得通的...她似乎不想打扰任何人。不过现在，怯懦反而是她最大的敌人。"

# game/act2.rpy:778
translate schinese act2_d22b7307:

    # el "I… I don’t know if I can, [mc]. He won’t even let me see the light of day when it comes to socializing."
    el "[mc]，我...都不知道该不该说。他甚至不想让我在任何社交场合露面，就像不见天日一样。"

# game/act2.rpy:779
translate schinese act2_ad276bf0:

    # "I pull Ellie to face me, and she stiffens up as I do so."
    "我拉着Ellie的袖子，让她面对着我，她的身体突然僵硬了起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:780
translate schinese act2_7085eab0:

    # main "That’s exactly why you have to confront him! I don’t know Benjie as well as you do, but I can sort of tell that… he doesn’t push twice."
    main "这就是你必须面对他的原因！我不像你那么了解Benjie，但我可以保证...他并不是那种不分善恶的人。"

# game/act2.rpy:782
translate schinese act2_1c1d8aaf:

    # el "W-What?"
    el "什...什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:783
translate schinese act2_6ea04986:

    # main "If he pushes you and you stay down, that’s the end of the line."
    main "如果他对你恶言以待，而你只是逆来顺受，那结果就会像现在一样。"

# game/act2.rpy:784
translate schinese act2_f3543439:

    # main "But people who he pushes and they stand their ground… they seem to catch his attention longer than anything."
    main "但是如果你能在他的否定下，坚持自己的立场...似乎更能引起他的注意。"

# game/act2.rpy:786
translate schinese act2_6fcc4a90:

    # el "[mc]… I-I don’t know if it’s…"
    el "[mc]...我不知道自己能不能..."

# game/act2.rpy:787
translate schinese act2_47dc91d0:

    # "She’s still in doubt. I can understand that, but nothing’s gonna happen if she stays like this! At the very least, she has to consider it."
    "我能理解她现在还在犹豫，但如果一直这样下去的话，什么也改变不了！至少，她应该把这件事认真考虑一下。"

# game/act2.rpy:788
translate schinese act2_8ab62d40:

    # "C’mon, [mc], think…!"
    "好吧，[mc]，想想看该怎么说...！"

# game/act2.rpy:789
translate schinese act2_bb457117:

    # main "...A friend once told me something that’s stuck with me ever since that point in my life."
    main "...有位朋友曾经告诉过我一些话，从那一刻起，我就一直在思考。"

# game/act2.rpy:791
translate schinese act2_1c1d8aaf_1:

    # el "W-What?"
    el "什...什么话？"

# game/act2.rpy:792
translate schinese act2_99017485:

    # main "‘Regretting in silence is the crappiest feeling ever. Better to let it all out than to let keep it bottled up inside.’"
    main "‘这世上最糟糕的感觉就是后悔之前自己什么都没有去做。’——与其把疑问一直藏在心底，不如勇敢地去寻找答案。"

# game/act2.rpy:794
translate schinese act2_4949df6d:

    # el "I-Is that so…?"
    el "是...这样吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:795
translate schinese act2_46b46378:

    # "Ellie thinks for a moment. She looks around aimlessly, clearly debating something. After a few moments of silence, she looks at me."
    "Ellie想了想，然后漫无目的地环顾四周，显然在进行着思想斗争。沉默片刻后，她重新看向了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:797
translate schinese act2_120be5df:

    # el "I’ll... think about it… but I can’t just ignore all the work and clutter I have in my lab."
    el "我会...考虑一下试试的...但我现在得先把实验室里工作以外的其它杂务做完才行。"

# game/act2.rpy:798
translate schinese act2_39226c65:

    # main "Then let me help you! That way, you can focus on thinking!"
    main "那我来帮你吧！这样你就可以专心思考了！"

# game/act2.rpy:800
translate schinese act2_46ae6985:

    # el "[mc]… why do you care so much?"
    el "[mc]...你为什么这么关心我的事？"

# game/act2.rpy:801
translate schinese act2_ff69502f:

    # main "O-Oh? Well..."
    main "噢？...好吧..."

# game/act2.rpy:802
translate schinese act2_5898ffc0:

    # "I think for a moment. This has been mostly just my feelings overriding my judgment, but I’m already too deep into it to go back now!"
    "我思考了一会儿。主要是因为我的感性压倒了理性，但我现在已经没办法再撒手不管了！"

# game/act2.rpy:803
translate schinese act2_5cb435ba:

    # "I’ve already committed to finding out the mysteries of this group and this whole situation, and if I had another person to help me solve those mysteries, best I take them."
    "我已经加入到这个团队中了，所以如果这里有人向我提供了帮助，那我也应该回以好意才对。"

# game/act2.rpy:804
translate schinese act2_f245b5ce:

    # main "...Think of it as a personal thing."
    main "...也许是因为一些个人的原因吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:805
translate schinese act2_e699cc0a:

    # el "If you say so... I won’t pry if you don’t want to say."
    el "这样啊...没关系，如果你不想说的话，我也就不多问了。"

# game/act2.rpy:806
translate schinese act2_0d14f474:

    # "Ellie takes a basket filled with flasks of chemicals and other liquids and hands it to me."
    "Ellie拿起一个装满化学品和其他液体的烧瓶筐子，把它递给我。"

# game/act2.rpy:808
translate schinese act2_82ffdd04:

    # el "First, I’ll need these to be relocated to the infirmary. I’ll tell you what you have to do next afterwards."
    el "首先，需要把这些东西搬到医务室。然后我再告诉你接下来要做的事情。"

# game/act2.rpy:809
translate schinese act2_11d447eb:

    # main "You got it!"
    main "好的！"

# game/act2.rpy:810
translate schinese act2_d85566a5:

    # "I enthusiastically take the basket and start marching to the infirmary."
    "我兴致冲冲地拿起筐子，开始向医务室走去。"

# game/act2.rpy:812
translate schinese act2_7f9caab2:

    # el "B-Be careful it doesn’t spill!"
    el "小心不要洒出来了！"

# game/act2.rpy:814
translate schinese act2_1a61666a:

    # el "Oh dear..."
    el "噢...我的天..."

# game/act2.rpy:818
translate schinese act2_a20cefa7_2:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/act2.rpy:819
translate schinese act2_648a7d8a:

    # "{i}Later that day...{/i}"
    "{i}当天晚些时候...{/i}"

# game/act2.rpy:823
translate schinese act2_68eda341:

    # el "Hmmm… that should be the last thing that needs doing around here."
    el "嗯...这应该是剩下的最后一件事了。"

# game/act2.rpy:825
translate schinese act2_e905ea13:

    # el "Now to take a well-deserved break…!"
    el "现在你可以好好休息一下...！"

# game/act2.rpy:828
translate schinese act2_11299b92:

    # "I carefully place the last empty basket under Alice’s counter and crash onto the lounge’s sofa."
    "我小心翼翼地把最后一个空塑料筐放在Alice的办公桌下面，然后瘫倒在休息室的沙发上。"

# game/act2.rpy:829
translate schinese act2_862eccf6:

    # main "...Phew, that was a workout! Who knew she had so many baskets?!"
    main "...唔，她是从哪里变出来这么多的筐子？！看来我以后要好好锻炼一下身体了。"

# game/act2.rpy:830
translate schinese act2_ccd8eeb5:

    # "I puff out a large exhale as I slowly sink into the soft foam. I swear I can just take a nap right here…"
    "我深深地呼出一口气，沉入柔软的沙发中。我好想在这里打个盹..."

# game/act2.rpy:832
translate schinese act2_7c1b8e3d:

    # "That is, if there wasn’t some faint knocking coming from in front of me."
    "如果现在...没有这敲门声的话..."

# game/act2.rpy:833
translate schinese act2_974a6458:

    # "I jolt upwards and the whiplash from the sudden movement causes an imbalance of blood circulation hitting me a bit hard afterwards."
    "我从沙发上爬了起来，突如其来的动作导致我的血液还来不及回流到酸痛的脖子上。"

# game/act2.rpy:834
translate schinese act2_4a501a4c:

    # "I take a moment to wait for my vision to return to normal, but as soon as it does, I see Oswald leaning on the doorframe, a smile plastered on his face."
    "我花了一点时间等待我模糊的视线恢复正常，就在这时，我看到Oswald正靠在休息室的门框上，脸上写满了轻松的笑容。"

# game/act2.rpy:835
translate schinese act2_798b784e:

    # main "Oswald!"
    main "Oswald！"

# game/act2.rpy:837
translate schinese act2_97f579d4:

    # osw "Hey there."
    osw "嘿，你还好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:838
translate schinese act2_d7627513:

    # "I jump off the sofa to greet him, as he looks at me with a smirk."
    "我从沙发上跳下来迎接他，他仍然在微笑地看着我。"

# game/act2.rpy:839
translate schinese act2_8f44224e:

    # "I don’t really know what’s gotten him in such a good mood, but I’m not that curious to ask either."
    "我不知道是什么让他看起来心情这么好，但我也没有好奇到直接问他。"

# game/act2.rpy:840
translate schinese act2_285f3e14:

    # "He’s here now and that makes me feel a lot safer."
    "至少他现在就在我的身边，这让我倍感安心。"

# game/act2.rpy:842
translate schinese act2_b0f07216:

    # osw "So… How was training, [mc]? Benjie didn’t give you a hard time, yeah?"
    osw "所以...[mc]，训练怎么样? Benjie应该没有刻意刁难你吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:843
translate schinese act2_34fbd21a:

    # main "O-Oh, training? Well, it was-"
    main "哦哦，训练？嗯，一切都很——"

# game/act2.rpy:846
translate schinese act2_bd33d14e:

    # "Suddenly, a large figure appears behind Oswald and pushes him off the doorway."
    "突然，一个巨大的身影出现在Oswald身后，将他从门口推开。"

# game/act2.rpy:847
translate schinese act2_596ee3a0:

    # "Oswald nearly crashes onto me, but he manages to stop himself midway."
    "Oswald差点撞在我身上，但他还是设法在中途停了下来。"

# game/act2.rpy:849
translate schinese act2_df903bca:

    # "He then immediately gazes at the figure who turned out to be Max."
    "然后他立即转身注视着Max的身影。"

# game/act2.rpy:851
translate schinese act2_3e678118:

    # mx "Blockin' the way, Oz."
    mx "Oz，你挡路了。"

# game/act2.rpy:853
translate schinese act2_39e6e380:

    # osw "Didn’t have to shove me though…"
    osw "你可以不用推我..."

# game/act2.rpy:855
translate schinese act2_39742c3d:

    # mx "Eh, whatever. Besides, you might forget to tell the pup."
    mx "呃，随便吧。话说，你忘了你有事要告诉小狗勾吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:857
translate schinese act2_c37a920e:

    # mx "A hit in your head might help jog your memory, haha!"
    mx "拍拍你的脑袋可是有助于你恢复记忆的，哈哈哈哈！"

# game/act2.rpy:859
translate schinese act2_7d34bf93:

    # "Max then leaves in the direction of the hallway, disappearing into the bend. I look at Oswald questioningly."
    "随后，Max朝着走廊的方向离开，消失在了拐角处。我一脸疑惑地看着Oswald。"

# game/act2.rpy:861
translate schinese act2_9ed4a048:

    # main "Tell me what?"
    main "你要告诉我什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:862
translate schinese act2_1e07b765:

    # "Oswald blinks at me for a moment before lighting up in realization."
    "Oswald对我眨了眨眼，然后突然露出了恍然大悟的表情。"

# game/act2.rpy:864
translate schinese act2_73d1263b:

    # osw "O-Oh yeah! I told Dylan about your… situation."
    osw "噢——！对了！我告诉了Dylan你现在的...情况。"

# game/act2.rpy:865
translate schinese act2_0c226e6f:

    # main "My… situation? Oh."
    main "我的...情况？"

# game/act2.rpy:867
translate schinese act2_b9ce1ca0:

    # osw "Yeah. I told him that you were alright, and that you were bunking with me."
    osw "是的。我跟他说你一切安好，现在一直在我家里过夜。"

# game/act2.rpy:868
translate schinese act2_724b1098:

    # "I give him a suspicious look."
    "我一脸疑惑地看着他。"

# game/act2.rpy:869
translate schinese act2_98c0b012:

    # main "Wouldn’t that be a bit… concerning, from his point of view?"
    main "从他的角度来看，这不是更...令人担忧吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:871
translate schinese act2_5e612284:

    # "Oswald thinks for a moment."
    "Oswald想了想。"

# game/act2.rpy:872
translate schinese act2_d01d83f3:

    # osw "Hmmm... maybe. He didn’t seem to mind, though."
    osw "嗯...或许吧，不过他听到这个消息以后似乎也表现得挺安心的。"

# game/act2.rpy:873
translate schinese act2_d21e79ee:

    # main "I… I see. Does Dylan know about… {i}all this?{/i}"
    main "我明白了，那...Dylan知道发生在{i}这里的一切{/i}吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:875
translate schinese act2_9c4fc392:

    # "I gesture all around me. Slight surprise forms on Oswald’s face from that question."
    "这个问题让Oswald的脸上露出了些许惊讶。"

# game/act2.rpy:877
translate schinese act2_49f7f1e2:

    # "He tugs his collar afterwards, exhaling a large puff of air."
    "他松了松衣领，然后呼出一大口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:878
translate schinese act2_588a2e1a:

    # osw "Not really… W-Well, not at all, I hope."
    osw "大概...好-好吧，我觉得他并不知道。"

# game/act2.rpy:879
translate schinese act2_9f01af34:

    # main "I… Well I guess that makes sense…"
    main "呃...这样也好。"

# game/act2.rpy:880
translate schinese act2_fa2b8158:

    # "Oswald places his paw on my shoulder."
    "Oswald把手搭在了我的肩膀上。"

# game/act2.rpy:882
translate schinese act2_dff2f7af:

    # osw "Don’t worry, [mc]. The less people who know about this, the less people that’ll be hurt because of us."
    osw "[mc]，别担心。知道这里的人越少，我们就越可能让更多的人们远离伤害。"

# game/act2.rpy:883
translate schinese act2_89f425e3:

    # main "That... doesn’t really ease my conscience…"
    main "但是向自己最好的朋友隐瞒这一切仍然会让我在心里感到有些愧疚..."

# game/act2.rpy:884
translate schinese act2_7a90ab31:

    # "The wolf sighs as he lets go of me."
    "狼在松开我的肩膀时叹了口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:886
translate schinese act2_e20b0b05:

    # osw "I… I had a feeling it wouldn’t. Just, please… stay strong for us, yeah?"
    osw "我有种感觉...他一定能够理解你的...所以拜托了，为了我们的团队，你要变得更加坚强，好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:887
translate schinese act2_9835de73:

    # "I take a deep breath, giving Oswald the best smile I can give."
    "我深呼吸，然后向Oswald露出了我能够做到的最好的微笑。"

# game/act2.rpy:888
translate schinese act2_4f902c85:

    # main "...Alright. I will, for the team."
    main "...好，为了团队，我会的。"

# game/act2.rpy:890
translate schinese act2_4dcff169:

    # "Oswald nods, walking towards the hallway to the rooms."
    "Oswald点了点头，朝着房间的方向前进。"

# game/act2.rpy:892
translate schinese act2_0d460b1f:

    # osw "I need to get changed. Talk to you later, yeah?"
    osw "我需要先换下衣服，待会儿再找你，好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:893
translate schinese act2_a854e1f7:

    # "I nod at him and off he goes to his room."
    "我也向他点了点头，目送他消失在走廊拐角处。"

# game/act2.rpy:895
translate schinese act2_f4e246aa:

    # "A little bit after he disappears from my view, Benjie exits from the same hallway."
    "在Oswald刚离开不久，Benjie从同一条走廊里走了出来。"

# game/act2.rpy:897
translate schinese act2_f5bc7e85:

    # ben "Oh, [mc]. Figures you’re the first thing the wolf sees to have a grin like that plastered on his face."
    ben "噢，[mc]。仔细想想，你还是第一个能让那只狼笑成这样的人呢。"

# game/act2.rpy:898
translate schinese act2_04e04ae9:

    # "He walks towards me in a rather relaxed manner while sporting a mischievous smirk. I sit back down on the sofa and recompose myself before facing Benjie."
    "他以一种漫不经心的方式向我走来，同时还带着有些戏谑的微笑。我回到沙发旁，面对着Benjie坐了下来。"

# game/act2.rpy:899
translate schinese act2_cca6be32:

    # main "Hello to you too, Benjie. What do you mean by ‘a grin like that’?"
    main "嗨，Benjie，你说的‘笑成这样’指的是什么意思？"

# game/act2.rpy:900
translate schinese act2_3308308f:

    # "Benjie chuckles, crossing his arms as he strokes his chin."
    "Benjie轻轻地笑了，双臂抱在胸前，用手抚摸着自己的下巴。"

# game/act2.rpy:902
translate schinese act2_8be4af70:

    # ben "Hmmm… well, you’re quick to study, so I doubt you need my input to reach a verdict."
    ben "嗯...你很敏锐，所以并不需要我解释，也应该能知道我指的是什么。"

# game/act2.rpy:903
translate schinese act2_55b7b0a9:

    # main "Is that so? A second opinion wouldn’t hurt."
    main "是吗？但是听听你的意见也无妨。"

# game/act2.rpy:905
translate schinese act2_7117dbad:

    # ben "True… but I’m interested in a solo conclusion."
    ben "是的...不过我这个人只对结果感兴趣。"

# game/act2.rpy:906
translate schinese act2_7c5464c8:

    # "I laugh Benjie’s remarks off because he’s right, I {i}am{/i} smart enough to know what he’s insinuating."
    "我朝着Benjie笑了笑，因为他说的是对的。我{i}一点儿{/i}也不傻，所以很清楚他在暗示些什么。"

# game/act2.rpy:907
translate schinese act2_fa0455ab:

    # "It feels a bit too convenient and weird that he’s so happy around me; it doesn’t help that that’s the only lead I’ve got on the guy."
    "今天下午的时候我还以为他是个相当严肃的人，但此时我已经可以和他一起开我和Oswald的玩笑了，感觉有点方便，但又有点奇怪。"

# game/act2.rpy:908
translate schinese act2_7aec79bc:

    # main "Alright… I’ll keep you posted."
    main "好吧...真有结果的话我会告诉你的。"

# game/act2.rpy:910
translate schinese act2_893177d2:

    # ben "Only if I ask for it, of course!"
    ben "当然，只有在我要求你告诉我的时候，你才能跟我讲！"

# game/act2.rpy:911
translate schinese act2_8da35ff8:

    # "As Benjie and I continue our playful banter, Alice walks in with Ellie."
    "当我和Benjie继续开玩笑的时候，Alice和Ellie走了进来。"

# game/act2.rpy:915
translate schinese act2_95c000c0:

    # ali "Alright, that makes four. Where’re the last two?"
    ali "好了，已经到了四个人了，剩下的两个呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:916
translate schinese act2_10797016:

    # ben "Back in their rooms, changing. Should be here any minute now."
    ben "他们还在自己的房间里换衣服，应该马上就到了。"

# game/act2.rpy:917
translate schinese act2_53eb06e6:

    # "Alice nods, tapping Ellie on the arm, the cat quickly walks to the corner opposite where Benjie and I are."
    "Alice点了点头，拍了拍Ellie的手臂，猫快步地走到我和Benjie对面的一个角落里。"

# game/act2.rpy:918
translate schinese act2_3e1316f0:

    # "I wonder if she’s done making up her mind…? It’s been a few hours since I asked her to think about it."
    "我想她应该已经下定决心了...？毕竟从她开始思考那件事到现在已经有几个小时了。"

# game/act2.rpy:920
translate schinese act2_2a993ec0:

    # ali "Hey, Benjie. Mind if I have a minute?"
    ali "嗨，Benjie，介意我占用你一小段时间吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:922
translate schinese act2_ac2319e4:

    # ben "Not at all, darling."
    ben "一点也不介意，亲爱的。"

# game/act2.rpy:924
translate schinese act2_b8c41e34:

    # ali "Ugh, just come with me."
    ali "呃...那我们先到这边来吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:926
translate schinese act2_616ff59b:

    # ben "Haha, of course, of course."
    ben "哈哈，好吧，好吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:928
translate schinese act2_f786da54:

    # "Benjie turns to me."
    "Benjie突然转向了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:930
translate schinese act2_fb01e268:

    # ben "Why don’t you keep… her company? Girl’s a disappointing mess."
    ben "要不然...你去跟Ellie她谈谈？和她说话总让我觉得相当麻烦。"

# game/act2.rpy:932
translate schinese act2_2db938e9:

    # "I stifle my slight annoyance at Benjie and nod at him. He’s really hellbent on keeping Ellie at arm’s length, huh…?"
    "我忍住对Benjie的不满，冲他点了点头。看来他{i}的的确确{/i}很想和Ellie保持一定距离...？"

# game/act2.rpy:933
translate schinese act2_f3e10742:

    # "I walk towards Ellie, and she’s clearly shaken by Benjie’s presence. I hope it doesn’t affect her decision…"
    "我走向愣在原地的Ellie，显然她没有预料到Benjie的行为。我只希望这不要影响她的决心..."

# game/act2.rpy:935
translate schinese act2_96d78197:

    # main "Hey, Ellie. You doing ok?"
    main "嗨，Ellie，你还好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:936
translate schinese act2_32891f5c:

    # "Ellie looks at me briefly before recomposing herself but keeping her hands clasped still."
    "Ellie似乎在调整她的情绪，只是默默地看了我一眼，双手仍紧紧握着。"

# game/act2.rpy:938
translate schinese act2_d5e3f8be:

    # el "I-I’m alright, [mc]. This is just my homeostatic reaction to his presence…"
    el "[mc]，我...我还好。只是我身体原本平衡的稳态正在对外界做出强烈的反应..."

# game/act2.rpy:939
translate schinese act2_ba9db56e:

    # main "...What?"
    main "...你在说什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:941
translate schinese act2_6703b625:

    # el "F-Force of habit…"
    el "啊...只是我的习惯性用词..."

# game/act2.rpy:942
translate schinese act2_a727d12c:

    # main "Ah. Anything I can do to help?"
    main "呃...那有什么我可以帮你的吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:944
translate schinese act2_7d3522d2:

    # el "N-No. I just have to get used to it, then I’ll be back to normal…"
    el "没...没事，我已经习惯了，等一会儿就会恢复正常的..."

# game/act2.rpy:945
translate schinese act2_95ff920c:

    # main "A-Alright… Lemme know if you need anything, ok?"
    main "好吧...要是你有什么需要帮忙的，尽管告诉我，好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:946
translate schinese act2_3a212a9b:

    # "I nod to her before turning to sit back on the couch, but the sound of her stuttering stops me."
    "我向她点点头，然后转身准备回到沙发上，但是她用结结巴巴的声音叫住了我。"

# game/act2.rpy:948
translate schinese act2_8e4ee2b0_1:

    # el "...[mc]?"
    el "...[mc]?"

# game/act2.rpy:949
translate schinese act2_f82e0873_1:

    # main "Yes?"
    main "怎么了？"

# game/act2.rpy:951
translate schinese act2_e5006456:

    # el "I… haven’t made a decision yet."
    el "我...现在还是无法下定决心。"

# game/act2.rpy:952
translate schinese act2_baf1dab9:

    # "I sigh inwardly."
    "我在内心里叹了口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:953
translate schinese act2_f5b6bfd4:

    # main "Ellie, It’s ok, just take your time. No point rushing something as important as this."
    main "没关系的，Ellie，慢慢来吧。这么重要的事，着急也没有用。"

# game/act2.rpy:955
translate schinese act2_566277c5:

    # el "A-Alright..."
    el "好-好的..."

# game/act2.rpy:956
translate schinese act2_45d5be91:

    # "As I continue to try and comfort Ellie, Max and Oswald arrive from changing clothes."
    "在我试着安慰Ellie的时候，Oswald和Max也换好了衣服。"

# game/act2.rpy:962
translate schinese act2_60a051f9:

    # ali "Good, the whole team is here."
    ali "好，这下全员都到齐了。"

# game/act2.rpy:963
translate schinese act2_312836ff:

    # osw "Sup."
    osw "OK。"

# game/act2.rpy:964
translate schinese act2_db056098:

    # mx "Hmph."
    mx "嗯。"

# game/act2.rpy:966
translate schinese act2_2969a5df:

    # "Alice presses a button which reveals all the panels on her PC. It catches our attention, even more so as Alice claps her hands to actually catch our attention."
    "Alice按下一个按钮，面前的显示面板全部亮了起来。然后她拍了拍手，让我们所有人的注意都集中在她身上。"

# game/act2.rpy:968
translate schinese act2_0518d5f8:

    # ali "Alright, gather around! Time for the team briefing!"
    ali "好了，靠近一些！团队会议的时间到了！"

# game/act2.rpy:970
translate schinese act2_7d357e9c:

    # "Benjie’s the first to take his seat, cross-legged at that, on a spare barstool next to the couch."
    "Benjie是第一位入座的，他翘着二郎腿，坐到了沙发旁备用的高脚凳上。"

# game/act2.rpy:971
translate schinese act2_0581b851:

    # "He takes that stool closer to the screen, positioning himself just in front of the couch."
    "他坐着挪动着凳子，移动到沙发前方的位置。"

# game/act2.rpy:972
translate schinese act2_605e2301:

    # "Ellie, on the other hand, takes a spare seat on the other end of the room to the side. Max takes Ellie’s original spot, behind the two."
    "另一边，Ellie在房间的另一端找到了一个空位。Max则是走到了Ellie一开始的位置上，在两人身后站着。"

# game/act2.rpy:973
translate schinese act2_3d8267ed:

    # "Oswald pushes the couch to the center of the room, a clear view of everything Alice has presented on the screen."
    "Oswald直接把沙发推到了房间中央、能清楚看到显示屏内容的地方。"

# game/act2.rpy:976
translate schinese act2_1c18c42a:

    # "He crashes onto it, his weight causing the couch to scoot back a bit, but he doesn’t seem to care, he just looks at me before tapping the space next to him."
    "沙发由于他坐下去的惯性又向后偏移了一些，但他似乎并不在意，只是看着我，然后拍了拍他身旁的位置。"

# game/act2.rpy:977
translate schinese act2_796e8635:

    # main "Thanks."
    main "谢谢。"

# game/act2.rpy:978
translate schinese act2_b35af7b8:

    # osw "Don't mention it."
    osw "别客气。"

# game/act2.rpy:979
translate schinese act2_fba862e5:

    # "Alice clears her throat as she pulls out her keyboard."
    "Alice清了清嗓子，然后掏出键盘。"

# game/act2.rpy:982
translate schinese act2_ae4f4ded:

    # ali "Ehem. Now, let’s get started."
    ali "嗯，那我们现在开始吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:984
translate schinese act2_860a498f:

    # "Alice flashes several images of a large, extravagant building."
    "屏幕上闪现出几张巨大而又奢华的建筑图像。"

# game/act2.rpy:985
translate schinese act2_fa486bb4:

    # "I’m immediately able to recognize the kind of architecture and figure out that it’s located somewhere in the uptown districts, up in the hills."
    "我立刻认出了这些建筑，并清楚地知道它们位于富人区的某个山上。"

# game/act2.rpy:986
translate schinese act2_07e57336:

    # "It’s supported by tall, intricately carved pillars by the entrance, with a large man-made tunnel opening just in front of it."
    "入口处由高大、雕刻复杂的柱子支撑，前方还有一个巨大的人工隧道。"

# game/act2.rpy:988
translate schinese act2_09b54af0:

    # ali "There’ll be a charity party that’s gonna be hosted by Eden Corps here."
    ali "这里将会举办一场由伊甸公司主持的慈善活动。"

# game/act2.rpy:989
translate schinese act2_b8c1dad6:

    # ali "Apparently, it’s their usual practice to bolster the monetary support from the uptown residents."
    ali "显然，这是他们的惯常做法，目的是为了获得富人区居民的资金支持。"

# game/act2.rpy:990
translate schinese act2_7df678f7:

    # ali "It’s gonna be held in the Uptown Community Center, where they’ll be importing a data bank from Eden Island itself to track the guests."
    ali "这次活动会在富人区的社区中心举行，在那里他们将从‘伊甸岛’系统中导入一个数据库来跟踪客人的信息。"

# game/act2.rpy:991
translate schinese act2_f9c31428:

    # "Oswald leans forward a bit from the couch, dispersing the weight forward."
    "Oswald把身子向前倾了一些。"

# game/act2.rpy:993
translate schinese act2_3ad65b9c:

    # osw "Yep, we’ve made that clear. We also know that the data bank has some possible information regarding the next steps we’ll take to take Eden Corps down."
    osw "是的，我们之前也已经说的很明白了。他们的数据库中会有一些关键性的信息，可以让我们更好地制定下一步的行动计划，从而与伊甸公司进行对抗。"

# game/act2.rpy:995
translate schinese act2_1750dd38:

    # ali "Right."
    ali "没错。"

# game/act2.rpy:997
translate schinese act2_7af4c315:

    # ali "However, that same data bank makes it extra hard to do long range comms as well as infiltrating the community center."
    ali "然而，数据库的集中性使得远程通信和潜入社区中心都变得格外困难。"

# game/act2.rpy:998
translate schinese act2_702678ac:

    # ali "It keeps track of guests going in and out in real time thanks to all the patrols."
    ali "再加上现场的巡逻人员，所有到场客人的动向都会被盯得很紧。"

# game/act2.rpy:1000
translate schinese act2_249acd15:

    # ali "Luckily, Benjie got us a way in."
    ali "幸运的是，Benjie找到了突破的方法。"

# game/act2.rpy:1002
translate schinese act2_3b54ca61:

    # osw "The possibility was a bit far-fetched at first. A contact of mine could convince the rear-guard that we’re staff and let us in."
    osw "起初，我的一位内线人员可以帮我们伪装成现场工作人员，并且瞒过后方警卫，让我们得以混进去。但是这种方法有些牵强，漏洞也很多。"

# game/act2.rpy:1004
translate schinese act2_85214772:

    # osw "[mc], however, changes that. After... proposing a better course of action for the previous DJ, [mc] can fill that role instead."
    osw "然而，[mc]的出现提供了更好的保障。由于之前负责音响系统的DJ正好无法出席，因此，[mc]可以名正言顺地作为出席现场的DJ进入到社区中心的活动现场。"

# game/act2.rpy:1006
translate schinese act2_9f3cb456:

    # osw "Once we’re in, [mc] can be our surveillance as Alice’s comms are offline once we’re in."
    osw "一旦我和Benjie混入会场，Alice就必须断掉通讯，这样的话，[mc]就会成为我们唯一的联络人。他可以通过监视会场的环境以及我们的动向，来为我们提供辅助。"

# game/act2.rpy:1007
translate schinese act2_e3e0162c:

    # "I start to shake a little at the realization of how vital I am to sell this whole alibi."
    "当我意识到自己在整个任务中的重要性时，我开始有些动摇了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1009
translate schinese act2_c424920d:

    # el "T-The equipment that all 3 will need will be set just before the mission starts. I planned for… most scenarios."
    el "你们三人要用到的装备，会在任务开始前就准备好的。我已经对...大多数可能的情况进行过充分考虑了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1012
translate schinese act2_758dafdc:

    # mx "The mission’s also gonna take place on a work day. I’ll make sure the bar’s safe while you guys are wreaking havoc."
    mx "由于任务是在工作日进行。在你们执行任务的时候，我会负责确保酒吧的安全。"

# game/act2.rpy:1015
translate schinese act2_965e499f:

    # "Alice nods before turning to her desk and taking out a small device from a drawer. She tosses it to Benjie, and the raccoon effortlessly catches it."
    "Alice点了点头，然后转向她的办公桌，从抽屉里拿出一个小设备扔给Benjie。浣熊毫不费力地接住了它。"

# game/act2.rpy:1017
translate schinese act2_1c4109f7:

    # ali "Plug that into the data bank once you get there. It’ll mine all that data and keep it safe until you get back to base."
    ali "一旦你到了那里，就把它插入数据库服务器。它会搜刮出所有的数据。另外，记得在返回基地前都要保证设备完好无损。"

# game/act2.rpy:1018
translate schinese act2_ba3b910f:

    # "Alice turns back to the panels again, switching the images from the schematics of the building to five profiles."
    "Alice点击了一下面板，图像从建筑的示意图切换到了各个方位的视角。"

# game/act2.rpy:1019
translate schinese act2_59c060ba:

    # "They all seemed to have codenames in place instead of actual names."
    "他们似乎都用代号表示，而不是实际的名字。"

# game/act2.rpy:1021
translate schinese act2_4fabc946:

    # ali "Also, I’ve got some bad news. Before last mission’s comms went dark, the ruckus that we caused got the {i}Omega Squad’s{/i} attention."
    ali "另外，我有一个坏消息必须要讲。在上一次任务发生通讯中断之前，我们造成的骚乱已经引起了{i}‘欧米茄小队’{/i}的注意。"

# game/act2.rpy:1022
translate schinese act2_211d8535:

    # main "Omega Squad? W-What’s that?"
    main "欧米茄小队？那是什么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1024
translate schinese act2_729d5433:

    # ali "It’s... Eden Corps’ elite task force."
    ali "那是...伊甸公司的精锐特遣卫队。"

# game/act2.rpy:1025
translate schinese act2_e07697f6:

    # ali "I’ve got no leads to their actual identities, only some code names."
    ali "我还没有找到有关他们真实身份的线索，目前只是知道这个代号。"

# game/act2.rpy:1027
translate schinese act2_f3a7a040:

    # ali "However, one thing’s clear; the reports I have say that they’re all unlike any normal soldier in any military force on the planet, each of them defying at least one of the natural laws of the world."
    ali "然而，有一件事是可以确定的；我得到的报告表明，他们不同于地球上任何军事势力中的普通士兵，其中每个成员都曾经至少有过一条违法记录。"

# game/act2.rpy:1028
translate schinese act2_84606d37:

    # "Alice’s grip tightens on her keyboard a bit, clicking her tongue as she lays each incomplete profile that she displays on the screens."
    "Alice的手稍稍攥紧了一下键盘，然后在屏幕上为我们展示着这些她收集到的、并不完整的消息。"

# game/act2.rpy:1030
translate schinese act2_e3cdf866:

    # ali "They’re all very dangerous, and at least one of them might very well be in the charity party."
    ali "他们都非常危险，而且其中至少有一人大概率会参加这场慈善活动。"

# game/act2.rpy:1031
translate schinese act2_f4f98832:

    # ali "I’ve also heard that there’s some hired muscle there too, and they’re all packing heat."
    ali "我也得到消息说那里还雇佣了一些其他的保安，那些人已经在为活动当天做足了准备。"

# game/act2.rpy:1033
translate schinese act2_11a0fd40:

    # ali "I hope that whatever happens at that party doesn’t tip them off and cause a gunfight. Oswald, Benjie, [mc]… be careful."
    ali "我希望在执行任务的过程中，不论你们做什么事情，都要尽可能避免引起他们的注意，否则可能会导致一场不可避免的枪战。Oswald、Benjie、还有[mc]...请你们一定要小心。"

# game/act2.rpy:1035
translate schinese act2_0cae90bb:

    # "Benjie scoffs while lightly stroking his fur."
    "Benjie轻轻抚摸着他的毛发，不过显然没把Alice的关切放在心上。"

# game/act2.rpy:1037
translate schinese act2_9476e32c:

    # "I exhale with a shaky breath, unable to stifle my uneasiness from the whole mission now."
    "我颤抖着呼出一口气，完全无法抑制住整个任务给自己带来的不安。"

# game/act2.rpy:1038
translate schinese act2_7465a9a3:

    # "Hired muscle and some enigmatic super-soldiers? You’ve got to be kidding me..."
    "雇佣了保安还派遣了精锐特遣部队？这不是在开玩笑吧..."

# game/act2.rpy:1040
translate schinese act2_bc061ae8:

    # ben "...It should be fine. It’s only some richie party."
    ben "...应该没问题，只不过是个富人派对罢了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1042
translate schinese act2_d9cb28b6:

    # ben "The data bank’s probably in the storage facility of the center, and those pompous idiots aren’t gonna set foot in that dingy place."
    ben "数据库大概就在中心的存储设施里，那些浮夸的白痴们是不会想去踏入那种肮脏的地方的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1044
translate schinese act2_ea086ef3:

    # ali "Still… if anything goes wrong…"
    ali "还是不可大意...如果出事的话..."

# game/act2.rpy:1046
translate schinese act2_cf1a6b41:

    # osw "We’ll handle it."
    osw "我们会处理好一切的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1049
translate schinese act2_dd8792d9:

    # "Oswald appears to say it to Alice, but his gaze is on me. Is he… trying to reassure me?"
    "Oswald的这句话似乎是对Alice说的，但他的目光却对准了我。他...是在安慰我、让我不要担心吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1051
translate schinese act2_191227df:

    # ali "Right. Let’s get to it, Midnight Sun!"
    ali "那就这样。午夜炙阳小队，让我们开始准备行动吧！"

# game/act2.rpy:1054
translate schinese act2_6e29afad:

    # "Everyone nods without hesitation."
    "每个人都毫不犹豫地点头。"

# game/act2.rpy:1057
translate schinese act2_1baafc59:

    # "Ellie is the first to stand and return to her lab after the briefing."
    "简报结束以后，Ellie是第一个站起来返回实验室的人。"

# game/act2.rpy:1059
translate schinese act2_4ba558bb:

    # "Alice returns to working on the panels, and Max stretches a bit after leaning on the corner for a while."
    "Alice在显示面板上继续工作，Max则是在角落里站了一会儿后，伸展了一下身体。"

# game/act2.rpy:1061
translate schinese act2_cbe18e64:

    # mx "Best rest early today. Still have some training to do."
    mx "今天我就早点休息了，之后还有其他的训练要做。"

# game/act2.rpy:1063
translate schinese act2_2bbed5b0:

    # "Max turns to the hallway afterwards, leaving me with Oswald and Benjie. Benjie leaps off the barstool, facing the two of us."
    "Max向Oswald、Benjie还有我打了声招呼，转身走进了通往休息室的走廊。Benjie从高脚凳上一跃而下，面对着我们两人。"

# game/act2.rpy:1065
translate schinese act2_d18360ff:

    # ben "Alright. You’re taking over his hand-to-hand combat training tomorrow, right?"
    ben "对了，明天应该是你要手把手教他肉搏战的训练，对吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:1066
translate schinese act2_df0af833:

    # "I raise my eyebrow at Benjie, looking at Oswald afterward."
    "我对Benjie挑起了眉毛，然后看向了Oswald。"

# game/act2.rpy:1067
translate schinese act2_82cd8d0c:

    # main "Hand-to-hand combat?"
    main "肉搏战？"

# game/act2.rpy:1069
translate schinese act2_a76f3993:

    # osw "Mmhmm. Keeping yourself skilled in both close and long-range combat is the best way to keep yourself alive."
    osw "对，无论是近身战斗还是远距离对峙，只有全都熟练掌握，才是保护自己安全的最好办法。"

# game/act2.rpy:1070
translate schinese act2_de907ead:

    # osw "Luckily, excelling in one can also do that, but that’s all a case-by-case basis. Your skills are just one big wild card, you know?"
    osw "在面对突发情况时，掌握出色的技能确实能做到这一点。不过，你的技能往往并不只是局限在某一方面，更是一张可塑造的‘万能牌’。"

# game/act2.rpy:1071
translate schinese act2_588bf692:

    # main "So… you’re trying to see where I’m good at, is that what you mean?"
    main "所以...你想弄清楚我都擅长哪些东西？是这个意思吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1072
translate schinese act2_e89f6c30:

    # "Oswald nods enthusiastically at me, which is admittedly quite endearing."
    "Oswald满怀热情地向我点了点头，我真的很喜欢他现在的表情和动作。"

# game/act2.rpy:1075
translate schinese act2_ae608678:

    # "Suddenly, some ringing comes from Benjie, the raccoon also surprised by it as well."
    "突然，Benjie的手机响了，连他自己都有些惊讶。"

# game/act2.rpy:1077
translate schinese act2_71839ddb:

    # ben "Huh, it’s from Ray. Hold on, lemme answer this…"
    ben "啊，是Ray打来的电话，我先接一下..."

# game/act2.rpy:1081
translate schinese act2_c5622c46:

    # "Benjie takes the call, leaving Oswald and I alone to talk a bit more."
    "Benjie去一旁接通了电话，现在只剩我和Oswald两人面对面了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1082
translate schinese act2_83355520:

    # "Oswald looks at me rather gently, his gaze neither too intrusive nor too aloof. He pats me on the back, fully grasping my attention in a heartbeat."
    "Oswald温柔地看着我，我从他的目光中看不出任何强迫与冷漠。他拍了拍我的背，使我从这份温柔中缓过了神。"

# game/act2.rpy:1084
translate schinese act2_62575fe5:

    # osw "C’mon, [mc]. Let's talk on the way."
    osw "来吧，[mc]，我们边走边谈。"

# game/act2.rpy:1085
translate schinese act2_b89f876f:

    # "His other hand motions to the hallway and I’m more than happy to oblige."
    "他用绅士般举起一只手朝向走廊向我示意，而我当然很乐意听从他的指示。"

# game/act2.rpy:1086
translate schinese act2_3cace755:

    # main "Sure."
    main "好啊。"

# game/act2.rpy:1088
translate schinese act2_25fd5854:

    # "We begin to walk, neither of us really attempting to break the silence so far. Oswald places his hands onto his pockets, relaxed and seemingly undisturbed, unlike me."
    "我们开始并排向前走，都没有试图去打破此刻的沉默。Oswald把手插在口袋里，看起来既放松又平和，不像我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1089
translate schinese act2_3c3ad729:

    # "I’m thinking about so many things right now and it’s starting to overwhelm me to the point that I can’t even describe them, not even to myself."
    "我的大脑里正在思考相当多的事情，这让我有些不知所措。我试着理清每一件事，但并没有任何作用。我无法将这些事描述给别人，甚至无法描述给自己。"

# game/act2.rpy:1090
translate schinese act2_47e599c4:

    # "The mission, my life, the possibility of death, the people around me..."
    "任务和使命，生命与生存，甚至可能要面对我和我身边的人负伤甚至于牺牲的可能性..."

# game/act2.rpy:1091
translate schinese act2_35d59dba:

    # "It becomes a deafening ringing in my mind, each footstep making me fall deeper and deeper into an anxiety-filled collapse."
    "复杂的想法在我的脑海里交织成错综复杂的乱麻，每走一步都能感到自己越来越陷入到焦虑的深渊。"

# game/act2.rpy:1093
translate schinese act2_ce617998_2:

    # "…"
    "..."

# game/act2.rpy:1094
translate schinese act2_c1e09595:

    # "...Then he speaks."
    "...还好，他说话了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1097
translate schinese act2_09c1b1e3:

    # osw "Hey, [mc]."
    osw "对了，[mc]。"

# game/act2.rpy:1098
translate schinese act2_046b90e5:

    # main "Yes... Oswald?"
    main "有什么事吗...Oswald？"

# game/act2.rpy:1100
translate schinese act2_bc9dd156:

    # osw "I never asked how your day was while I was gone. So, how did it go?"
    osw "我还没问你今天过得怎么样呢？所以...在我不在的这段时间里，你过得还好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1101
translate schinese act2_7dadccf0:

    # "How was my day, huh? Well, I can pick a few things out from today. Probably going to have to skimp out on the shower, though, for obvious reasons."
    "我今天过得怎么样吗？好吧，我可以从今天经历的事情中挑出一件有趣的事告诉他。不过，至于在浴室里发生的那件事，还是把它当成一个小插曲，默默地藏在心里吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:1102
translate schinese act2_19d2aeaf:

    # "Hmmm… There was training with Benjie, which was a mixed bag in itself. Then again, there is Ellie’s exam to consider… Hmmm, decisions, decisions…"
    "嗯...先是和Benjie一起训练，和他聊了杂七杂八的事；然后就是去找Ellie做了身体检查...嗯...要和他聊聊哪个好呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:1106
translate schinese act2_7db1eef5:

    # main "...Training with Benjie was ok, for the most part."
    main "...今天大部分时间都和Benjie一起训练来着。"

# game/act2.rpy:1108
translate schinese act2_cf1f8a16:

    # osw "Is that so? Did you learn a lot?"
    osw "是吗？学到了很多东西吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1109
translate schinese act2_de0c424b:

    # main "Hmmm… just the basics. He let me shoot a few rounds, but that was it."
    main "嗯...只是一些基础的知识，然后他让我打了好几发子弹，也就这样而已。"

# game/act2.rpy:1111
translate schinese act2_238001dd:

    # osw "Hmph, figures. Well next time, if we ever get the chance, I’ll train you myself and make sure you’ll learn a lot more with the better shot!"
    osw "了解了。那么，下次有机会的话，我来亲自训练你，确保你可以学到更多射击技巧！"

# game/act2.rpy:1113
translate schinese act2_c515d061:

    # "He winks at me while sporting a wide grin. Well, something tells me that Benjie can easily prove him wrong."
    "他对我眨着眼，笑得很开心。虽然我觉得Benjie可能在射击上更有发言权..."

# game/act2.rpy:1114
translate schinese act2_de6d05c3:

    # "I’m not going to tell that to his face, though. I’ll let him have his moment."
    "不过，我不会当着这只热情的狼面前说这些话的，我希望他也可以有自我表现的机会。"

# game/act2.rpy:1117
translate schinese act2_8e4e0cba:

    # main "...I had Ellie check on my ear today."
    main "...今天我去找Ellie，让她帮我检查了一下耳朵的伤。"

# game/act2.rpy:1119
translate schinese act2_d448f5db:

    # osw "Y-Yeah… I was trying to ignore the chip. I’m glad that she was able to take care of it."
    osw "是...是啊...我一开始并不是很想告诉你受伤的地方可能会留下缺口...不过看起来Ellie似乎已经把伤口处理的很完善了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1121
translate schinese act2_91954b57:

    # "Oswald sighs to himself then averts his gaze from mine."
    "Oswald自言自语地叹了口气，将视线慢慢地从我身上移开。"

# game/act2.rpy:1122
translate schinese act2_3a4d3886:

    # main "W-What’s wrong, Oswald?"
    main "Oswald，你怎么了？"

# game/act2.rpy:1124
translate schinese act2_9475ed90:

    # osw "Nothing, [mc]. At least it healed quickly, right?"
    osw "啊，[mc]，我没事。至少...伤口愈合的很快，对吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:1125
translate schinese act2_43a5dbb3:

    # "He grins widely before giving off a soft chuckle."
    "在我发出轻笑时，Oswald也开心地笑了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1127
translate schinese act2_07336e1c:

    # osw "All thanks to my bandaging skills, of course!"
    osw "当然，这都要归功于我的包扎技巧！"

# game/act2.rpy:1128
translate schinese act2_bdb07997:

    # "Hmmm… should I tell him that Ellie was the one that activated the bandage?"
    "嗯...我该告诉他，Ellie才是那个激活绷带的人吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1129
translate schinese act2_46983824:

    # "All he essentially did was wrap my ear in a warm blanket… then again, acting kind of cute. Eh, I’ll let it slide."
    "他基本上只是用一条“温暖的毛毯”把我的耳朵包起来...不过，看到他现在可爱的表现，呃，还是别去戳破好了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1130
translate schinese act2_9c8c6e38:

    # main "Heh, sure Oswald."
    main "嘿嘿，不愧是你。"

# game/act2.rpy:1132
translate schinese act2_52fbfc48:

    # "We continue to talk a bit more, this time about his day in the bar. Unlike when I was there, it was mostly uneventful, and most of the DJs didn’t seem to interest him either."
    "我们又聊了一些关于他一开始在酒吧工作的那些时光。与我来到酒吧后不同的是，当时的演出基本上都平淡无奇，大多数DJ似乎也只是在表演完成后拿钱走人。"

# game/act2.rpy:1133
translate schinese act2_37010903:

    # "While we continue to walk, a rather slender figure shoves past between us, revealing itself to be Benjie coyly swishing his tail as he skips ahead of us rather flippantly."
    "正当我们准备朝着卧室的方向走去时，一个相当高瘦的人影从我们中间挤了过去。我看过去，发现Benjie正随意地甩着尾巴，带着轻率的表情出现在我们前面。"

# game/act2.rpy:1136
translate schinese act2_bfe2f064:

    # ben "Alright, you lovebirds. Get a room!"
    ben "好了好了，你们这对恩爱鸳鸯，show show way！"

# game/act2.rpy:1138
translate schinese act2_e694b4d0:

    # "Benjie chuckles before entering {i}his{/i} room. His words linger in the air and cause me to become flushed. Ugh, that raccoon never fails to get under my skin…!"
    "Benjie在进入{i}自己{/i}房间前偷偷地笑了，但他的话仍在我的耳边回荡。我的脸唰的一下红了起来，呃，那只浣熊总是有办法让我尴尬到无地自容...！"

# game/act2.rpy:1139
translate schinese act2_06b6829e:

    # main "L-Lovebirds?"
    main "小...小情侣？"

# game/act2.rpy:1141
translate schinese act2_64f7fb11:

    # osw "...[mc]?"
    osw "...[mc]?"

# game/act2.rpy:1142
translate schinese act2_25aa542e:

    # main "L-L-Lovebirds...!"
    main "他刚才说...情...情侣...！"

# game/act2.rpy:1143
translate schinese act2_44f41ae2:

    # "I can feel my face getting red… This isn’t good…"
    "我感觉我的脸已经红透了...该怎么办才好..."

# game/act2.rpy:1145
translate schinese act2_0e6a4df0:

    # osw "[mc], you’re starting to heat up…"
    osw "[mc]，你的身体开始发烫了..."

# game/act2.rpy:1146
translate schinese act2_c68b3dde:

    # "Oswald places his paw on my shoulder, and I reflexively brush it away."
    "Oswald把手搭在我的肩膀上，但是我却本能地甩开了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1147
translate schinese act2_a34d6e6c:

    # main "I-I’m fine! Lemme just calm down…"
    main "我...我没事！让我冷静一下就好..."

# game/act2.rpy:1148
translate schinese act2_74b9d20a:

    # osw "Oh... ok."
    osw "哦哦...好的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1150
translate schinese act2_03c57312:

    # "I take a few moments to let my emotions die down with a few deep breaths. I start feeling better, though I can’t seem to get rid of his words ringing in my ears."
    "我深呼吸了几次，让自己的情绪平复下来。现在似乎感觉好多了，虽然Benjie的话还是没有彻底从我耳边消失。"

# game/act2.rpy:1152
translate schinese act2_b5b3bf50:

    # main "...Ugh! How embarrassing…"
    main "...呃！好丢人啊..."

# game/act2.rpy:1154
translate schinese act2_83ddfd68:

    # osw "Embarrassing?"
    osw "丢人？"

# game/act2.rpy:1155
translate schinese act2_e671181b:

    # main "S-Sorry, Oswald. Benjie’s probably just trying to get under my skin…"
    main "对...对不起，Oswald。Benjie可能只是想让我难堪..."

# game/act2.rpy:1156
translate schinese act2_fdcce3c8:

    # "Oswald chuckles."
    "Oswald轻轻地笑了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1158
translate schinese act2_4c93e9d8:

    # osw "Heh, happens to the best of us."
    osw "嘿嘿，没事，我也经常被他吐槽。"

# game/act2.rpy:1159
translate schinese act2_880366b3:

    # main "Right?! Besides, us being lovebirds? A bit of a stretch, don’t you agree?"
    main "对吧？！再说了，我们是情侣？这也有点牵强了，你不觉得吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1160
translate schinese act2_fcba59c8:

    # "A few seconds pass. No response."
    "几秒钟过去了，没有回应。"

# game/act2.rpy:1161
translate schinese act2_1d1c5ab6:

    # "I wait for a few more to pass. Complete silence."
    "我又等了几秒钟时间，还是没有回应。"

# game/act2.rpy:1163
translate schinese act2_e28f1ec8:

    # main "...You agree, right?"
    main "...你难道是...这么想的吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1164
translate schinese act2_f64f8c24:

    # "Oswald’s only response is to nervously chuckle while rubbing his nape."
    "Oswald唯一的反应就是一边揉着后颈、一边紧张地对着我笑。"

# game/act2.rpy:1165
translate schinese act2_fb5d1024:

    # main "You… swing that way?"
    main "你...是弯的吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1166
translate schinese act2_6686fdcb:

    # "The wolf’s the one to get flustered this time."
    "这一次，轮到狼开始变得有些慌张了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1168
translate schinese act2_06b2740a:

    # osw "You’d... be surprised."
    osw "你会...感觉到惊讶吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1169
translate schinese act2_92af48fa:

    # main "WHAT?! All this time, you were…"
    main "{b}不-不会吧？！{/b}一直以来，你都是..."

# game/act2.rpy:1171
translate schinese act2_064a736c:

    # osw "Heh... Yes, I do prefer the company of men more."
    osw "嘿嘿...是啊，比起女性，我更留恋男性的陪伴。"

# game/act2.rpy:1172
translate schinese act2_f674f31b:

    # "This… I wasn’t expecting this {i}at all{/i}."
    "这...我{b}完全{/b}没有预料到。"

# game/act2.rpy:1173
translate schinese act2_585bff78:

    # "All of a sudden, a swarm of questions fill my brain, and I quickly switch gears to enter this whole rabbit hole I’ve just discovered."
    "突然间，一大堆问题充斥着我的大脑，这是我以前从来没有想到的有关Oswald的未知世界。"

# game/act2.rpy:1174
translate schinese act2_cbd40436:

    # main "W-Wha… S-Since when…?!"
    main "那...那么...你又是从什么时候...？！"

# game/act2.rpy:1176
translate schinese act2_1263c832:

    # "Instead of indulging the question I absentmindedly blurted out, Oswald giggles while he opens his room door."
    "Oswald并没有回答我随口提出的问题，只是在打开自己卧室的房门时傻傻地笑了起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1177
translate schinese act2_bd3831f0:

    # "I realize then that we’ve both reached our bedrooms, much to my dismay. Now the wolf has an excuse to dodge my questions…!"
    "这时，我才意识到我们已经走到了各自的房间前，这让我有点沮丧。现在狼可以有正当的借口回避我的问题了...！"

# game/act2.rpy:1179
translate schinese act2_15a7879f:

    # osw "Heh. Good night, [mc]."
    osw "嘿，[mc]，晚安吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:1180
translate schinese act2_f9b28457:

    # main "O-Oswald…{w} Y-Yeah…"
    main "O...Oswald...晚安..."

# game/act2.rpy:1182
translate schinese act2_04bc11c7:

    # "At this point, all I can do is laugh.{w} Just what the heck is this coincidental yet stupidly infuriating cliffhanger?!"
    "此刻，我能做的唯一一件事只有对他回以微笑。这是怎样一个巧合，这愚蠢到令人发指的悬念又是什么鬼啊？！ "

# game/act2.rpy:1183
translate schinese act2_6cbf0162:

    # "I swear, this is the kind of stuff that Dylan would enjoy out of a good book."
    "我发誓，即使是Dylan这样喜欢读书的人，也无法在书中读到这种他绝对爱看的剧情。"

# game/act2.rpy:1184
translate schinese act2_e7db3960:

    # "Now I have to live in it?{w} Agh!{w} How frustrating to be kept in the dark…"
    "我应该再去问问他吗？啊！被蒙在鼓里真让人难受..."

# game/act2.rpy:1185
translate schinese act2_917bb5ec:

    # "Yet, this is quite the big step in solving the mystery that is Oswald. Maybe he has the hots for me…?{w} No{cps=10}...{/cps}{w} that can’t be it."
    "不过，现在我对Oswald的了解更深了一层。或许他真的对我很着迷也说不定...？不...绝不可能。"

# game/act2.rpy:1186
translate schinese act2_f8c434af:

    # "Why would he be interested in a guy like me?{w} I guess I’ll just think about it later..."
    "他为什么会对我这种人感兴趣？我现在仍然没有头绪..."

# game/act2.rpy:1188
translate schinese act2_92d7681d:

    # "I enter my room and crash onto the bed, raring to get to the next day."
    "我进入到自己的房间里，躺在床上，准备迎接第二天的降临。"

# game/act2.rpy:1189
translate schinese act2_33cae044:

    # "I’ve made decent progress learning from some of the people in this group, and I hope I get to learn more…!"
    "比起我来这里的第一天，现在的自己已经从团队中的其他人那里取得了一些不错的进步了，我希望自己还能够学到更多东西...！"

# game/act2.rpy:1196
translate schinese act2_ba3f4cec:

    # "I wasn't prepared for the week's work that was ahead of me, as both Benjie and Oswald took turns training me to the best of their ability in all forms of combat."
    "我还没为接下来一周的工作做好准备，因为Benjie和Oswald尽他们所能地轮流在各式各样的战斗中训练我，力求达到极致。"

# game/act2.rpy:1198
translate schinese act2_79462fea:

    # "Oswald trained me in close, hand-to-hand combat, just like he said;{w} and while he's a nice and gentle teacher,"
    "如Oswald所言，他训练我近身肉搏战斗；{w}而且训练期间作为我的老师他真的又棒又温柔。"

# game/act2.rpy:1201
translate schinese act2_9e1d452a:

    # extend " I often find myself learning more from Benjie with his strict, yet enriching regimen in ranged combat."
    extend "不过我也发现我从Benjie那种严格与灵活并重的多样远距离作战训练中学到了更多没接触过的技能。"

# game/act2.rpy:1203
translate schinese act2_e0456755:

    # "Over the next six days, I became a lot more confident in my aim than with my fists, which probably shows who's better at teaching."
    "在接下来的六天里，比起挥舞双拳，我能更加自如地举枪瞄准，这也让二人的教学水平高下立见。"

# game/act2.rpy:1204
translate schinese act2_7826269f:

    # "Though it definitely didn’t feel like the week came and went, the fateful day…{w} the day of the mission finally came."
    "尽管不会觉得这周稍纵即逝，不过那决定性的一天...{w}派发任务的日子终于还是来了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1205
translate schinese act2_5b30dd7f:

    # "I wake up once more, still getting used to the earlier hours, being a part of the Midnight Sun demands of me."
    "我又一次早起，仍想尝试醒的比昨天更早，这已经是午夜炙阳组织要求的一部分了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1206
translate schinese act2_801d0223:

    # "I take my newly laundered clothes, neatly folded by Benjie, and put them on. That sly raccoon is quite the neat freak, surprisingly."
    "我拿起Benjie叠的整整齐齐的新衣服换上。没想到那只狡猾的浣熊会这么爱干净，着实令人惊讶。"

# game/act2.rpy:1207
translate schinese act2_2773dcc6:

    # "Considering he does most of the cleaning in the base;{w} it isn’t all that surprising for me anymore to see him sweeping the floors on his off time."
    "考虑到他做了基地中绝大部分的清洁；{w}看到他在休息时间擦地板倒也不是那么摸不着头脑。"

# game/act2.rpy:1208
translate schinese act2_769d9a60:

    # "Guess you really shouldn’t just judge people at first glance.{w} Of course, the raccoon constantly reminding me of those words isn’t helping me forget it anytime soon."
    "不要那么先入为主。{w}当然，浣熊的不断提醒也让我对这句话的记忆愈发深刻。"

# game/act2.rpy:1211
translate schinese act2_27ba28b5:

    # "As I take my time walking towards the training hall, my mind drifts towards Oswald.{w} Of course, the wolf is quite sweet, perhaps even a bit territorial…"
    "当我漫步走向训练场的时候，我的思绪把我引向了Oswald。{w}当然啦，这只大狼真的很可爱，不过他的领地意识有点重..."

# game/act2.rpy:1212
translate schinese act2_bdb01a29:

    # "Actually,{w} nope,{w} he’s definitely the territorial type;{w} there’s no doubt about that."
    "应该是，{w}不不不，{w}他的领地意识绝对是很强的；{w}毫无疑问。"

# game/act2.rpy:1213
translate schinese act2_5bb933b9:

    # "Whenever I think of it, though, a rather simple question goes through my head:{w}{b}'Why?'{/b}{w}\nI haven’t really warranted any of it, as far as I’m concerned."
    "每当我想起来，一个简单的问题就在脑中浮现；{w}{b}‘为什么是我？’{/b}{w}\n就我而言，我还无法证明这一点。"

# game/act2.rpy:1214
translate schinese act2_f6295044:

    # "It really only leaves me in the dark about Oswald’s intentions.{w} Yeah,{w} sure,{w} the guy’s about as straight as me, at the very worst, but people don’t get like that over a simple crush…"
    "这真的让我对Oswald的真实意图一无所知。{w}嗯，{w}当然，{w}这家伙对我一向直来直去，但可惜，只是简单的喜欢还不至于让他给我开后门..."

# game/act2.rpy:1215
translate schinese act2_4247c27e:

    # "The thought of {i}being{/i} his crush is a bit surprising, too.{w} To be honest…{w} I’m not too sure how to feel about it. Oswald may be nice for those reasons, but I’m not too eager on that possibility."
    "他是对我有意思吗？{i}这个念头{/i}也让我有点惊讶。{w}老实说...{w}我可不确定该怎么去面对这份感情。Oswald可能因为这个感觉还不错，但我不是很敢想。"

# game/act2.rpy:1216
translate schinese act2_7be2f600:

    # "Maybe because{cps=3}...{/cps}{w} I might not genuinely reciprocate those feelings."
    "可能是因为{cps=3}...{/cps}{w}我不太懂怎么好好回应这份感情。"

# game/act2.rpy:1219
translate schinese act2_21a85edf:

    # "I finally arrive at the training hall, despite my self-imposed delays. I peek inside to see and see Oswald and Benjie."
    "终于到了训练场，尽管我刻意放慢了脚步。我瞥见Oswald和Benjie在里面。"

# game/act2.rpy:1220
translate schinese act2_9441e9af:

    # "Oswald was in the middle of training his footwork on the ring while Benjie was at the shooting range, as usual.{w} I suppose, since this is the last day, I should train with ‘em, but where to go first…"
    "Oswald在拳击台训练他的步法，Benjie一如既往在射击场。{w}我想，既然是最后一天了，我该先和谁一起训练呢..."

# game/act2.rpy:1227
translate schinese act2_acca0da4:

    # "I suppose my aim could use some work.{w} No offense to Oswald, but Benjie can definitely teach more with less time."
    "我觉得我的瞄准还需要多下点功夫。{w}不是说Oswald不行，但在有限的时间Benjie肯定能里教会我更多。"

# game/act2.rpy:1228
translate schinese act2_4c644627:

    # "I walk past the ring, Oswald offering me a slight nod. I wave at him before going to the shooting range and the wolf returns to his footwork practice."
    "我走过拳击台，Oswald轻轻冲我点头。我向他挥了挥手后走向射击场，他也继续去训练步法。"

# game/act2.rpy:1229
translate schinese act2_566ef1b2:

    # "Benjie is leaning on one of the rows, fiddling with a pistol.{w} I approach him rather casually, the raccoon nodding back to me."
    "Benjie靠在一排长凳上，摆弄着一把手枪。{w}我轻松地向他走去，浣熊也朝我点头。"

# game/act2.rpy:1230
translate schinese act2_dff826fb:

    # main "Hey, Benjie."
    main "嘿，Benjie。"

# game/act2.rpy:1232
translate schinese act2_47c582d5:

    # ben "Sup, hotshot. Want a round?"
    ben "嘿，大人物驾到了，来一轮？"

# game/act2.rpy:1234
translate schinese act2_76231200:

    # "Benjie hands me the gun together with the headphones on the row next to his, stands from his leaning position, and readjusts the target to keep a 25-meter distance."
    "Benjie把枪和他在一旁的耳机递给我，从斜对角站起来，重新调整和靶子的距离到25米。"

# game/act2.rpy:1235
translate schinese act2_2db6510e:

    # main "Well, you always told me the past week-{w=0.5}{nw}"
    main "嗯，在过去的一周里你总是告诉我——{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1237
translate schinese act2_62bbb474:

    # ben "Shooting’s half constant practice, half timing."
    ben "射击一半是保持练习，一般是把握时机。"

# game/act2.rpy:1238
translate schinese act2_64e0b8d3:

    # main "Heh. Right, let’s do this…"
    main "嘿，说的对，直接来吧..."

# game/act2.rpy:1241
translate schinese act2_be31d817:

    # "We take a few minutes going through a few rounds in the shooting gallery, alternating once we empty our magazines."
    "我们花了几分钟在射击场里打枪，射空一个弹匣就换一个新的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1243
translate schinese act2_c8a6a558:

    # "I’ve noticed over the past week that he’s more comfortable teaching through demonstration rather than explanation,{w=0.5}{nw}"
    "过去一周里我注意到比起解释他更觉得用演示教学来得舒服，{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1244
translate schinese act2_d48c2258:

    # "teaching me tips on how to better keep balance while keeping focus and moving around my form to see any mistakes I might have made."
    "教我在瞄准的同时也能保持住平衡的小技巧，在我旁边看着我可能犯下的错误。"

# game/act2.rpy:1245
translate schinese act2_5fcb88da:

    # "I’ve gotten a general sense of self-correction from past sessions, though it doesn’t hurt to have Benjie correct me here and there."
    "从过去的训练中，我找到了自我修正的感觉，尽管这并不影响Benjie这里那里地纠正我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1247
translate schinese act2_8df70bb3:

    # "We continued for a few minutes, plowing through most of the bullets that were available at the range.{w} I’ve gotten a bit more confident landing the shots I’m {i}expected{/i} to hit."
    "我们继续练习了几分钟，几乎用光了射击场里的所有子弹。{w}我在{i}指哪打哪{/i}这方面更加自信了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1249
translate schinese act2_8ae90b2b:

    # "To be honest, a lot of Benjie’s teachings do keep me in line for the range, but in actual practice…{w} Well,{w} I’m certainly not too thrilled with the thought of having to put them in practice in the first place."
    "说实话，Benjie的很多教导确实让我保持了射击水平，但在实战演练中...{w}好吧，{w}我很难确保在上战场实操的时候还能想起来他教的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1251
translate schinese act2_fca77eb5:

    # "I quickly finish the last few rounds in the magazine, the raccoon slowly clapping behind me as he leans on one of the training room’s pillars."
    "我很快完成了弹药库里最后几轮射击，浣熊靠在训练室的一根柱子上，在我身后慢慢鼓掌。"

# game/act2.rpy:1252
translate schinese act2_9998086c:

    # "He stands straight as I place the empty gun on its row, the raccoon patting me on the shoulder.{w} However, he notices something behind me, causing me to lean as well."
    "当我把射空的枪放好时，他站起来，拍了拍我的肩膀。{w}他注意起了我背后，我也回头看去。"

# game/act2.rpy:1253
translate schinese act2_bf4823a2:

    # "It’s Oswald, who just so happened to finish training at the same time."
    "是Oswald，他也几乎在同时完成了训练。"

# game/act2.rpy:1255
translate schinese act2_95de87ab:

    # ben "Yo, Oz! You mind if{cps=5}...{/cps}{nw}"
    ben "呦，Oz！你介意{cps=5}...{/cps}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1257
translate schinese act2_5b66eda1:

    # extend " {cps=6}you...{/cps}"
    extend "{cps=6}你...{/cps}"

# game/act2.rpy:1258
translate schinese act2_5ab8745a:

    # "Benjie trails off, as Oswald isn’t paying us any attention. That’s a bit odd.{w} Usually, he’d at least greet us again before leaving."
    "Benjie的声音越来越小，因为Oswald根本没注意到我们。那有点怪。{w}通常，他走开前至少会再和我们打声招呼。"

# game/act2.rpy:1260
translate schinese act2_ee1974f3:

    # "Benjie seems to share my sentiment as well, as he sighs before recomposing himself."
    "Benjie似乎和我有同感，他叹了口气，重新调整了一下自己。"

# game/act2.rpy:1261
translate schinese act2_6065d9f6:

    # main "Well, that was pretty weird."
    main "额，这太怪了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1263
translate schinese act2_f615452a:

    # "I see him try to stifle his concern, yet his expression betrays that effort."
    "我看到他试图抑制自己的担忧，但他的表情出卖了他。"

# game/act2.rpy:1264
translate schinese act2_20fef3c0:

    # main "Think he woke up on the wrong side of the bed?"
    main "我在想他是有起床气吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1265
translate schinese act2_710bc98e:

    # ben "Considering his bed, that’s quite an impossibility.{w} Besides, it’d be arguably preferable if that’s what’s happening at the moment…"
    ben "考虑他的大床，那绝对不可能。{w}不过，这个时候他脾气不好说不定是件好事..."

# game/act2.rpy:1266
translate schinese act2_ee52b952:

    # "Preferable? Why would a grumpy Oswald be preferable over anything?{w} I quickly grow curious with the raccoon’s choice of words, but before I can even get the chance to ask, he speaks first instead."
    "好事？为什么一个暴躁的Oswald是好事？{w}我很快对浣熊为啥选择说这些感到好奇，不过还没等我问他，他先开口了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1268
translate schinese act2_5c4ad7cf:

    # ben "Well, shall we walk?"
    ben "行，咱走吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1269
translate schinese act2_5512a730:

    # main "O-Oh, alright."
    main "哦-哦，好。"

# game/act2.rpy:1274
translate schinese act2_6d3e128b:

    # "I certainly need to brush up on my hand-to-hand combat. I’d definitely prefer it if I didn’t have to fight anybody, but at this rate, coming to blows with someone else is sounding more like an inevitability than a possibility."
    "我觉得我需要温习一下我的白刃战。我当然希望不要和任何人打架，但按这个进度，和别人打起来听起来比起有可能更像不可避免。"

# game/act2.rpy:1275
translate schinese act2_849fc26a:

    # "When it comes to hand-to-hand combat, Oswald’s proven to be the most knowledgeable of all of the guys in the base, as far as I’ve seen."
    "说起白刃战，Oswald在我看来是基地里所有人中学识最渊博的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1276
translate schinese act2_5eadb81b:

    # "Sure, Benjie’s got his instincts and his agility, Max’s got that hot-blooded nature of his, but Oswald…"
    "当然，Benjie有战斗本能和敏捷的身体，Max有热血的本性，但Oswald..."

# game/act2.rpy:1277
translate schinese act2_b50c0f2f:

    # "It always seems like every punch, and every strike, every action in battle…{w} there’s meaning and purpose to all of them."
    "战斗中的每一拳，每一击，每个动作...{w}似乎都带有明确的目的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1278
translate schinese act2_77fc1ec5:

    # "No matter what way you ask him about why he dodged a certain way, and why he pulled his punch then… he always has an answer."
    "无论你用什么方式问他为什么要躲避，为什么要出击...他总有答案。"

# game/act2.rpy:1279
translate schinese act2_2ff497b2:

    # "Even though he can’t always put it into words."
    "尽管他有时候会显得语无伦次。"

# game/act2.rpy:1280
translate schinese act2_c41ee801:

    # "I climb into the ring. Puddles of sweat from Oswald’s practice are littered across its floor, making it glisten and gleam against the ceiling light."
    "我翻进拳击台。Oswald训练过的地板上散落着汗水，在天花板的灯下闪闪发光。"

# game/act2.rpy:1281
translate schinese act2_476d234e:

    # "He gazes at me as I let out a large puff of air upon standing back up, the short climb surprisingly taking the wind out of me."
    "他盯着我看，一爬上来我就喘了一大口气，这段短短的攀爬惊讶地让我呼吸困难。"

# game/act2.rpy:1282
translate schinese act2_4e7ec242:

    # "Guess it’s still too steep for me to just lunge over easily.{w} Well,{w} I suppose I can’t expect much from a week of training, but still…"
    "我猜这对我来说还是太陡了，不能轻易翻过去。{w}好吧，{w}仅仅是一周的训练而已，我确实不能急于求成，但仍旧..."

# game/act2.rpy:1284
translate schinese act2_09c1b1e3_1:

    # osw "Hey, [mc]."
    osw "嘿，[mc]。"

# game/act2.rpy:1285
translate schinese act2_219b5631:

    # "His tone is unexpectedly sullen, but I suppose that should be a given, with the mission and all that. I decide to ignore it, raising my fists up."
    "他语气出乎意料地阴沉，但我觉得这很正常，毕竟他肩负着那些重任。我决定忽略他语气的问题，举起我的拳头。"

# game/act2.rpy:1287
translate schinese act2_c3d9a2b2:

    # main "Mind a sparring session?{w} I need to refresh on that stance you’ve been teaching me."
    main "介意陪练一会儿吗？{w}我需要复习一下你教我的那个姿势。"

# game/act2.rpy:1289
translate schinese act2_67f121f7:

    # "He doesn’t respond, chuckling a bit as he raises his fists in return."
    "他没回应，只是微微一笑举起拳头。"

# game/act2.rpy:1291
translate schinese act2_a22c62bd:

    # "I nod as I take the first step forward, inching closer towards the wolf’s large form. My whole body still feels heavy from his presence in the ring, his fierce eyes intimidating me to no end."
    "我点了点头，向前迈出一步，慢慢向狼巨大的身躯靠近。我的全身仍会因他在拳击台的表现而感到沉重，他凶狠的眼神让我感觉到漫无边际的恐惧。"

# game/act2.rpy:1292
translate schinese act2_fa9b7ca7:

    # "Aside from the times I had to spar with him, I was a lot more comfortable when he just taught me to throw good punches.{w} Still can’t apply it all too well, though…"
    "除了我要和他对打的那几次，当他教我如何漂亮地出拳时，我感觉很舒服。{w}尽管，我还不能很好地运用他教我的技巧..."

# game/act2.rpy:1294
translate schinese act2_b31844e7:

    # "Regardless of my feelings, I muster up the strength to take a wide swing at him, which he easily dodges."
    "先暂时撇开我的感受，我向他大力挥出一拳，他很轻松就躲开了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1295
translate schinese act2_36094904:

    # "He grabs my extended arm,{w=0.5}{nw}"
    "他抓住我伸出来的手臂，{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1298
translate schinese act2_750a7478:

    # extend " throwing me to the hollow floor of the ring."
    extend "把我重摔到拳击台凹陷的地板上。"

# game/act2.rpy:1303
translate schinese act2_1a05d5db:

    # "I take a second to recover, the speed of all of it happening going way too fast for me. When I open my eyes, Oswald is leaning downward, looking at me with a concerned look."
    "我花了一会儿来恢复状态，那些动作对我来说太快了。当我睁眼时，Oswald正俯身向下，关切地看着我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1305
translate schinese act2_bc15c3e1:

    # osw "You ok?"
    osw "你还好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1307
translate schinese act2_44e8df17:

    # main "Y-Yeah… just a bit winded by the speed, is all."
    main "额-嗯...只是速度太快，有点喘不过气来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1309
translate schinese act2_5750f746:

    # "Oswald nods as he sighs in relief. He extends his hand to me, which I take immediately.{w} He lifts me up to a sitting position, sitting cross-legged afterward to level with me."
    "Oswald点了点头，松了口气。他向我伸手，我很快握住起身。{w}他把我带到坐下休息的地方，然后盘腿坐下，刚好和我到一样的高度。"

# game/act2.rpy:1311
translate schinese act2_cac17a66:

    # osw "So, what did you do wrong?"
    osw "那么，你认为你哪个步骤出了问题？"

# game/act2.rpy:1312
translate schinese act2_003addc9:

    # "I groan as I scratch my head, the impact I had on the ring still slightly tingling across my back."
    "我一边挠头一边呻吟，后背撞到拳击台的地方仍然隐隐作痛。"

# game/act2.rpy:1313
translate schinese act2_71737487:

    # main "Well… I thought that I could-{w=0.5}{nw}"
    main "额...我觉得我应该-{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1315
translate schinese act2_c4fca4c0:

    # osw "Alright, stop. That’s where the problem lies."
    osw "好，停下吧。这就是问题所在。"

# game/act2.rpy:1316
translate schinese act2_9e897d2b:

    # "He pokes my forehead with his finger, his claw trailing on it softly."
    "他用手指戳戳我的额头，爪子轻轻挠。"

# game/act2.rpy:1318
translate schinese act2_c19dd821:

    # osw "You’re still dependent on that head of yours. Thinking in the middle of the fight can only get you so far."
    osw "你仍然在依赖用头脑来战斗，在战斗中思前虑后只能让你止步于此。"

# game/act2.rpy:1319
translate schinese act2_fadcdc42:

    # "I pout in frustration. The wolf continues on."
    "我有点沮丧地噘嘴，狼继续说道。"

# game/act2.rpy:1321
translate schinese act2_f50b0f44:

    # osw "You have to learn to cut your thinking mid-fight. You see an attack, you react accordingly."
    osw "你必须去学习用本能战斗。看到袭击就本能地躲闪。"

# game/act2.rpy:1322
translate schinese act2_5d336660:

    # main "You make it sound so easy…"
    main "你说的太简单了..."

# game/act2.rpy:1323
translate schinese act2_00c7d0a2:

    # "Oswald grabs me by the torso, lifting me as he stands up."
    "Oswald抓住我的手，拉我起身。"

# game/act2.rpy:1324
translate schinese act2_a1953c68:

    # osw "Well, that’s because it develops naturally the more experience you have. You don’t have to actively hone it, but it speeds up the process if you do."
    osw "是这样，因为战斗本能的形成仰赖于你战斗经验的多寡程度。并不需要主动去训练，但是训练确实能加速战斗本能培养的过程。"

# game/act2.rpy:1325
translate schinese act2_832bba9a:

    # "I shake my head in confusion."
    "我困惑地摇摇头。"

# game/act2.rpy:1326
translate schinese act2_0e984e67:

    # main "If it’s just a natural progression thing, why do we still spar and train? Wouldn’t it be better if I beat up some criminals out in some alleys or something?"
    main "如果这只是一种自然的进步，那我们为啥还要在这里格斗训练呢？我直接去巷子里痛打几个罪犯之类的不是更好吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1327
translate schinese act2_adad4431:

    # "Oswald chuckles at my remark, but quickly recomposes himself."
    "Oswald听了我的话咯咯笑了起来，但很快镇定下来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1329
translate schinese act2_bb689878:

    # osw "C’mon, [mc]. Just because you’re mentally capable of keeping up with someone, doesn’t mean your body will follow suit.{w} If it does, it’ll break itself in the process."
    osw "好嘛，[mc]。因为只是在精神上跟上别人的步伐，并不意味着你的身体也行。{w}如果你真这么干了，在这过程中你会受伤的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1331
translate schinese act2_a0d60f96:

    # "Oswald flexes his bicep, smirking to himself as he does so.{w} At this point, I’m quite used to seeing the wolf’s toned form, at least enough to stop being a blushing mess around him."
    "Oswald弯曲他的肱二头肌，自鸣得意地笑着。{w}现在的我已经习惯看他健美的体型了，至少足以令我在他身旁镇之以静，而不是感到脸红。"

# game/act2.rpy:1332
translate schinese act2_e5b00b66:

    # osw "We train and spar to mitigate that. The more our body’s capable of doing the things it needs to survive, the more possibilities our mind can default to almost any situation."
    osw "我们训练和演习来缓解这种情况。练的越多，我们的身体越能掌握生存必须的能力，我们的头脑也更有可能去应对更多种情况。"

# game/act2.rpy:1333
translate schinese act2_e23eb6a2:

    # "Oswald raises his fists once more, his expression returning to a serious one."
    "Oswald再次举起拳头，表情愈渐严肃。"

# game/act2.rpy:1335
translate schinese act2_f510f7ac:

    # osw "Now, I’m not going to attack nor counter any of your moves.{w} Try to develop your strength,{w} throw stronger punches.{w} That’ll be the focus for as long as we can ‘til the mission."
    osw "现在，我不会主动攻击或者反击你的动作，你就任意施为吧。{w}试着提升你攻击的力道，{w}打出更为强力的一拳。{w}我们就专注于此着重训练，直到你能达成目标。"

# game/act2.rpy:1337
translate schinese act2_9fd01d5f:

    # main "Right!"
    main "好！"

# game/act2.rpy:1339
translate schinese act2_f53dc245:

    # "We continue like this for the next few minutes or so, stopping after a sequence of strikes at his open palms for him to give his feedback."
    "我们持续这么做了几分钟，连续击打在他张开的手掌上，直到他给出反馈为止。"

# game/act2.rpy:1340
translate schinese act2_c42573c9:

    # "He focuses on being more agile, making me work harder to keep up with his speed."
    "他专注于使自己的动作更加敏捷，我得投入更多精力才能跟上他的节奏。"

# game/act2.rpy:1341
translate schinese act2_78b67016:

    # "After a while, we finally stop, my body not feeling as shit as after the first few combat sessions with Oswald."
    "过了一段时间，我们还是停下来了，不过我的身体不像第一次和Oswald战斗后感觉那么糟糕了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1342
translate schinese act2_72f5707a:

    # "I suppose there’s that as a mark of improvement to be proud of."
    "我想这算是进步的标志，还是值得骄傲的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1343
translate schinese act2_fe7a48ed:

    # "Oswald creates a distance between us as I take a moment to catch my breath."
    "Oswald在我们之间留了一段距离让我喘了口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:1345
translate schinese act2_1d7d527e:

    # extend " As I regain myself I look up to Oswald, who’s dripping in sweat."
    extend "当我恢复回来时，我看向Oswald，他正流着汗。"

# game/act2.rpy:1347
translate schinese act2_3a08c7ee:

    # "He rotates his arms as he stretches upwards, a low-pitched groan escaping his muzzle.{w} Probably hit a good spot in that stretch."
    "他一边向上伸展，一边转动手臂，一阵低沉的呻吟从他嘴里传出。{w}可能那个力度打的不错。"

# game/act2.rpy:1349
translate schinese act2_03f8797e:

    # "Sweat falls down from his chest to his abdomen, until he finally stops, releasing a sigh as he looks at me once more."
    "汗水从他的胸肌滴落到腹部，他最后停下来，再次看向我，叹了一口气。"

# game/act2.rpy:1351
translate schinese act2_2a1bf1e2:

    # osw "Well, that was a nice warmup, I’d say. Enough for the mission, maybe?"
    osw "好吧，我得说，这是个不错的热身。可能，足够完成任务了？"

# game/act2.rpy:1352
translate schinese act2_36af877e:

    # "I laugh nervously at his remark."
    "听到他的回应，我紧张地笑了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1353
translate schinese act2_386c5602:

    # main "I’d like to think I won’t overexert myself…"
    main "我希望我不会过度劳累..."

# game/act2.rpy:1355
translate schinese act2_580dff37:

    # osw "That is a nice thought, yeah…"
    osw "那想法不错，哈..."

# game/act2.rpy:1356
translate schinese act2_e4abd345:

    # "Oswald sighs to himself, his smile quickly dissipating back into that aloof expression."
    "Oswald自己也松了口气，他的微笑很快又被冷漠取代。"

# game/act2.rpy:1357
translate schinese act2_3a4a74ad:

    # main "Is{cps=5}...{/cps} something wrong, Oz?"
    main "有{cps=5}...{/cps}什么问题么，Oz？"

# game/act2.rpy:1359
translate schinese act2_935a8bdb:

    # "Oswald quickly realizes my concern, his ears perking up as his eyes dart towards me."
    "Oswald立刻察觉到了我的不安，他的耳朵立了起来，将目光投向我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1361
translate schinese act2_771d2fa2:

    # osw "...I’m fine, [mc]. I’m just thinking about the stuff I need for the mission."
    osw "...我没事，[mc]。我只是在思考任务需要的东西。"

# game/act2.rpy:1363
translate schinese act2_53451b9d:

    # "Oswald walks past me, patting me on the shoulder."
    "Oswald从我身边走过时拍了拍我的肩膀："

# game/act2.rpy:1364
translate schinese act2_1de7da01:

    # osw "You better get ready too."
    osw "你也应该做好准备了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1365
translate schinese act2_f789f79f:

    # "I nod to him, the wolf taking it as a signal to drop from the ring and leave.{w} As I look at him as his figure disappears into the corner, something tugs onto the edges of the ring."
    "我向他点点头，狼会意，从拳击台跳下并离开了。{w}就在我注视着他的身影消失在角落时，我注意到有什么东西轻轻刮蹭着拳击台的边缘。"

# game/act2.rpy:1367
translate schinese act2_4f328028:

    # ben "Well, well. You really are that wolf’s happy pill."
    ben "好吧，好吧。你可真是那只狼的开心果啊。"

# game/act2.rpy:1368
translate schinese act2_c9ad85f8:

    # "Benjie leans on one of the ring’s support beams, his tail swishing playfully."
    "Benjie靠在拳击台的一根支撑柱上，他的尾巴玩味地摇摆着。"

# game/act2.rpy:1369
translate schinese act2_881f527a:

    # ben "Well, I suppose a conversation could be nice. After all, I do need to get ready for the mission. Why don’t we talk on the way?"
    ben "嗯，看来你需要有人陪你聊聊天。毕竟我也需要为任务做准备，要不边走边聊吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:1370
translate schinese act2_ee3b3c4d:

    # main "A-Alright."
    main "好，好吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:1373
translate schinese act2_0e2fbbd2:

    # "We walk off from the training area towards the hallway, silence enveloping the atmosphere around us."
    "我们从训练区慢步走向走廊，沉默的氛围笼罩着我们。"

# game/act2.rpy:1374
translate schinese act2_22c6688d:

    # "The faint hum of the pipes echoes across the vents on the ceiling, tempting me to take the first step."
    "天花板上排气管道轻微的嗡嗡声在走廊里回荡，让我有了先搭话的冲动。"

# game/act2.rpy:1375
translate schinese act2_73a92c4f:

    # "I’ve always let Benjie start conversations, for the short time I knew the raccoon.{w} It’s always felt a lot more natural, that way."
    "因为我认识Benjie的时间不长，一直以来我都是让Benjie先挑起话茬的。{w}那样我会感觉更自在一些。"

# game/act2.rpy:1376
translate schinese act2_bc216b84:

    # "I hesitate to speak, yet I eventually find the right words to break the silence."
    "虽然我的内心有些挣扎，但最后还是找到了破冰的合适话题。"

# game/act2.rpy:1377
translate schinese act2_77ab525f:

    # main "So… About Oswald…"
    main "所以...关于Oswald..."

# game/act2.rpy:1379
translate schinese act2_617b0acf:

    # ben "Hmm?"
    ben "嗯？"

# game/act2.rpy:1380
translate schinese act2_7ac831be:

    # "Benjie glances at me nonchalantly, a hint of curiosity on his face."
    "Benjie面无表情地瞥了我一眼，但却流露出来一丝好奇。"

# game/act2.rpy:1381
translate schinese act2_d1182c06:

    # main "Did you notice anything{cps=4}...{/cps} off about him?"
    main "你有注意到{cps=4}...{/cps}他有些不对劲么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1382
translate schinese act2_2fcf81ee:

    # ben "'Off?'"
    ben "不对劲？"

# game/act2.rpy:1383
translate schinese act2_9690425a:

    # main "Yeah. Like something’s on his mind."
    main "是啊。好像他有些心事。"

# game/act2.rpy:1385
translate schinese act2_551ab840:

    # "Benjie chuckles playfully."
    "Benjie玩味地笑了笑。"

# game/act2.rpy:1386
translate schinese act2_13292d99:

    # ben "Quite a phenomenon for the airhead, no?"
    ben "对榆木脑袋来说确实不太正常，是吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:1387
translate schinese act2_a0a3d1d4:

    # main "Heh… I suppose so. But that isn’t the weirdest part…"
    main "哈...可能吧。不过这不是最怪的地方..."

# game/act2.rpy:1389
translate schinese act2_791690f8:

    # "Benjie doesn’t respond, and I decide to continue with my thoughts."
    "Benjie没回应，于是我就继续将我的想法表达出来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1390
translate schinese act2_7e94dbcb:

    # main "It’s not like him to stay quiet about his emotions… right?"
    main "会隐瞒情绪就已经很不像他了...不是么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1392
translate schinese act2_6f929785:

    # ben "...Quite observant. Though, it is a bit off the mark."
    ben "...你倒是对他关注有加呢。虽然这有点离题了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1393
translate schinese act2_c394bd03:

    # "Benjie pauses for a moment."
    "Benjie顿了顿，然后说，"

# game/act2.rpy:1394
translate schinese act2_a33d943d:

    # ben "...The wolf’s remarkably good at keeping his emotions in check when it matters."
    ben "...那只狼的确很擅长在必要的时候处理好自己的情绪。"

# game/act2.rpy:1395
translate schinese act2_6833a3dd:

    # main "Really? I wouldn’t be able to tell."
    main "真的？我就看不出来他是这样的呢。"

# game/act2.rpy:1396
translate schinese act2_0943bc60:

    # "The raccoon places his hand on my shoulder, Facing me as we stop in our tracks."
    "我们停下了脚步，浣熊将手放在我的肩膀上面对我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1398
translate schinese act2_4fe8438d:

    # ben "It’s understandable. Devoid of the full picture, you made a rather convincing template, given the information before you."
    ben "可以理解。在不知道事情全貌的情况下，你就只能基于已知的信息套用惯性思维。"

# game/act2.rpy:1399
translate schinese act2_545fd2e6:

    # "Benjie faces back towards the door behind him, and I immediately recognize it as his room."
    "Benjie重新转身面向他身后的门，我才突然意识到这就是他的房间。"

# game/act2.rpy:1400
translate schinese act2_22eb3ecc:

    # ben "However,{w} for your {cps=5}{i}safety…{/i}{/cps} I suppose context shall be your best shield, so you know where you and I stand."
    ben "不过，{w}为了你的{cps=5}{i}安全...{/i}{/cps}时刻注意周围环境可以让你免受伤害，比如现在你就会知道我们在哪了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1402
translate schinese act2_91963967:

    # "The doors behind him open as he steps back, standing on the doorframe. "
    "他退了一步到门框边缘，背后的门随即打开。"

# game/act2.rpy:1403
translate schinese act2_574ad431:

    # extend "He signals me to come with him, much to my confusion."
    extend "令我大为疑惑的是，他竟然示意我跟着他进去。"

# game/act2.rpy:1404
translate schinese act2_98ebc53f:

    # main "You told me your room was off-limits."
    main "你说过你不让任何人进你的房间啊。"

# game/act2.rpy:1406
translate schinese act2_2876ea10:

    # ben "I said that it’s off-limits unless I told you otherwise.{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ben "我说不让任何人进我的房间——除非经过我的允许。{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1408
translate schinese act2_c2fba3f3:

    # extend "So…"
    extend "所以..."

# game/act2.rpy:1409
translate schinese act2_ddad0146:

    # "He signals me again, and the idea finally settles on me."
    "他又向我点头示意，这次我终于下定了决心。"

# game/act2.rpy:1410
translate schinese act2_bcbae81d:

    # ben "Oh come on now, pup.{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ben "哦快点的吧，小狗勾。{w=0.5}{nw} "

# game/act2.rpy:1412
translate schinese act2_94a6664c:

    # extend "Nervous to see the nefarious machinations that come at my abode~?"
    extend "或者说你害怕在我这里见证到什么可怕的阴谋~？"

# game/act2.rpy:1413
translate schinese act2_fd2256da:

    # "I roll my eyes as I humor him."
    "我翻着白眼取笑他。"

# game/act2.rpy:1414
translate schinese act2_7917f20f:

    # main "Well… This is what you trained me for, right?"
    main "好吧...这才是你训练我的目的，对吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:1418
translate schinese act2_fe3f7134:

    # "He giggles as we enter his room. The walls are rather dark, purposefully painted in a dark shade of green, neon lights trailing the walls."
    "他咯咯地笑着，带我走进了他的房间。四周的墙壁粉刷得很暗，霓虹般的光芒在上面辉映着，仔细看能发现是深绿色。"

# game/act2.rpy:1419
translate schinese act2_69ebf39a:

    # "The color scheme of the room and glow from the lighting reminded me of his jacket.{w} Benjie has a bed bigger than the one I have in my room, and it’s quite neat and orderly."
    "房间的配色和灯光的照耀让我想起了他的夹克。{w}Benjie的床比我房间里面的还要大，而且床单和被子都捋得整齐又利索。"

# game/act2.rpy:1420
translate schinese act2_476dc07c:

    # "The same thing can be said for the things on his end table and the desk opposite the bed.{w} This just confirms that Benjie is definitely a neat freak.{w} Surprising,{w} for a raccoon{cps=4}...{/cps}"
    "他的茶几和床对面的桌子上的东西也同样整洁。{w}而这恰好证实了Benjie绝对是一个有洁癖的怪胎。{w}对一个浣熊来说，{w}有些出乎意料{cps=4}...{/cps}"

# game/act2.rpy:1423
translate schinese act2_664a57ce:

    # ben "I’ll pack some things for the mission. I’ll holler if I need you to grab something. Why don’t you look around?"
    ben "我要为任务打包一些东西。需要你给我递东西的话会叫你的。为什么不四处看看呢？"

# game/act2.rpy:1425
translate schinese act2_a2f99d53:

    # "I nod as I walk toward the center of the room. It feels more spacious than my own room, despite all the extra furniture he has."
    "我点了点头并向房间的中央走去。尽管比我的房间多了很多家具，这里也宽敞很多。"

# game/act2.rpy:1426
translate schinese act2_8218101b:

    # ben "Oh, and try not to mess with the order of things. I don’t want to have to clean this place up when I get back."
    ben "哦，也尽量别把东西的顺序弄乱了。我不想回来之后再做个大扫除。"

# game/act2.rpy:1427
translate schinese act2_9479a57f:

    # main "Heh… will do, {cps=8}{i}sir.{/i}{/cps}"
    main "哈哈...明白了，{cps=8}{i}长官。{/i}{/cps}"

# game/act2.rpy:1428
translate schinese act2_ff37c068:

    # "I chuckle as I survey the area, with Benjie sitting on the bed and taking some things from his desk.{w} I notice a few things of note in his room, outside of what I’ve already seen."
    "我笑着环顾这里，Benjie从桌子上拿了一些东西坐在了床上。{w}除了已经看到的，我又发现了他房间里的一些之前没注意到的有趣的东西。"

# game/act2.rpy:1429
translate schinese act2_05c19909:

    # "There’s a row of small vials neatly arranged next to a diffuser, and a framed picture on the end table next to it."
    "一排小瓶子整齐地排列在透镜旁边，旁边的茶几上放着一张相框。"

# game/act2.rpy:1431
translate schinese act2_5a96aa91:

    # "I approach the dresser first, taking a few of the vials and reading the inscriptions on them."
    "我先靠近了橱柜，拿起几个小瓶子并阅读上面的标签。"

# game/act2.rpy:1433
translate schinese act2_dbeb62fb:

    # centered "“{i}Citrus in Lemon”{w}\n“Earthen Morning”{w}\n“Rainy Day”{/i}" (what_outlines=[(3,"#000000",0,0)])
    centered "“{i}柑橘柠檬”{w}\n“晨土”{w}\n“雨天”{/i}" (what_outlines=[(3,"#000000",0,0)])

# game/act2.rpy:1435
translate schinese act2_430c1bcd:

    # "...All have a sort of “nature” theme to them."
    "...都是“自然”主题的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1436
translate schinese act2_6af27bd3:

    # main "So… This is the culprit to your unique scent, hmm?"
    main "所以...就是这些让你有那种独特气味的，对吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:1437
translate schinese act2_a0b165ca:

    # "Benjie leans back at me with slight surprise, followed by a chuckle."
    "Benjie有点吃惊地靠在我身后，然后轻笑了一声。"

# game/act2.rpy:1439
translate schinese act2_fe0373d0:

    # ben "Well, I like to remind myself what it’s like to breathe rural air."
    ben "这么说吧，我想让我记住呼吸乡下空气的感觉。"

# game/act2.rpy:1440
translate schinese act2_9fd05c13:

    # main "Rural, huh?{w} That takes me back…"
    main "乡下，哈？{w}那让我回想起..."

# game/act2.rpy:1442
translate schinese act2_eb1c7965:

    # ben "You’re a provincial too?"
    ben "你也是乡里人？"

# game/act2.rpy:1443
translate schinese act2_a32c693d:

    # main "Yep. I’m from further south. It was quiet, and there was a {i}lot{/i} of water surrounding our town."
    main "是啊。我来自更南边的地方。那是个很安静的城镇，周围有{i}很多{/i}的水。"

# game/act2.rpy:1445
translate schinese act2_c6822bfd:

    # ben "Coupled with the cold breeze, it must’ve been a nice swim, I assume."
    ben "我想要是有冷风相伴的话在那里游泳一定很愉快。"

# game/act2.rpy:1446
translate schinese act2_50fe1466:

    # main "Heh… yeah, it was. Especially during the summer."
    main "嘿嘿...是啊。尤其是在夏天的时候。"

# game/act2.rpy:1448
translate schinese act2_de27ec53:

    # ben "Well, I don’t get the appeal. Being from the north makes you look at the cold a bit differently."
    ben "好吧，我可能不太能理解。作为北方人会对寒冷有不同的看法。"

# game/act2.rpy:1449
translate schinese act2_fb6825a9:

    # main "Huh. Good to know."
    main "哈。明白了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1452
translate schinese act2_a4dc6cf6:

    # "I put the vials back in their exact positions, as I’m sure Benjie’s a stickler for the details."
    "我将容器放回它们原本的位置，因为我知道Benjie是个注重细节的人。"

# game/act2.rpy:1453
translate schinese act2_36ccbb22:

    # "I stand a few feet back before investigating the end table. I approach it, taking the picture and observing the frame’s front and back."
    "我又后退了几步观察起茶几。我拿起相框，观察起它的正反面。"

# game/act2.rpy:1454
translate schinese act2_b520f0ed:

    # "It’s rare to see physical photos, even more so actual wooden frames.{w} I take a look at the photo itself;{w} it’s a family picture.{w} Part of it is folded, almost purposefully."
    "现在很难看到实体照片了，更别说这种木制相框。{w}我看了看照片本身；{w}那是一张全家福。{w}照片的一部分被折叠起来了，应该是故意的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1455
translate schinese act2_d2a0a74b:

    # main "Hey, Benjie…"
    main "嘿，Benjie..."

# game/act2.rpy:1457
translate schinese act2_cae532c0:

    # ben "Yeah?"
    ben "嗯？"

# game/act2.rpy:1458
translate schinese act2_2952aa97:

    # "I hesitate to bring it up, yet my curiosity makes me reaffirm my decision."
    "我有些迟疑要不要说，但我的好奇心还是坚定了我的决心。"

# game/act2.rpy:1459
translate schinese act2_07803c2e:

    # main "You don’t have to answer, if you don’t want to, but…"
    main "如果你不想回答的话可以不回答，不过..."

# game/act2.rpy:1460
translate schinese act2_8eb63ca9:

    # "I show him the picture as he looks behind him."
    "当他回头的时候，我给他看了那张我发现的照片。"

# game/act2.rpy:1461
translate schinese act2_732124d0:

    # main "Is this...{w=0.5} your family?"
    main "这是...{w=0.5}你的家人么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1463
translate schinese act2_5aa43be4:

    # "Benjie’s expression deflates into a rather bitter one, causing me to recoil and place the frame back on the end table."
    "一丝苦涩的愁容拉下了Benjie正扬起的嘴角，这使我退缩了，急忙把相框放回了茶几上。"

# game/act2.rpy:1464
translate schinese act2_3e58f10f:

    # main "I-I’m sorry… I didn’t mean to remind you of anything-{w=0.5}{nw}"
    main "对—对不起...我不是故意让你想起任何——{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1466
translate schinese act2_ed92f3ba:

    # ben "No,{w} it's fine, hotshot.{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ben "没，{w}没关系，大人物。{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1468
translate schinese act2_a7b22880:

    # extend "To answer your question,{w} it is my family."
