translate schinese act2_546447a0:

    # ben "{cps=5}I...{/cps} have six siblings.{w} I’m the oldest, and that makes us seven."
    ben "{cps=5}我...{/cps}有六个兄弟姐妹。{w}我是最大的那个，加上我一共是七个。"

# game/act2.rpy:1472
translate schinese act2_37be8768:

    # main "Are...{w} Are they in Bayline City?"
    main "他们...{w}他们在Bayline城么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1473
translate schinese act2_aeca2ff7:

    # "He shakes his head."
    "他轻轻摇了摇头。"

# game/act2.rpy:1474
translate schinese act2_49b14f57:

    # main "They’re… back in the province, are they…?"
    main "那么他们...还在乡下，对么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1475
translate schinese act2_77d65967:

    # "No response."
    "没有回答。"

# game/act2.rpy:1476
translate schinese act2_2d5bc80e:

    # "Hoo fuck, I just made a mistake, didn’t I?{w} I hope he isn’t mad at me…{w} I take a seat on the bed, making sure to keep myself behaved for the rest of the time I’m here."
    "哦——干，我刚犯了个错，不是么？{w}希望他别记恨我...{w}我在床上老实坐下，希望自己呆在这里的剩余时间里别再犯浑了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1477
translate schinese act2_32823ea7:

    # ben "...I didn't leave because I was selfish."
    ben "...我不是因为自私才离开的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1478
translate schinese act2_64e364f9:

    # "He takes me by surprise, and I quickly glance back at him."
    "他的话出乎我的意料，我迅速看向他。"

# game/act2.rpy:1479
translate schinese act2_70f825b3:

    # ben "That’s what you were thinking, right? The oldest brother leaves his family to gain riches on his own?"
    ben "不过你就是那么想的，不是吗？身为大哥...却抛下弟弟妹妹们抛弃家庭自己一人去发财？"

# game/act2.rpy:1480
translate schinese act2_7e28d487:

    # main "N-Not at all!{w} The thought never even crossed my mind!"
    main "完-完全没有！{w}我从来没那么想过的！"

# game/act2.rpy:1481
translate schinese act2_573687a8:

    # ben "Heh, maybe.{w} Maybe you don’t realize it…"
    ben "呵，也许吧。{w}又或者你没意识到..."

# game/act2.rpy:1482
translate schinese act2_15d5de47:

    # "A sigh escapes under his breath, surely to hide it from me."
    "一声叹息从他的呼吸中逸出，肯定是不想让我听到。"

# game/act2.rpy:1483
translate schinese act2_b9cb8e2a:

    # ben "I have my reasons. As much as this past week’s been a delight, I don’t believe we’re there yet."
    ben "我有我自己的理由。尽管这周我们过的还算愉快，但我不觉得我们熟悉到可以告诉你那些。"

# game/act2.rpy:1484
translate schinese act2_ac0f8046:

    # "He turns to face me once more."
    "他又一次调整姿势面向我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1486
translate schinese act2_da6700f7:

    # ben "Just... trust me{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ben "但就...请相信我{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1488
translate schinese act2_e61dc455:

    # extend ", alright?"
    extend "，好么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1489
translate schinese act2_a9ec568c:

    # main "...Ok."
    main "...嗯。"

# game/act2.rpy:1491
translate schinese act2_4f52baf4:

    # "The doors suddenly slide wide open, with Alice on the other side, a box covering up her chest."
    "门突然敞开了，Alice站在门外，胸前抱着一个箱子。"

# game/act2.rpy:1494
translate schinese act2_bc01c9cc:

    # ali "Hey Benjie! Here’s the rest of the stuff that-{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ali "嘿Benjie！这些是你需要的其他东——{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1495
translate schinese act2_17413015:

    # "She cuts herself off when she sees me."
    "一看到我，她就把想说的咽了回去。"

# game/act2.rpy:1497
translate schinese act2_64e03516:

    # ali "Oh{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ali "哦{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1499
translate schinese act2_7b10366c:

    # extend ", hey, [mc]!{w} Perfect timing."
    extend "，嘿，[mc]！{w}时间刚刚好。"

# game/act2.rpy:1500
translate schinese act2_eb65e46b:

    # "I wave at her, but Benjie stands, approaching the tiger."
    "我挥手向她问好，Benjie则站了起来，向那只雌虎走去。"

# game/act2.rpy:1501
translate schinese act2_e2f1835d:

    # ben "Everything’s here, yes?"
    ben "所有东西都在这里了是吧？"

# game/act2.rpy:1503
translate schinese act2_e2e405c4:

    # ali "With some extra leftovers, as per your request."
    ali "还有你要求额外留的一些剩菜。"

# game/act2.rpy:1504
translate schinese act2_fb595235:

    # "Benjie chuckles."
    "Benjie轻轻笑道。"

# game/act2.rpy:1506
translate schinese act2_fc31a73f:

    # ben "Perfect.{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ben "完美。{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1508
translate schinese act2_afcb0a59:

    # extend "Thank you, darling."
    extend "谢谢你，亲爱的。"

# game/act2.rpy:1510
translate schinese act2_db262a35:

    # "He winks, Alice rolling her eyes in response. "
    "Benjie抛了个媚眼，却惹得Alice以白眼相回。"

# game/act2.rpy:1512
translate schinese act2_c9bea6a9:

    # extend "Her eyes dart to me instead."
    extend "相反她将目光快速转向我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1514
translate schinese act2_0d71c6a0:

    # ali "Your stuff’s at the lounge, in a box, too. All prepared for the mission at hand!"
    ali "你的东西都放到休息室了，也在一个箱子里面。它们全部都已为即将到来的任务做好了准备！"

# game/act2.rpy:1517
translate schinese act2_ec796e62:

    # "I nod at her, and she promptly leaves, pouting at Benjie before doing so, causing the raccoon to chuckle."
    "我向她点点头，接着她就迅速离开了，临走前还对Benjie撅了噘嘴，这让那只浣熊咯咯笑了起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1519
translate schinese act2_b365a1b3:

    # ben "Well then, hotshot. Go ahead, to the lounge.{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ben "那么，大佬。走吧，到休息室去。{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1521
translate schinese act2_e5e2afce:

    # extend "We’ll need to get ready for a party, after all."
    extend "毕竟我们得为那场活动做好准备。"

# game/act2.rpy:1522
translate schinese act2_83a23442:

    # main "O-Oh. Alright, then…"
    main "喔—哦。也对，那..."

# game/act2.rpy:1526
translate schinese act2_a0b3062d:

    # "I take the hint and leave first for the lounge. I’m sure Benjie will catch up after a bit;{w} he’s always been quick with his business."
    "我心领神会，先一步向休息室走去。我很确定Benjie很快就会赶上我；{w}他做事一向很快。"

# game/act2.rpy:1529
translate schinese act2_5e8a6ff0:

    # "I take a brisk pace to reach the lounge,{w=0.5}{nw} "
    "我迈着轻快的步伐到了休息室，{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1531
translate schinese act2_149dc75d:

    # extend "crashing onto the couch as I groan to myself."
    extend "我呻吟着一头倒向沙发。"

# game/act2.rpy:1532
translate schinese act2_77a74d1e:

    # main "Ugh… I messed up…didn’t I?"
    main "呃啊...我搞砸了...不是吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1533
translate schinese act2_0e8ecaf1:

    # "I shake my head in embarrassment and shame.{w} Dammit, I’m a lot more tactful than{cps=4}...{/cps} whatever that was."
    "我摇了摇头，感觉无地自容。{w}真是的，我刚才真是{cps=4}...{/cps}委婉得不能再委婉了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1534
translate schinese act2_fac21e2c:

    # "Bringing up his parents when they were hidden in the photo…{w} Stupid, [mc], stupid!{w} I suppose I did need to sate my curiosity, but…"
    "指出他藏在照片里的父母...{w}愚蠢，[mc]，真是愚蠢！{w}我猜我确实需要满足一下自己的好奇心，但是..."

# game/act2.rpy:1535
translate schinese act2_0b5fc1cc:

    # "As I groan, I suddenly feel something pressing on my nose. A shadow looms over me with it,{w=0.5}{nw}"
    "正当我懊悔不已，我突然感到有什么东西压到了我的鼻子。一团阴影笼罩了我，{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1542
translate schinese act2_1c9bf07a:

    # extend " making me blink twice to see what was booping me."
    extend "我眨了眨眼，想看看是谁在戳我。"

# game/act2.rpy:1543
translate schinese act2_837fb5d5:

    # ali "Nervous?"
    ali "焦虑吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1544
translate schinese act2_da2ae48d:

    # "I slowly stand as the shadow turns out to be Alice."
    "我慢慢直起身来，慢慢看清原来是Alice。"

# game/act2.rpy:1546
translate schinese act2_f4d90cbd:

    # ali "A bit imprudent to sleep before you head out on a mission, no?"
    ali "在执行任务之前睡觉是不是有点鲁莽，嗯？"

# game/act2.rpy:1547
translate schinese act2_3914e830:

    # "I shift into a sitting position on the sofa, leaning back with a sigh escaping my lips."
    "坐立不安，我最后一屁股坐在了沙发上，深深地向后靠下去，内心的话语伴随着一丝无奈从低垂的嘴角叹了出来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1548
translate schinese act2_13cd6613:

    # main "I know…{w} but I kinda need to calm down."
    main "我知道...{w}但我需要稍微冷静一下。"

# game/act2.rpy:1549
translate schinese act2_acf5a417:

    # "Alice stifles a chuckle."
    "Alice忍住没笑出来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1551
translate schinese act2_c4f3322b:

    # ali "Did Benjie give you the ol’ boot after letting you in his room?"
    ali "Benjie让你进他的房间后有没有给你一脚？"

# game/act2.rpy:1552
translate schinese act2_7bf00dd1:

    # "I nod to her, the tigress planting herself onto the living chair opposite me.{w=0.5}{nw} "
    "我点点头，这只雌虎一屁股栽进我面前的扶手椅上。{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1554
translate schinese act2_dd963b5d:

    # extend "She places a bag onto the coffee table, signaling me to take a look inside."
    extend "她把一个包放在咖啡桌上，示意我看看里面。"

# game/act2.rpy:1556
translate schinese act2_beed8936:

    # ali "Your new gear. You can thank me and Ellie for all the upgrades we found useful for your skillset!"
    ali "你的新装备。你可要感谢我和Ellie，我们升级的这些地方与你的相关技能可谓是相性极好！"

# game/act2.rpy:1558
translate schinese act2_8ace9d8b:

    # "As I open the bag, Alice looks expectantly at me with each object I take out.{w} Inside the bag is: a gas mask,{w} an improved version of my jacket{w} and a communicator device."
    "当我打开袋子时，Alice期待地看着我从里面掏出每一样东西。{w}包里有:一个防毒面具，{w}我的夹克的改进版{w}和一个通讯设备。"

# game/act2.rpy:1569
translate schinese act2_ff923416:

    # main "W-Wow…{w} This is…"
    main "喔-哇哦...{w}这真的是..."

# game/act2.rpy:1570
translate schinese act2_f1e5ef3f:

    # "Alice’s smile minimizes a bit, her eyebrow raising in tandem."
    "Alice脸上的笑意略减，同时，眉头一挑。"

# game/act2.rpy:1572
translate schinese act2_ee7f1d2c:

    # ali "Your hesitation doesn’t bode well. You don’t like it?"
    ali "这犹豫的表现，可不是个好兆头啊，怎么，你不喜欢么？"

# game/act2.rpy:1573
translate schinese act2_51e09414:

    # main "N-No!{w} I think it’s amazing.{w} I guess I’m just a bit disappointed in myself? I bet you were able to get more creative with the others’ gadgets…"
    main "不—怎么会！{w}我认为这真的很惊人。{w}我想我只是对自己有点失望？我敢打赌，别人的那些小玩意儿可能会让你施展更多的创意..."

# game/act2.rpy:1575
translate schinese act2_db4d78e2:

    # ali "Don’t get your tail in a twist.{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ali "别大惊小怪的。{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1577
translate schinese act2_b0f5965c:

    # extend "It’s your first mission, after all, so you can consider this your starter set!"
    extend "毕竟，这是你的第一个任务，所以你可以把它当作你的起点！"

# game/act2.rpy:1579
translate schinese act2_838de88b:

    # ali "Besides, I’ve already had your bracelet updated to interface with the party’s sound system. That’ll be all you need,{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ali "另外，我已经将你的手环升级，它现在可以连接到派对音响系统了。这些应该足够你用的了，{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1581
translate schinese act2_424b9c64:

    # extend "if things go smoothly."
    extend "如果一切顺利的话。"

# game/act2.rpy:1583
translate schinese act2_efa78099:

    # main "If things go smoothly, huh…"
    main "如果一切顺利的话，哈..."

# game/act2.rpy:1584
translate schinese act2_e1a0f4bb:

    # "My mind still feels uneasy about the entire mission. Dylan always said I was the type to worry, but in this case, I feel like it’s warranted."
    "我仍就对于此次任务感到十分不安。Dylan总说我是那种会处处担心的那种人，但这次，我觉得我的担心很有必要。"

# game/act2.rpy:1585
translate schinese act2_1213b3f2:

    # "After all, a life and death situation would certainly be cause to think about the outcomes, right?"
    "毕竟，面对生死抉择人们总是会忍不住思考自己的结局不是吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1586
translate schinese act2_65fa97eb:

    # "As my thoughts drift to the near-infinite possibilities that the mission might end, I quickly notice a shiny piece of metal twirling in between Alice’s fingers, slight gleams reflecting off its surface."
    "当我的思绪飘向任务可能终止的无限可能性时，我很快注意到一片闪闪发光的金属在Alice的手指间旋转，它的表面反射出微弱的光芒。"

# game/act2.rpy:1587
translate schinese act2_1d218891:

    # main "Hey, Alice..."
    main "嘿，Alice..."

# game/act2.rpy:1589
translate schinese act2_aa64e5c8:

    # ali "Yeah?"
    ali "怎么了？"

# game/act2.rpy:1590
translate schinese act2_3057a0ec:

    # main "What’s that… thing you’re spinning around? It looks like something fragile."
    main "你在旋转的...是什么？看起来像是个易碎品。"

# game/act2.rpy:1591
translate schinese act2_88904d1d:

    # "Alice does a double-take on what I see is a metal chip. Had…{w=0.5} she not considered that she could break it if it {i}was{/i} a chip?"
    "听到这Alice仔细打量着我看到那个金属片。如果这{i}真的{/i}是个芯片，她...{w=0.5}难道从没考虑到她可能会把它摔碎吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1593
translate schinese act2_b9be6895:

    # ali "It’s not fragile…{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ali "这不是个易碎品...{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1595
translate schinese act2_87bc9363:

    # extend "I think.{w=0.3}{nw} "
    extend "我想。{w=0.3}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1597
translate schinese act2_49476d9b:

    # extend "Maybe it’s ‘cause I’m used to handling stuff like this."
    extend "也许是因为我摆弄得久了，都已经成为习惯了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1598
translate schinese act2_6e728b3a:

    # "She lays it flat on her palm, showing it to me slowly."
    "她把它平放在手掌上，慢慢地给我看。"

# game/act2.rpy:1599
translate schinese act2_1cd3a66b:

    # ali "Besides, this isn’t gonna be something you need for the mission. It’s a backup copy of a gadget for Oswald and Benjie."
    ali "而且，这不是你执行任务需要的东西。这是给Oswald和Benjie准备的备用装置。"

# game/act2.rpy:1600
translate schinese act2_80b05d50:

    # ali "A cloaking device that allows them to change their clothes’ appearance through the use of hardlight."
    ali "一种通过强光改变衣服外观的隐形装置。"

# game/act2.rpy:1601
translate schinese act2_be631cad:

    # main "A cloaking device?{w} How does it work?"
    main "隐身装置？{w}它是如何工作的？"

# game/act2.rpy:1603
translate schinese act2_f2b4aa86:

    # ali "Well, that’s what I’m here for."
    ali "嗯，这就是我在这里的原因。"

# game/act2.rpy:1604
translate schinese act2_9f660b6a:

    # "Alice gazes towards the entrance of the rooms, causing me to look back as well, only to see Benjie, the chip attached to his choker."
    "Alice转头盯着房间的入口，让我也回头看了看，只看到了Benjie，以及他脖子上的芯片。"

# game/act2.rpy:1607
translate schinese act2_bd990bbd:

    # ali "With a simple press of a button…"
    ali "只需简单地按一下按钮..."

# game/act2.rpy:1619
translate schinese act2_18562d2d:

    # "Benjie’s outfit quickly changes from his usual jacket to a very dapper and convincing tuxedo, completely concealing the bag he had strapped on his shoulder."
    "Benjie的装扮很快从他平常穿的的那件夹克变成了一件非常整洁、令人信以为真的燕尾服，他身上的双肩包被完美的隐藏了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1620
translate schinese act2_8638b6cc:

    # main "W-Woah...!"
    main "喔—哇哦...！"

# game/act2.rpy:1621
translate schinese act2_1bf1a8d2:

    # ali "Infiltrating enemy lines means that they’re gonna have to be non-threatening, but that often means we have to come up with roundabout ways to smuggle any weapons and gadgets in. That would often implicate our insider man."
    ali "想要渗入敌人的防线意味着他们必须得装成人畜无害的样子，但这也通常意味着我们必须想出迂回的方法来‘偷渡’武器和一些小玩意。稍有不慎就会牵连到我们的线人。"

# game/act2.rpy:1622
translate schinese act2_cd962b5b:

    # ben "However, with this technology, we can still be Prince Charmings…{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ben "然而，有了这项技术，我们依旧能以白马王子模样...{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1624
translate schinese act2_dd68ae03:

    # extend "with deadly firearms strapped on our backs, and no one would be the wiser."
    extend "背着致命的武器，没人会发现。"

# game/act2.rpy:1626
translate schinese act2_866ce419:

    # ben "Of course, rifles are not my style,{w=0.5}{nw} "
    ben "当然，步枪不是我的菜，{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/act2.rpy:1628
translate schinese act2_c98c50fc:

    # extend "so this is mostly for my other nifty trinkets I have to hide before we get to the backrooms."
    extend "所以这主要是为了在我们进入密室之前把其他漂亮的小饰品藏起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1630
translate schinese act2_05d4b680:

    # "As we talk, we hear footsteps echoing from the hallway."
    "就在我们谈话的时候，我们听到走廊里传来脚步声的回声。"

# game/act2.rpy:1632
translate schinese act2_b508f47e:

    # ali "And, speaking of a supposedly harmless Prince Charming-type…"
    ali "说到所谓无害的白马王子..."

# game/act2.rpy:1634
translate schinese act2_f9a4780e:

    # "Oswald comes into the lounge, already in a pseudo-tuxedo similar to Benjie’s, though his has a bit more of a personal touch."
    "Oswald走进休息室，他已经穿上了一件类似于Benjie的伪燕尾服，不过他的衣服更有个人风格。"

# game/act2.rpy:1637
translate schinese act2_b3a511b8:

    # osw "Sorry for the wait. It took me a bit to get this thing to work…"
    osw "抱歉让你们久等了。我花了一点时间才让这东西正常工作..."

# game/act2.rpy:1639
translate schinese act2_9a1da962:

    # "Oswald places his hand close to his sleeves, revealing the actual gauntlets hidden beneath the hardlight illusion."
    "Oswald把手靠近袖子，露出了隐藏在硬光幻象下的真正的手套。"

# game/act2.rpy:1641
translate schinese act2_47a826b3:

    # ali "Oz, remember what I said? The illusion can easily break under sudden movement, so you have to be delicate with it."
    ali "Oz，记得我说的吗？这种视觉伪装在突然的移动下很容易失灵，所以你必须要小心处理。"

# game/act2.rpy:1646
translate schinese act2_cec17ad9:

    # osw "A-Ah. Sorry, Alice"
    osw "呃—啊。对不起,爱丽丝"

# game/act2.rpy:1647
translate schinese act2_b8f4cb6e:

    # "There’s that distant tone again.{w} Am I just imagining it, or…"
    "这种疏离感又来了。{w}这只是我的想象，还是..."

# game/act2.rpy:1648
translate schinese act2_036f60e4:

    # main "Y-You two certainly look fit for a fancy party. I kinda wish I had an excuse to wear a tux, too."
    main "你—你们俩看起来很适合参加豪华派对。我有点希望我也能有个穿晚礼服的借口。"

# game/act2.rpy:1649
translate schinese act2_395f6bde:

    # ben "It may look comfortable, but believe me, hotshot. We’ve got our gear under all this."
    ben "看起来很舒服，但相信我，大佬。我们的装备都在这下面。"

# game/act2.rpy:1650
translate schinese act2_8cd43608:

    # osw "Indeed.{w} Of course, this is just to get past the initial crowd, but…"
    osw "确实。{w}当然，这只是为了穿过一开始的那群人，但是..."

# game/act2.rpy:1651
translate schinese act2_7f73a445:

    # "Oswald pauses for a moment, causing the raccoon next to him some unease."
    "Oswald停了一下，让他旁边的浣熊有些不安。"

# game/act2.rpy:1652
translate schinese act2_613f40be:

    # osw "We’ll be prepared to fight if it comes to that."
    osw "如果真的到了那一步，我们会做好战斗的准备。"

# game/act2.rpy:1653
translate schinese act2_94a8d6d4:

    # ben "If we do this right, we won’t have to.{w} I’d prefer that option, at the moment…"
    ben "如果我们进行得顺利，就不必这么做了。{w}就目前为止，我宁愿低调行事..."

# game/act2.rpy:1657
translate schinese act2_c68f362f:

    # "The wolf chuckles as he gently pats Benjie on the back."
    "狼轻轻地拍了拍Benjie的背，咯咯地笑了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1658
translate schinese act2_ca5941df:

    # osw "Heh, that so? I’ll keep the safety on, then."
    osw "呵，是这样吗？那我还是开着（枪的）保险吧。"

# game/act2.rpy:1660
translate schinese act2_b516a284:

    # "Oswald walks towards the exit of the base, looking back at me and Benjie."
    "Oswald走向基地的出口，回头看着我和Benjie。"

# game/act2.rpy:1661
translate schinese act2_f52a93a3:

    # osw "Well, are you guys ready?"
    osw "哼嗯，你们准备好了吗？"

# game/act2.rpy:1662
translate schinese act2_319faa1c:

    # main "Ready as I’ll ever be, I guess."
    main "一切准备就绪，我猜。"

# game/act2.rpy:1664
translate schinese act2_87d8d25d:

    # "Benjie moves past Oswald, disappearing into a corner."
    "Benjie从Oswald身边走过，消失在一个角落里。"

# game/act2.rpy:1665
translate schinese act2_223ec740:

    # ben "Let me get the car ready."
    ben "让我把车准备好。"

# game/act2.rpy:1666
translate schinese act2_09cd7e6a:

    # osw "Of course.{w} Tell Corvus I said hi!"
    osw "当然。{w}代我向Corvus问好!"

# game/act2.rpy:1667
translate schinese act2_bc123a35:

    # ben "Hmph."
    ben "嗯哼。"

# game/act2.rpy:1672
translate schinese act2_2f902ea9:

    # "Oswald and I follow the raccoon onto the hallway, his figure disappearing off into the staircase. I quickly try to pick up the pace, but Oswald lags behind, having no intention of keeping up with me or Benjie."
    "我与Oswald跟着浣熊走进走廊，他的身影消失在楼梯间。我努力加快步伐，但Oswald落在了后面，他根本没打算跟上我或者Benjie。"

# game/act2.rpy:1673
translate schinese act2_985162fe:

    # "I constantly alternate between taking a few steps ahead and then waiting for the wolf to keep up with me, his gaze mostly directed at the floor."
    "我不断反复走几步，然后等待狼跟上我，而他的目光几乎一直盯着地板。"

# game/act2.rpy:1674
translate schinese act2_78845dd9:

    # "If his tone hadn’t given it away by now, his averted gaze definitely sells the idea. Of course, the mission is just around the corner, but still…"
    "就算他的语气没出卖他，他的目光也把他的想法赤裸裸的暴露出来了。当然，任务已经近在眼前了，但是依旧..."

# game/act2.rpy:1675
translate schinese act2_2414efd4:

    # "This is a large disconnect, something that feels unnatural, in a sense."
    "这与他平常有巨大的差异，从某种意义上说，感觉很不自然。"

# game/act2.rpy:1676
translate schinese act2_3fd123cc:

    # "I hesitate to bring it up to Oswald, with all the signs I’ve been getting. Whatever is bothering him is going to be too disruptive to bring up right now.{w} Maybe later…"
    "我很犹豫要不要直接和Oswald挑明，我捕捉到了很多迹象。无论困扰着他的是什么，现在提出来都会让他心神不宁。{w}也许之后..."

# game/act2.rpy:1677
translate schinese act2_e1c025fb:

    # "I quickly go up the steps towards the exit, my partner’s steps echoing loudly behind me.{w} As I reach the first signs of light, I quickly see Benjie fiddling around outside the car."
    "我迅速走上通往出口的台阶，我同伴的脚步声在我身后响亮地回荡。当第一缕光芒显现时，我很快看到了Benjie在车外摆弄。"

# game/act2.rpy:1679
translate schinese act2_516f9587:

    # ben "Ah, you’re here."
    ben "啊，你们来了。"

# game/act2.rpy:1680
translate schinese act2_f5eab462:

    # "I give him a casual wave in response."
    "我漫不经心地朝他挥了挥手作为回应。"

# game/act2.rpy:1681
translate schinese act2_0daee81d:

    # ben "Hey, [mc], I’d like you to meet someone."
    ben "嘿，[mc]，我想让你见个人。"

# game/act2.rpy:1682
translate schinese act2_de31878b:

    # main "Oh? Who would that be?"
    main "哦？是谁？"

# game/act2.rpy:1684
translate schinese act2_3b689d85:

    # "He chuckles as he wraps his arm around my shoulder. He ushers me to the driver’s seat of the car, rolling down the window.{w} Suddenly,{w} an electrical buzzing comes from the inside of the car."
    "他笑着用手臂搂住我的肩膀。他把我领到驾驶座，摇下车窗。{w}突然，{w}一阵电子嗡嗡声从汽车内部传来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1685
translate schinese act2_e24b61c6:

    # corvai "Greetings, Sir [mc].{w} Charmed to make your acquaintance."
    corvai "你好,[mc]先生。很高兴认识你。"

# game/act2.rpy:1686
translate schinese act2_cd3b1244:

    # "I… I didn’t expect this.{w} Benjie’s car{cps=5}...{/cps} has an AI in it?"
    "我...我没想到会是这样。{w}Benjie汽车里{cps=5}...{/cps}有一个AI?"

# game/act2.rpy:1687
translate schinese act2_78b780a9:

    # main "So… artificial intelligence in a car?"
    main "那么...是车载人工智能？"

# game/act2.rpy:1688
translate schinese act2_fa7a5faf:

    # corvai "I am much more than some measly A.I., my good sir.{w} I would highly suggest you rectify such notions in your mind before you enter my premises."
    corvai "我远不是什么可悲的人工智能，我的好先生。{w}我将强烈建议你在进入我的地盘之前纠正你头脑中的这些观念。"

# game/act2.rpy:1689
translate schinese act2_c610c583:

    # main "O-Oh… a surprisingly sassy one. I wonder why you picked this A.I., Benjie…"
    main "呃—哦...出乎意料的时髦。我想知道你为什么选择这个人工智能，Benjie..."

# game/act2.rpy:1690
translate schinese act2_77ce0eb5:

    # "The raccoon giggles as he steps into the driver’s seat."
    "浣熊坐在驾驶座上，咯咯地笑了起来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1692
translate schinese act2_301aeb16:

    # ben "This is Corvus, [mc]. He’s got the power of the latest GPS and maneuverability at his arsenal without all the boring, straight-laced bullcrap of conventional A.I.."
    ben "这是Corvus，[mc]。他拥有最新的GPS和强劲的机动性，没有常规人工智能那些无聊的、刻板的废话。"

# game/act2.rpy:1693
translate schinese act2_1f25f293:

    # corvai "Without the legal limitations as well, might I add."
    corvai "容我补充一下，也没有那些法律限制。"

# game/act2.rpy:1694
translate schinese act2_6b1763be:

    # main "Oh… well, that’s{cps=5}...{/cps} {cps=8}{i}reassuring.{/i}{/cps}"
    main "哦...好吧，这可真是是{cps=5}...{/cps}{cps=8}{i}让人安心。{/i}{/cps}"

# game/act2.rpy:1696
translate schinese act2_029ee570:

    # "I almost forgot that what we’re about to do is illegal in every sense of the word. At least this is a good reminder of where we stand."
    "我差点忘了我们要做的事绝对是违法的。至少这是一个绝佳的提醒——让我们摆正自己的位置。"

# game/act2.rpy:1697
translate schinese act2_6d3cdfaa:

    # "It’s definitely jarring that I have to worry about being caught as a wanted criminal. Is it, maybe…{w} too late to turn back?"
    "我还得担心自己会被当作通缉犯抓起来，这真是太不和谐了。现在回头...{w}是不是已经太晚了?"

# game/act2.rpy:1699
translate schinese act2_14625fd8:

    # "My thought process gets cut off as the doors to the front seat of the car open up, with Benjie on the wheel."
    "我的思考过程被打断了，汽车前座的门打开了，Benjie坐在驾驶位上。"

# game/act2.rpy:1700
translate schinese act2_08833fbb:

    # "He ushers me inside with a quick waving motion, which places me back in the reality of the situation."
    "他快速挥手把我招呼过来，将我的思绪拉回现实。"

# game/act2.rpy:1701
translate schinese act2_f1d39436:

    # "Even if there was any way I could turn back from all this, a part of me won’t let what happened to my roo- no,{w} my life,{w} to anyone else."
    "即使有任何方法可以让我从这一切中恢复过来，我的一部分也不会让发生在我的房子——不，{w}我生活中的事情，{w}在其他人身上重蹈覆辙。"

# game/act2.rpy:1702
translate schinese act2_1d94314d:

    # "If Eden Corps decided that I was out of line fighting for the people I care about, like Dylan, then I’d gladly do it again. I have little to no doubts now."
    "如果伊甸公司认为我为我在乎的人挺身而出，比如Dylan，是件越界的事儿，那我很乐意再来一次。我现在几乎毫不怀疑。"

# game/act2.rpy:1704
translate schinese act2_b2c31c56:

    # "Stepping into the car, I’m quickly readied up with a seatbelt, coupled with Corvus’ engines whirring."
    "钻进车里，我迅速地系好安全带，同时Corvus的引擎也在隆隆作响。"

# game/act2.rpy:1706
translate schinese act2_68c350c5:

    # "Benjie places his hand on my shoulder as he starts backing out of the bar’s garage."
    "Benjie把他的手搭在我的肩膀上，他开始倒出酒吧的车库。"

# game/act2.rpy:1707
translate schinese act2_de44daff:

    # "Light quickly comes from behind us from the sunset, an orange hue filling the backseats, a bit peeking through Oswald’s large frame."
    "夕照的光芒很快从背后就流淌进来，暖橙色的色调铺满了后座，丝缕光线从Oswald健壮的身影旁溜了出来。"

# game/act2.rpy:1708
translate schinese act2_7ee50949:

    # "This is it;{w} {cps=10}the very first {b}mission{/b}{/cps}."
    "就是这样；{w}{cps=10}切切实实的第一个{b}任务{/b}{/cps}。"

# game/act2.rpy:1712
translate schinese act2_0254a4df:

    # centered "{i}The mission that starts the battle of my life.{/i}" (what_outlines=[(3,"#000000",0,0)])
    centered "{i}开启我人生之战的任务。{/i}" (what_outlines=[(3,"#000000",0,0)])

